                    { 16239, "", "1 hr 42 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/8/52463.jpg", 1709, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.56m, null, 2, new DateTime(2012, 12, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The story of the Hand Island no Bouken special is set a little before the events of One Piece Film Z and depicts a major \"Hand Island\" incident during the New World storyline. The story is set at \"Cannon Town\" where a parent and a child work as craftspeople. The incident revolves around them and a commodore of a marine base. The special will also have a flashback scene to the story in the first chapter of the manga, but with new animation. \n\n(Source: ANN)", "One Piece: Episode of Luffy - Hand Island no Bouken", "One Piece: Episode of Luffy - Adventure on Hand Island", "ワンピース エピソードオブルフィ 〜ハンドアイランドの冒険〜", null, 5, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/16239/One_Piece__Episode_of_Luffy_-_Hand_Island_no_Bouken" },
