                    { 38982, "ONA streaming in Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans G mobile game.", "4 min per ep", new DateTime(2023, 9, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 12, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1573/100529.jpg", 7819, "R - 17+ (violence & profanity)", 6.36m, null, 1, new DateTime(2022, 11, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Year P.D. 323. Gjallarhorn's political intervention into the Arbrau central parliament escalated into an armed conflict using mobile suits. The incident was brought to an end by Tekkadan, a group of boys who came from Mars.\n \nNews of Tekkadan's exploits has also reached the ears of Wistario Afam, a youth born and raised at the Radonitsa Colony near Venus. Venus, which lost to Mars in the contest for development, is a remote frontier planet in which the four great economic blocs show little interest. It is now used only as a penal colony for criminals, whose inhabitants don't even have IDs.\n \nThen Wistario, who hopes to change the status quo of this homeland, encounters a girl who claims to be the guide to the Urdr-Hunt.\n\n(Source: Gundam Global Portal)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam: Tekketsu no Orphans - Urdr Hunt", "Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans - Urdr Hunt", "機動戦士ガンダム 鉄血のオルフェンズ ウルズハント", null, 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/38982/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam__Tekketsu_no_Orphans_-_Urdr_Hunt" },
                    { 39014, "", "1 hr 39 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1643/102220.jpg", 1208, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.73m, null, 1, new DateTime(2019, 7, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Recap of the Free!: Dive to the Future TV series featuring new scenes.", "Free! Movie 3: Road to the World - Yume", null, "劇場版 Free!-Road to the World-夢", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uIadgcH8mXk", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/39014/Free_Movie_3__Road_to_the_World_-_Yume" },
                    { 39195, "", "22 min per ep", new DateTime(2019, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 12, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1713/145599.jpg", 988, "R - 17+ (violence & profanity)", 7.81m, 3, 2, new DateTime(2019, 10, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "In a civilized society of anthropomorphic animals, an uneasy tension exists between carnivores and herbivores. At Cherryton Academy, this mutual distrust peaks after a predation incident results in the death of Tem, an alpaca in the school's drama club. Tem's friend Legoshi, a grey wolf in the stage crew, has been an object of fear and suspicion for his whole life. In the immediate aftermath of the tragedy, he continues to lay low and hide his menacing traits, much to the disapproval of Louis, a red deer and the domineering star actor of the drama club.\n\nWhen Louis sneaks into the auditorium to train Tem's replacement for an upcoming play, he assigns Legoshi to lookout duty. That very night, Legoshi has a fateful encounter with Haru, a white dwarf rabbit scorned by her peers. His growing feelings for Haru, complicated by his predatory instincts, force him to confront his own true nature, the circumstances surrounding the death of his friend, and the undercurrent of violence plaguing the world around him.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Beastars", null, "BEASTARS", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bDudMKQBgWc", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/39195/Beastars" },
