                    { 42916, "Sword Art Online: Progressive Movie - Hoshi Naki Yoru no Aria has been licensed by Aniplex of America as Sword Art Online the Movie -Progressive- Aria of a Starless Night with the launch of the Official USA Website on November 19, 2020. Aniplex announced the movie's theatrical and IMAX release in the USA on December 3, 2021. The movie's first limited edition advance ticket was released from December 28, 2020 to January 11, 2021 on the Aniplex+ website, which recorded the world's fastest advance ticket sale.", "1 hr 37 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1590/116274.jpg", 709, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.96m, null, 3, new DateTime(2021, 10, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Excelling socially and academically, Asuna Yuuki is on track to ace her high school entrance exams. Her friend and classmate, Misumi \"Mito\" Tozawa, advises her to take a short break from studying and join her on the launch day of Sword Art Online (SAO)—the highly anticipated online virtual reality multiplayer game. Asuna accepts her offer and soon meets her in the game.\n\nIn a cruel twist of fate, Asuna, Mito, and every other player logged into SAO find themselves trapped in the game permanently. The only way out is to clear all one hundred floors of the game, and to make matters worse, dying inside the game will kill the player in real life. With SAO now turned into a nightmare death trap, Asuna and other gamers—such as the lone swordsman Kazuto \"Kirito\" Kirigaya—must adapt and survive, all whilst attempting to beat the unforgiving competition to the top.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Sword Art Online: Progressive Movie - Hoshi Naki Yoru no Aria", "Sword Art Online the Movie: Progressive - Aria of a Starless Night", "劇場版 ソードアート・オンライン プログレッシブ 星なき夜のアリア", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XvJRE6Sm-lM", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/42916/Sword_Art_Online__Progressive_Movie_-_Hoshi_Naki_Yoru_no_Aria" },
                    { 42955, "", "54 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1772/109454.jpg", 9875, "PG - Children", 5.98m, null, 4, new DateTime(2020, 9, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The story is set in the ungoverned Tokyo shortly after a mysterious power outage incident. Those who survived from the incident had to protect themselves from the mob.\n\nIt was \"Links,\" the young people with superpower, that saved the people in Tokyo. Among these young people, a performance group known as \"Crown\" gained tremendous support.\n\nThe protagonist Hallelujah and and his best friend Akatsuki, who grew up with him together in an orphanage, are also awakened with the abilities of Links. They join Crown and play an active part to save people every day.\n\n(Source: Qoo News, edited)", "Hallelujah: Unmei no Sentaku", null, "ハレルヤ - 運命の選択 -", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XSndRU32tlI", 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/42955/Hallelujah__Unmei_no_Sentaku" },
                    { 43204, "", "1 hr 44 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1192/117737.jpg", 6138, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.64m, null, 1, new DateTime(2021, 7, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "At Sankt Porto, the spaceships of the Amerian Army suddenly come under attack. The space colony nation of Towasanga has begun its \"Reconguista\" operation, whose goal is a return to Earth. As four powers from Earth and space gather at Sankt Porto, asserting their respective claims and fighting for their causes, Aida decides to head for Towasanga with Bellri and her comrades in order to seek the truth. In Towasanga, on the far side of the Moon, shocking facts will be revealed to Bellri and Aida...\n\n(Source: AllTheAnime)", "Gundam: G no Reconguista Movie III - Uchuu kara no Isan", "Gundam Reconguista in G III: Legacy from Space", "劇場版 ガンダム Ｇのレコンギスタ Ⅲ 宇宙からの遺産", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zEJu4ddy-yQ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43204/Gundam__G_no_Reconguista_Movie_III_-_Uchuu_kara_no_Isan" },
                    { 43205, "", "1 hr 41 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1133/124283.jpg", 5131, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.83m, null, 1, new DateTime(2022, 7, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The fourth film in the five-part Gundam: G no Reconguista Movie series.", "Gundam: G no Reconguista Movie IV - Gekitou ni Sakebu Ai", "Gundam Reconguista in G IV: Love That Cries Out in Battle", "劇場版 ガンダム Ｇのレコンギスタ Ⅳ 激闘に叫ぶ愛", null, 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43205/Gundam__G_no_Reconguista_Movie_IV_-_Gekitou_ni_Sakebu_Ai" },
                    { 43206, "", "1 hr 35 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1876/125206.jpg", 5523, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.75m, null, 1, new DateTime(2022, 8, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The fifth and final film in the five-part Gundam: G no Reconguista Movie series.", "Gundam: G no Reconguista Movie V - Shisen wo Koete", "Gundam Reconguista in G V: Beyond the Peril of Death", "劇場版 ガンダム Ｇのレコンギスタ Ｖ 死線を越えて", null, 2, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43206/Gundam__G_no_Reconguista_Movie_V_-_Shisen_wo_Koete" },
                    { 43349, "", "30 sec", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1170/111193.jpg", null, "G - All Ages", 7.23m, null, 1, new DateTime(2020, 10, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "In Sekikashita Kusanagi, Senkuu discovers an alternative way to revive petrified people–using Snickers! By feeding this chocolate to someone who has been petrified, that person will instantly revive just to have a taste of a Snickers bar. With this discovery, Senkuu uses Snickers to revive the famous comedian Kouki Kusanagi. \n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Sekikashita Kusanagi", "Snickers x Dr. Stone", "石化した草薙", null, 8, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43349/Sekikashita_Kusanagi" },
                    { 43523, "", "23 min per ep", new DateTime(2021, 9, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 12, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1950/116474.jpg", 1238, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.71m, 2, 3, new DateTime(2021, 7, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "As part of a mysterious contract agreed upon by a goddess and his parents years ago, Makoto Misumi finds himself sent to another world to meet the goddess and become the hero. However, the deity deems Makoto to be \"hideous,\" refusing to even lay eyes upon him and revokes his heroic title. Disdainfully giving him the ability to understand all languages except the human language as compensation, the goddess drives Makoto off to the farthest edges of the wasteland, far from human civilization.\n\nDue to the disparity between Earth and this new world, Makoto's inherent physical and magical capabilities awaken, making him extremely powerful. He meets various demihumans and mythical beings who all end up being captivated with his characteristics and join Makoto in building a new community where all of them can peacefully coexist.\n\nNevertheless, despite this success, Makoto still yearns to meet fellow humans. In a world where the goddess herself has barred him from interacting with his kind, it is up to Makoto and his companions to fulfill his desire—and perhaps reform society along the way.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tsuki ga Michibiku Isekai Douchuu", "Tsukimichi -Moonlit Fantasy-", "月が導く異世界道中", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9KtypYdnDWY", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43523/Tsuki_ga_Michibiku_Isekai_Douchuu" },
                    { 43555, "", "22 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1097/109900.jpg", 3210, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.22m, null, 2, new DateTime(2020, 10, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "A recap episode with additional scenes which was screened on Jump's official YouTube channel for Jump Special Anime Festa 2020.", "Dr. Stone: Stone Wars - Kaisen Zenya Special Eizou", "Dr. Stone: Stone Wars Eve of the Battle Special Feature", "Dr.STONE STONE WARS 開戦前夜スペシャル映像", null, 4, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43555/Dr_Stone__Stone_Wars_-_Kaisen_Zenya_Special_Eizou" },
                    { 43629, "The anime was originally supposed to premiere in April 2021. However, after plagiarism of costume designs was discovered it was delayed to an indefinite time. After even more plagiarism was discovered, the production team chose to suspend production in March 2021 and restart from the ground up with new staff at a later date.", "Unknown", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1301/113833.jpg", null, null, null, null, 2, null, 3, "Subaru Sumeragi is the thirteenth head of his powerful onmyouji clan. Until the time comes when he must succeed his grandmother fully, Subaru is allowed to live in Tokyo with his fraternal twin Hokuto. While Subaru is kind and shy, Hokuto has exuberance to spare, and her favorite pastime is designing bold matching outfits for the two of them to wear. Her next favorite thing to do is try to set up Subaru with their veterinarian friend Seishirou Sakurazuka who, oddly enough, is always readily available to accompany the Sumeragis throughout the city.\n\nSubaru has to resolve a variety of spiritual conflicts in Tokyo: some are cases formally brought to him by clients, and others are matters in which he decides to involve himself. A selfless teenager, he empathizes with others to the point that their pain may as well be his own. This leaves him vulnerable in a city where nearly everyone makes decisions that only benefit themselves as individuals. Hokuto hopes that if Subaru develops feelings for Seishirou, their relationship will be the one thing that he never gives up for the sake of anyone else. However, is Seishirou the best candidate for her brother's love, or is he hiding sinister secrets?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tokyo Babylon 2021", null, "東京BABYLON 2021", null, null, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43629/Tokyo_Babylon_2021" },
                    { 43741, "", "24 min per ep", new DateTime(2021, 9, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 13, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1805/116661.jpg", 8895, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.17m, 2, 2, new DateTime(2021, 7, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Getter Robo Arc is the fifth Getter Robo series chronologically.\n\nTaking place several years after Getter Robo Go, Earth is now a post-apocalyptic world. Hayato, now an aging scientist, has completed Professor Saotome's masterpiece, Getter Robo Arc. Piloting it are Ryoma's son Takuma, the human-dinosaur Kamui, and the younger brother of Tayel, Baku. Alongside the reformed Dinosaur Empire, they fight the insectoid Andromeda Flow Country attacking from across time and space.\n\n(Source: MAL News)", "Getter Robo Arc", null, "ゲッターロボ アーク", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9C0k2xtPIk", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43741/Getter_Robo_Arc" },
                    { 43745, "", "33 sec", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1662/110189.jpg", null, "G - All Ages", 5.33m, null, 1, new DateTime(2020, 11, 1, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Web commercial for chemical and cosmetics company Kao's Attack ZERO detergent line in collaboration with the Neon Genesis Evangelion franchise.", "Attack Zero x Evangelion", null, "花王 アタックZERO エヴァンゲリオン", null, 8, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43745/Attack_Zero_x_Evangelion" },
                    { 43751, "Ayanami Rei, Hajimete no Kuchibeni is a partnership between the Evangelion franchise and the cosmetics company Kate Tokyo, announcing the launch of their Red Nude Rouge lipstick. While the ad premiered in late 2020, an extended cut was released on February 9, 2021 with additional content featuring Rei.", "20 sec", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1576/110060.jpg", null, "G - All Ages", 5.8m, null, 1, new DateTime(2020, 11, 2, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Rei Ayanami might be a girl of few words, but that does not mean she should neglect to emphasize the beauty of her lips. As she gets ready to meet someone special, she applies her Kate Tokyo brand Red Nude Rouge lipstick and declares that there are \"no more rules.\"\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Ayanami Rei, Hajimete no Kuchibeni", "Ayanami Rei, First Lipstick", "綾波レイ、はじめての口紅", null, 8, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43751/Ayanami_Rei_Hajimete_no_Kuchibeni" },
                    { 43878, "", "2 min per ep", new DateTime(2019, 2, 7, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 10, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1085/117744.jpg", 9036, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.14m, null, 1, new DateTime(2018, 12, 6, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The slightly mysterious daily life of Sakura Miko, a virtual shrine maiden at the Dennou Sakura shrine.", "Miko no Tsutome!", null, "みこのつとめっ！", null, 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43878/Miko_no_Tsutome" },
                    { 43879, "", "4 min", null, 1, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1843/110168.jpg", null, "G - All Ages", 6.38m, null, 1, new DateTime(2020, 10, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "An unprecedented, over-the-top collaboration between Nissin Curry Meshi and hololive has become a reality!\n\nThis is the music video for the original song, Curry Meshi in Miracle, sung by Spice Love (Oozora Subaru, Minato Aqua, Usada Pekora)\n\n(Source: Official Hololive YouTube channel)", "Curry Meshi in Miracle", null, "カレーメシ・イン・ミラクル", null, 7, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43879/Curry_Meshi_in_Miracle" },
                    { 44037, "", "23 min per ep", new DateTime(2021, 12, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 13, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1723/117854.jpg", 4620, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.93m, 3, 3, new DateTime(2021, 10, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Far away from the reaches of demons and war, near the borderland of Zoltan, D-Rank adventurer Red lives a normal existence. Through perseverance and hard work, his dream of starting his own apothecary and peaceful life in the countryside finally came true. Abruptly, Red gets a live-in partner and assistant named Rit—the princess of Duchy Loggervia and an adventurer herself—who gives everything up to join him.\n\nAlthough honest, kind, and loved by all, Red has a secret shared only with Rit: his real name is Gideon, brother of Ruti Ragnason, the \"Hero\" and a former member of her party. Ares Drowa, the \"Sage,\" kicked Red out of their party after their war against the Demon Lord after deciding he was weak and insignificant. Now, even though Red has left the Hero's party behind by assuming a new life together with Rit, his past has yet to let go of him.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Shin no Nakama ja Nai to Yuusha no Party wo Oidasareta node, Henkyou de Slow Life suru Koto ni Shimashita", "Banished From The Hero's Party, I Decided To Live A Quiet Life In The Countryside", "真の仲間じゃないと勇者のパーティーを追い出されたので、辺境でスローライフすることにしました", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q-WDh396OEg", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/44037/Shin_no_Nakama_ja_Nai_to_Yuusha_no_Party_wo_Oidasareta_node_Henkyou_de_Slow_Life_suru_Koto_ni_Shimashita" },
                    { 44041, "", "24 min per ep", new DateTime(2021, 9, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 24, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1390/115029.jpg", 11053, "PG - Children", 5.74m, null, 1, new DateTime(2021, 4, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The balance of the worlds is maintained by heroes. Suddenly, a red-hot meteor falls upon one of these worlds, called Neo World. An amnesiac youth named Wukong Impulse Gundam appears at the point where it landed. The chaos that starts with this incident spreads through the other worlds, one after another. At the same time, Zhuge Liang Freedom Gundam learns via astrology of an impending disaster. He and his sworn friend Liu Bei Unicorn Gundam take action to save the worlds from this crisis, and begin a journey along with Wukong.\n\nWhat will Wukong Impulse Gundam think as he meets the heroes of each world? Will this youth bring about peace or catastrophe? Now begins a new story of heroes!\n\n(Source: Official Site)", "SD Gundam World Heroes", "SD GUNDAM WORLD HEROES", "SDガンダムワールド ヒーローズ", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8O47QMhy09o", 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/44041/SD_Gundam_World_Heroes" },
