                    { 53406, "", "2 min per ep", new DateTime(2023, 2, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 17, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1014/129578.jpg", 3946, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.08m, null, 3, new DateTime(2022, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "A spin-off chibi anime of Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute!.", "Kagejitsu!", null, "かげじつ!", null, 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/53406/Kagejitsu" },
                    { 53414, "", "26 min per ep", new DateTime(2023, 1, 12, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 6, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1794/131565.jpg", 2296, "R+ - Mild Nudity", 7.4m, null, 2, new DateTime(2022, 12, 15, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "How did this young boy become notorious gentleman thief \"Lupin III\"?\n\nLoosely based on Young Lupin III from the original manga, Lupin Zero will tell a nostalgic, yet brand new original story, finally lifting the veil cast upon Lupin III's humble beginnings. Set during the era in which the original series was first published, the anime depicts Young Lupin III running around the streets of 1960's Japan during the country's economic boom.\n\nA young boy climbs the staircase to villainhood. What was he thinking and what steps did he take? This is the untold origin story of the world's greatest thief. \n\n(Source: TMS Entertainment)", "Lupin Zero", null, "LUPIN ZERO", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6H1Sd53SOhI", 6, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/53414/Lupin_Zero" },
                    { 53421, "Dosanko Gal wa Namara Menkoi was released on Blu-ray in three volumes from April 3, 2024, to June 5, 2024.", "24 min per ep", new DateTime(2024, 3, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 12, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1937/136906.jpg", 4235, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 7.02m, 4, 2, new DateTime(2024, 1, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Having just moved from Tokyo to Hokkaido, high school student Tsubasa Shiki decides to explore the picturesque winter landscape he could never experience in the nation's capital. It only takes a moment for Tsubasa's idealized view of Japan's northernmost prefecture to crumble, as the sheer cold and frigid air quickly overwhelm him. While trying to find the way to his new home, Tsubasa runs into Minami Fuyuki—a talkative and friendly Hokkaido native who, despite the cold, is wearing a short skirt. The girl wastes no time in striking up a conversation, and Tsubasa comes to realize that the winter weather is not all that is too much for him to handle.\n\nThe next day, Tsubasa is shocked to learn that not only is Fuyuki in his class, but her seat is also right next to his. Swept along by Fuyuki's persistent advances, the young man soon becomes captivated by both life in Hokkaido and the beautiful girl determined to get closer to him. As he deepens his relationship with Fuyuki and meets other fashionable girls from his school, Tsubasa finds out that Hokkaido gals truly are adorable.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Dosanko Gal wa Namara Menkoi", "Hokkaido Gals Are Super Adorable!", "道産子ギャルはなまらめんこい", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Slv7WZ_4vS8", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/53421/Dosanko_Gal_wa_Namara_Menkoi" },
                    { 53488, "", "23 min per ep", new DateTime(2024, 3, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 12, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1873/139792.jpg", 5415, "PG-13 - Teens 13 or older", 6.77m, 4, 3, new DateTime(2024, 1, 6, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Finally free of her Blessing's impulses, former Hero Ruti has settled into her idyllic slow life with assassin housemate Tisse in the border town of Zoltan. She's happy to once again be close to her apothecary brother Red, the former Guide of her previous Hero's Party, while he's living his best loved-up life with his partner (and soon-to-be fiancee) Princess Rit. Unfortunately, there's a new Hero on the scene whose fundamentalist interpretation of his Blessing's urges will bring conflict and despair to sleepy Zoltan…\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Shin no Nakama ja Nai to Yuusha no Party wo Oidasareta node, Henkyou de Slow Life suru Koto ni Shimashita 2nd", "Banished From The Hero's Party, I Decided To Live A Quiet Life In The Countryside Season 2", "真の仲間じゃないと勇者のパーティーを追い出されたので、辺境でスローライフすることにしました 2nd", "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JaRvWJr_E_I", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/anime/53488/Shin_no_Nakama_ja_Nai_to_Yuusha_no_Party_wo_Oidasareta_node_Henkyou_de_Slow_Life_suru_Koto_ni_Shimashita_2nd" },
