                    { 18654, "", 4, new DateTime(2000, 2, 16, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/28552.jpg", 47207, null, new DateTime(1998, 4, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A side series of Young Kindaichi's case file.\n\nThis manga consisted of:\n\n   1. \"File 1 The First Case of Young Akechi/Alternative title: Farewell, My Dear Friend\" (FILE1 明智少年最初の事件, \"Fairu Ichi Akechi Shōnen Saisho no Jiken\"?)\n   2. \"File 2 Quartet with Intent to Kill/Alternative title: The Perfect Violinist, Akechi\" (FILE2 殺意の四重奏, \"Fairu Ni Satsui no Karutetto\"?)\n   3. \"File 3 Ghost Swordman Murder Case/Alternative title: The Pride Murder)\" (FILE3 幽霊剣士殺人事件, \"Fairu San Yūrei Kenshi Satsujin Jiken\"?)\n   4. \"Special Story Kengo’s Room\" (スペシャルストーリー 健悟の部屋, \"Supesharu Sutōrī Kengo no Heya\"?)\n\n(Source: wikipedia)", "Akechi Shounen no Karei Naru Jikenbo", null, "明智少年の華麗なる事件簿", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/18654/Akechi_Shounen_no_Karei_Naru_Jikenbo", 1 },
                    { 18668, "", 5, new DateTime(2000, 5, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/61677.jpg", 47210, null, new DateTime(1997, 8, 12, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Side story of the Young Kindaichi Case Files. The cases in this series are:\n\n1. \"File 1 Testimony Puzzle/Alternative title: The Murder Train\" (FILE1 証言パズル, \"Fairu Ichi Shōgen Pazuru\"?)\n2. \"File 2 Killing Poker/Alternative title: Unlucky Men in the Rain\" (FILE2　殺人ポーカー, \"Fairu Ni Satsujin Pōkā\"?)\n3. \"File 3 Dead Person's Checkmate/Alternative title: The Great Chess Player, Akechi\" (FILE3 死者のチェックメイト, \"Fairu San Shisha no Chekkumeito\"?)\n4. \"File 4 Ghost Hotel Murder Case/Alternative title: The Encounter\" (FILE 4 幽霊ホテル殺人事件, \"Fairu Yon Yūrei Hoteru Satsujin Jiken\"?)\n5. \"Special Story Supt.Akechi Morning's Pretty Scenery\" (スペシャルストーリー明智警視　優雅なる朝の風景, \"Supesharu Sutōrī Akechi Keishi Yūga Naru Asa no Fūkei\"?)\n\n(Source: wikipedia)", "Akechi Keishi no Yuuga Naru Jikenbo", null, "明智警視の優雅なる事件簿", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/18668/Akechi_Keishi_no_Yuuga_Naru_Jikenbo", 1 },
