                    { 75719, "Devilman Tai Yami no Teiou was published in English as Devilman VS. Hades by Seven Seas Entertainment from March 13, 2018 to November 27, 2018.", 17, new DateTime(2014, 7, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/131343.jpg", 13767, 6.67m, new DateTime(2012, 11, 13, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After the world ended in the original Devilman, Akira Fudo is in hell, seeking the soul of his beloved Miki while at the same time Doctor Hell is beseeching the underworld for power in order to get his revenge upon the hated Mazinger. Akira sets in motion a chain of events that earn the enmity of Hades himself, who'll stop at nothing to avenge the slights Akira commits against him.", "Devilman Tai Yami no Teiou", "Devilman VS. Hades", "デビルマン対闇の帝王 -DEVILMAN vs HADES-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/75719/Devilman_Tai_Yami_no_Teiou", 3 },
                    { 75723, "", 3, new DateTime(2013, 10, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/131333.jpg", 19547, 5.75m, new DateTime(2013, 6, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Fudou Jun (Devilman Lady) heads to St. Chapel School in order to track down a Devil Beast.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Cutie Honey Tai Devilman Lady", null, "キューティーハニー対デビルマンレディー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/75723/Cutie_Honey_Tai_Devilman_Lady", 1 },
                    { 75749, "Katsute Mahou Shoujo to Aku wa Tekitai shiteita. is incomplete due to the author passing away. The announcement in Gangan Joker noted that the decision to publish the manga's third volume was made after consulting Fujiwara's family. The series was published in English as The Magical Girl and the Evil Lieutenant Used to Be Archenemies by Yen Press as a 3-in-1 omnibus volume on August 27, 2024.", 21, new DateTime(2015, 3, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/131223.jpg", 5504, 7.24m, new DateTime(2013, 9, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga tells the story of Mira, who leads an evil organization trying to take over and destroy everything. Earth is under attack, but a magical girl named Byakuya Mimori stands up to Mira's group. As they face off, something unexpected happens—Mira falls in love with Mimori.\n\n(Source: MAL News)\n\nIncluded one-shot:\nVolume 3: Beauty and the Beast", "Katsute Mahou Shoujo to Aku wa Tekitai shiteita.", "The Magical Girl and the Evil Lieutenant Used to Be Archenemies", "かつて魔法少女と悪は敵対していた。", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/75749/Katsute_Mahou_Shoujo_to_Aku_wa_Tekitai_shiteita", 3 },
                    { 76319, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/191172.jpg", 17518, 6.35m, new DateTime(2012, 6, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Seventeen years after the Walpurgis Night incident, the magical girls of Mitakihara—now in their thirties—have settled into ordinary lives. While her friends have found significant others, Mami Tomoe remains single as she toils away as a temporary worker. Despite being constantly pressured to find love at her age, Mami already struggles with the hurdles that come with taking care of herself, especially controlling her cravings for delicious food and refreshing alcohol. Even so, the freedom that comes with living alone inspires Mami to keep moving forward in her mundane everyday life!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tomoe Mami no Heibon na Nichijou", null, "巴マミの平凡な日常", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/76319/Tomoe_Mami_no_Heibon_na_Nichijou", null },
                    { 77213, "Aldnoah.Zero was published in English as Aldnoah.Zero Season One by Yen Press from December 15, 2015 to September 27, 2016.", 12, new DateTime(2015, 7, 12, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/171877.jpg", 9530, 6.95m, new DateTime(2014, 8, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "During Apollo 17's 1972 space exploration mission to the moon, humanity found a strange hypergate that led to Mars. Upon entering the gate, the astronauts discovered an ancient technology known as \"Aldnoah,\" which would soon cause mass migration to the planet, resulting in the creation of the Vers Empire to govern Mars. Descendants of this new civilization grew to resent Earthlings for their bountiful resources. These feelings led to a declaration of war, an event that ended with the hypergate's destruction in what would come to be known as the infamous \"Heavens Fall.\" The effects were catastrophic, causing the obliteration of the Moon and irreparable damage to Earth through multiple meteor impacts, earthquakes, and tsunamis.\n\nFifteen years later, a ceasefire has established a fragile peace, and Princess Asseylum Vers Allusia arrives on Earth in order to promote lasting friendship between the two races. However, not everyone is satisfied with the abrupt end of the first battle; certain forces have been waiting for such a moment in order to ignite the spark that will lead to a new war. When a group of terrorists attempts to assassinate the young princess, Martian soldiers retaliate by launching an assault, descending from space ready to enslave Earth's inhabitants once and for all.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Aldnoah.Zero", "Aldnoah.Zero Season One", "ALDNOAH.ZERO", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/77213/AldnoahZero", 4 },
                    { 77237, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/133539.jpg", 3648, 7.41m, new DateTime(2014, 5, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Short story about Futaba preparing for the leaders camp.", "Ao Haru Ride: Special Booklet", null, "アオハライド SPECIAL BOOKLET", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/77237/Ao_Haru_Ride__Special_Booklet", null },
