                    { 86129, "The first three novels of the Naruto Hiden Series were published in English by VIZ Media from November 3, 2015, to May 3, 2016. It was also released in Polish by J.P. Fantastica from July 27, 2016, to February 14, 2019.", 49, new DateTime(2015, 7, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/175457.jpg", 1564, 7.73m, new DateTime(2015, 2, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A series of Naruto novels. Naruto's allies and enemies take center stage in these fast-paced adventures, which each volume focusing on a particular clanmate, ally, team...or villain.\n\n1. Kakashi Hiden: Hyouten no Ikazuchi (Kakashi Secret Legend: Lightning in the Frozen Sky) [Higashiyama Akira]\n2. Shikamaru Hiden: Yami no Shijima ni Ukabu Kumo [Yano Takashi]\n3. Sakura Hiden: Shiren, Harukaze ni Nosete [Hinata Shou]\n4. Konohagakure Hiden: Shuugen Biyori [Oosaki Tomohito]\n5. Gaara Hiden: Sajin Gensou [Ukyo Kodachi]\n6. Akatsuki Hiden: Sakimidareru Aku no Hana [Shin Towada]", "Naruto Hiden Series", null, "NARUTO秘伝シリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/86129/Naruto_Hiden_Series", 6 },
