                    { 88589, null, 31, new DateTime(2016, 8, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/154511.jpg", 46931, null, new DateTime(2014, 5, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Akechi Keibu no Jikenbo", "The Akechi Files", "明智警部の事件簿", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/88589/Akechi_Keibu_no_Jikenbo", 5 },
                    { 88679, "", 4, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/154677.jpg", 4839, 7.29m, new DateTime(2015, 2, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Collection of four short stories related to the Kurama-yama arc.\n\nFirst narrated by Jirou, tells of his relationship with Suirou and his first encounter with the thunder beast. The second, narrated by Suirou, is about his relationship with Kurama (Shinjurou) and the events that led to his injury. The third is about Nanami trying to figure out whether or not Tomoe really said he liked her at the end of the Kurama-Yama arc. And the last one is about Botanmaru befriending a small tenma.", "Kamisama Hajimemashita: Kurama-yama Yawa", null, "神様はじめました 鞍馬山夜話", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/88679/Kamisama_Hajimemashita__Kurama-yama_Yawa", 1 },
                    { 88923, "Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on November 7, 2013. Overlap has released a revised and illustrated version of the series since June 25, 2015 under its Overlap Bunko label. The series was published digitally in English as Arifureta: From Commonplace to World's Strongest by J-Novel Club from May 6, 2017 to March 24, 2023, and in print by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint from February 6, 2018 to October 24, 2023.", 92, new DateTime(2022, 9, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/159433.jpg", 1850, 7.68m, new DateTime(2015, 6, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Seventeen-year-old Hajime Nagumo is your average, everyday otaku. However, his simple life of pulling all-nighters and sleeping in school is suddenly turned upside down when he, along with the rest of his class, is summoned to a fantasy world! They're treated like heroes and tasked with the duty of saving the human race from utter extinction. But what should have been any otaku's wet dream quickly turns into Hajime's nightmare. While the rest of his class are blessed with godlike powers, Hajime's job, Synergist, only has a single transmutation skill. Ridiculed and bullied by his classmates for being weak, he soon finds himself in despair. Will he be able to survive in this dangerous world of monsters and demons with only a glorified blacksmith's level of strength?\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou", "Arifureta: From Commonplace to World's Strongest", "ありふれた職業で世界最強", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/88923/Arifureta_Shokugyou_de_Sekai_Saikyou", 13 },
                    { 88930, "Youjo Senki has been published in English as The Saga of Tanya the Evil by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since December 19, 2017.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/155214.jpg", 217, 8.4m, new DateTime(2013, 10, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Tanya Degurechaff is a soldier who has the appearance of an innocent young girl. But behind her cute facade lies the soul of a ruthless salaryman who challenged \"Being X\"—the self-proclaimed God who reincarnated the man into an industrial world of magic. By doing this, Being X hopes to prove that, if the situation were dire enough, even a non-believer like this man would pray for God's help.\n\nOpposing Being X's desires to make her suffer, Tanya enlists in the military with the hope of living a peaceful life. She manages to impress the higher-ups with her aptitude for war, swiftly rising through the ranks. However, her country soon participates in the ongoing world war, quickly crushing her dream. In an attempt to return to her calm she starts using any merciless means to obliterate her opponents. Thus begins the saga of Tanya the Evil and the Empire as they seek world domination.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Youjo Senki", "The Saga of Tanya the Evil", "幼女戦記", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/88930/Youjo_Senki", null },
                    { 89357, "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e was published digitally in English as Classroom of the Elite by Seven Seas Entertainment from February 7, 2019 to May 12, 2022, and in print from May 7, 2019 to June 28, 2022.", 110, new DateTime(2019, 9, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/177958.jpg", 35, 8.82m, new DateTime(2015, 5, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Receiving funding from the government to nurture the next generation's hopefuls, Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School brings together the brightest youth of Japan onto a single campus. At this seemingly perfect institution, the reserved Kiyotaka Ayanokouji arrives as an incoming member of class 1-D, where he befriends one of his classmates, the antisocial Suzune Horikita.\n\nAt first, his peers revel in the academy's leisurely lifestyle, taking advantage of all of its state-of-the-art facilities. Soon enough, however, the facade of Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School gives way to its true nature—only the top scoring classes can fully utilize the school's offerings, and Class D is the furthest from such a status. Standing at the bottom of the hierarchy, Class D houses all of the school's \"worst\" students.\n\nFollowing this rude awakening, Ayanokouji, Horikita, and the rest of Class D must overcome their differences and clash against other classes in order to climb to the coveted position of Class A by any means necessary.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e", "Classroom of the Elite", "ようこそ実力至上主義の教室へ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89357/Youkoso_Jitsuryoku_Shijou_Shugi_no_Kyoushitsu_e", 14 },
                    { 89364, "", 9, new DateTime(2013, 10, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/157878.jpg", 14948, 6.59m, new DateTime(2012, 6, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Showcasing delicious sweets and a colorful atmosphere, Café Grief Seed welcomes a variety of patrons through its doors. On a whim, Madoka Kaname and her friend Sayaka Miki visit the restaurant after seeing it being featured in a magazine. They quickly befriend the three employees of the establishment and eventually become interested in working at the café.\n\nSeizing the opportunity, the apathetic store manager Kyuubey extends a job offer to Madoka and Sayaka, believing that their hiring will improve workplace efficiency. However, when waitress Homura Akemi eavesdrops on the cat-like creature, she learns that Kyuubey has ulterior motives behind the contract. Regretful of having made the wrong decision herself, Homura is determined to prevent Madoka from being deceived by the battlefield that is customer service!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Café☆Griefseed e Youkoso!", "Welcome to Cafe Griefseed!", "カフェ☆グリーフシードへようこそ!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89364/Café☆Griefseed_e_Youkoso", 1 },
                    { 89365, null, null, new DateTime(2016, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/157041.jpg", 36356, null, new DateTime(2012, 12, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Fuwatto Madoka", null, "ふわっとまどか", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89365/Fuwatto_Madoka", 3 },
                    { 89366, "", null, new DateTime(2016, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/157043.jpg", 36357, null, new DateTime(2013, 10, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A 4-koma about the Kaname family.", "Kaname-ke", null, "かなめけ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89366/Kaname-ke", 2 },
                    { 89610, "", null, new DateTime(2004, 5, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/157127.jpg", 36418, null, new DateTime(2003, 8, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Set thirty years after the original Kekkou Kamen, Spartan Institute of Higher Education is back to its old tricks under the reign of the son of Toenail of Satan. There a new Kekkou Kamen appears.", "Kekkou Kamen P", null, "けっこう仮面P", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89610/Kekkou_Kamen_P", 2 },
                    { 89734, "Dragon Ball Super has been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since May 2, 2017. It has also been simulpub through MANGA Plus. The series has also been published in French by Glénat since April 5, 2017; in Italian by Edizioni Star Comics since April 26, 2017; in German by Carlsen Manga since May 2, 2017; and in Spanish by Planeta Cómic in comic issues since March 2017 and in volumes since October 17, 2017.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/176933.jpg", 4699, 7.31m, new DateTime(2015, 6, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Having defeated Boo, Goku is starting to get bored with his life on Earth. His wife, Chi-chi, wants him to get a job, but all he wants to do is train and fight stronger enemies. Elsewhere in the universe, the God of Destruction, Beerus, and his attendant Whis are traveling from planet to planet in search of food and entertainment. After blowing up some hapless victims, Beerus is reminded of a man from his dreams with the moniker \"Super Saiyan God,\" or something like that... The God of Destruction sets his sights on Earth to track down this mysterious man! Maybe this will give Goku something to do?\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Dragon Ball Super", "Dragon Ball Super", "ドラゴンボール超〈スーパー〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89734/Dragon_Ball_Super", null },
                    { 89768, "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! Spin-off: Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Bakuen wo! has been published in English as Konosuba: An Explosion on This Wonderful World! by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since December 24, 2019.", 30, new DateTime(2019, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/156944.jpg", 587, 8.1m, new DateTime(2014, 6, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "My name is...\n\nOne year before a certain useless goddess and NEET extraordinaire hit the scene, Megumin, the \"Greatest Genius of the Crimson Magic Clan,\" is hard at work. Ever since a life-changing encounter in her youth, the young wizard has dedicated her every waking moment to the pursuit of the ultimate offensive magic, Explosion! (Well...every moment not spent hustling food from her self-proclaimed rival.) And while the big sister's away, the little one will play. On a routine trip into the woods, Megumin's little sister, Komekko, finds a strange black kitten. Little does she know that this cat plays a key role in unsealing a Dark God's tomb...\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! Spin-off: Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Bakuen wo!", "Konosuba: An Explosion on This Wonderful World!", "この素晴らしい世界に祝福を！スピンオフ この素晴らしい世界に爆焔を！", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89768/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Shukufuku_wo_Spin-off__Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Bakuen_wo", 5 },
                    { 89960, "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu: Dai-3 Shou - Truth of Zero adapts volumes four through nine of the light novel series. The manga was published in English as Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-, Chapter 3: Truth of Zero by Yen Press from October 31, 2017, to December 15, 2020. It was also released in Polish by Waneko from April 26, 2019, to January 12, 2021.", 55, new DateTime(2019, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/188948.jpg", 575, 8.1m, new DateTime(2015, 5, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Royal Capital, the city of Lugunica, has been in disarray ever since losing its king. Now without a figurehead, the royal family collapses, and the government must immediately hold an election to decide on his successor. Subaru Natsuki, who unknowingly saved the insignia that made Emilia a Royal Election candidate, accompanies her to an important meeting.\n\nWhile in the capital, Emilia insists that Subaru stay behind and repose following the demon beast attack, despite the fact he would do anything besides that. However, when Subaru sees Emilia being ill-treated by both the citizens and her fellow candidates, will he be able to keep his promise to the one he loves most?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu: Dai-3 Shou - Truth of Zero", "Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-, Chapter 3: Truth of Zero", "Re：ゼロから始める異世界生活 第三章 Truth of Zero", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/89960/Re_Zero_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu__Dai-3_Shou_-_Truth_of_Zero", 11 },
                    { 90016, "", 27, new DateTime(2016, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/172442.jpg", 36515, null, new DateTime(2012, 6, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Upon escaping into a parallel world, Homura Akemi discovers that she has become a kindergarten student! The differences do not stop there: at Mitakihara Kindergarten, Mami Tomoe is a teacher; Madoka Kaname is another kindergarten student; and Kyuubey is the principal of the school. Despite the bizarre changes in this world, Homura believes this is a rare opportunity to finally make intimate memories with her close friend. But with frequent unexpected signs threatening to lead her astray, Homura must continue her duty to protect Madoka from becoming a magical girl—all while in the body of a five-year-old!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Mitakihara Youchien Mahou-gumi", null, "みたきはら幼稚園まほう組", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90016/Mitakihara_Youchien_Mahou-gumi", 3 },
                    { 90065, "Keibu Zenigata concluded with the suspension of the Lupin Sansei Official Magazine, following the 50th anniversary of Lupin III.", 45, new DateTime(2017, 12, 7, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/172507.jpg", 36522, null, new DateTime(2010, 10, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Lupin III spin-off about Kouichi Zenigata.", "Keibu Zenigata", "Captain Zenigata", "警部銭形", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90065/Keibu_Zenigata", 12 },
                    { 90117, "Tsuki ga Michibiku Isekai Douchuu has been published digitally in English as Tsukimichi: Moonlit Fantasy by AlphaPolis through Alpha Manga. The volumes have also been published digitally by AlphaPolis since July 28, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/183227.jpg", 1354, 7.78m, new DateTime(2015, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "High school student Misumi Makoto is called into a fantasy world by the god Tsukuyomi, in order to be a hero. However, powerful others in this world aren't as thrilled to have him there, and they kick him to the edge of the world just as Tsukuyomi declares that he must leave Makoto to find his own way. Now it's up to Makoto to find his own way!\n\n(Source: MangaHelpers)", "Tsuki ga Michibiku Isekai Douchuu", "Tsukimichi: Moonlit Fantasy", "月が導く異世界道中", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90117/Tsuki_ga_Michibiku_Isekai_Douchuu", null },
                    { 90118, "Tsuki ga Michibiku Isekai Douchuu has been published digitally in English as Tsukimichi: Moonlit Fantasy by Hanashi Media since March 30, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/158263.jpg", 819, 7.96m, new DateTime(2013, 5, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "High school student Misumi Makoto is called to a fantasy world by the god Tsukuyomi in order to become a hero. However, powerful others in this world aren't as thrilled to have him there, and they kick him to the edge of the world just as Tsukuyomi declares that he must leave Makoto to find his own way. Now it's up to Makoto to find his own way!\n\n(Source: MangaHelpers)", "Tsuki ga Michibiku Isekai Douchuu", "Tsukimichi: Moonlit Fantasy", "月が導く異世界道中", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90118/Tsuki_ga_Michibiku_Isekai_Douchuu", null },
                    { 90180, "", 18, new DateTime(2015, 6, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/159411.jpg", 8189, 7.04m, new DateTime(2014, 11, 6, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "4-koma spin-off of the Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka series.", "DanMachi 4-koma: Somosomo Dungeon ni Moguru no ga Machigai de wa Nai Darou ka", null, "ダンまち4コマ そもそもダンジョンにもぐるのが間違いではないだろうか", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90180/DanMachi_4-koma__Somosomo_Dungeon_ni_Moguru_no_ga_Machigai_de_wa_Nai_Darou_ka", 1 },
                    { 90309, "Mahou Shoujo Madoka★Magica: Majuu-hen was published in English as Puella Magi Madoka Magica: Wraith Arc by Yen Press from November 23, 2021, to June 21, 2022. It has also been published in Turkish as Büyücü Kız Madoka Magica: Hayaletlerin Ayaklanışı by Komik Şeyler since June 2022.", 9, new DateTime(2016, 10, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/4/260579.jpg", 1481, 7.75m, new DateTime(2015, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Invisible to humans, wraiths are beings that feed on human emotions and cause chaos wherever they go. Magical girls must use the power they have gained in exchange for having one wish granted to protect humans from these wraiths. A group of magical girls in Mitakihara have been giving their all to keep the town safe, but two of their members, Sayaka Miki and Kyouko Sakura, cannot seem to get along. Their leader, Mami Tomoe, hopes that they can work together in time, but worries that their quarrels will begin to affect their magical girl duties.\n\nJoining this group of magical girls is Homura Akemi, who has recently transferred to Mitakihara Middle School. But Homura knows more about magical girls than she lets on, as well as the truth behind the current state of their world.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Mahou Shoujo Madoka★Magica: Majuu-hen", "Puella Magi Madoka Magica: Wraith Arc", "魔法少女まどか★マギカ [魔獣編]", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90309/Mahou_Shoujo_Madoka★Magica__Majuu-hen", 3 },
                    { 90322, "", 4, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/158910.jpg", 4700, 7.31m, new DateTime(2012, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Four short stories which appeared in the Nisemonogatari: Anime Complete Guidebook.\n\n1. Hitagi Neck\n2. Karen Arm-leg\n3. Tsukihi Eternal\n4. Shinobu House", "Nisemonogatari Short Stories", null, "偽物語アニメコンプリートガイドブック", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90322/Nisemonogatari_Short_Stories", null },
                    { 90324, "", 8, new DateTime(2014, 5, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/158927.jpg", 5505, 7.24m, new DateTime(2014, 4, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Special booklets bundled with the first press release of the 1st and 2nd Blu-ray and DVD volumes of Onimonogatari anime. They contain short advertisement manuscripts published in Yomiuri Shinbum along with short kakioroshi.\n\nVolume 1\n1. Tsubasa Board\n2. Mayoi Castle\n3. Shinobu Science\n4. Suruga Palace\n\nVolume 2\n1. Nadeko Mirror\n2. Hitagi Salamander\n3. Yotsugi Future\n4. Ougi Travel", "Monogatari Series: Second Season - Shinbun Koukoku Zenshuu", null, "〈物語〉シリーズ セカンドシーズン新聞広告全集", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90324/Monogatari_Series__Second_Season_-_Shinbun_Koukoku_Zenshuu", 2 },
                    { 90408, "", 8, new DateTime(1993, 10, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/158628.jpg", 36648, null, new DateTime(1990, 10, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In the future, advanced robotics has created heavy robots (\"labors\") for use in a variety of functions: construction, fire-fighting, military, and more. However, though the robots are only machines, their operators are also only human—and humans sometimes turn to crime. Since a heavy labor unit can be a dangerous weapon, the police of the future are set to fight fire with fire, using advanced patrol labor units, \"patlabors.\" This is the story of the Second Special Vehicles Division, a motley crew of patlabor policemen and women doing their best to fight crime and live a normal life.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Kidou Keisatsu Patlabor", null, "機動警察パトレイバー", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90408/Kidou_Keisatsu_Patlabor", 5 },
                    { 90531, "Naruto Shinden Series was published in English by VIZ Media from November 1, 2016 to March 7, 2017.", 11, new DateTime(2015, 11, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/190847.jpg", 276, 8.33m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story will focus on the brothers who have eyes that see through to the truth and who live on the threshold of hope and despair. Itachi's past and Sasuke's future will be made clear.", "Naruto Shinden Series", "Naruto: Itachi's Story", "NARUTO -ナルト- 真伝シリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90531/Naruto_Shinden_Series", 3 },
                    { 90585, "", 40, new DateTime(2013, 4, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/286587.jpg", 4925, 7.29m, new DateTime(2012, 3, 6, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A murder case for the 20th anniversary for the manga of Kindaichi.", "Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo: 20-shuunen Kinen Series", "Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo: 20th Anniversary Commemoration Series", "金田一少年の事件簿 20周年記念シリーズ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90585/Kindaichi_Shounen_no_Jikenbo__20-shuunen_Kinen_Series", 5 },
                    { 90687, "[Shinyaku] Mahou Shoujo Oriko★Magica: Sadness Prayer has been published in English as [New Testament] Puella Magi Oriko Magica: Sadness Prayer by Yen Press from November 22, 2016 to September 18, 2018.", 24, new DateTime(2017, 8, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/159418.jpg", 11048, 6.85m, new DateTime(2013, 11, 7, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Enduring the fallout of her father's political scandal and his following suicide, Oriko Mikuni makes a desperate wish to Kyuubey: to discover her purpose in life. With the \"gift\" of foresight as a magical girl, Oriko learns that only further despair awaits her, culminating in the destruction of Mitakihara City. To effectively prevent this unfortunate outcome, the fate of a familiar girl must be changed.\n\nThis revelation serves as the foundation for Oriko's new goal to battle \"witches\" and bring unwavering peace to the world. However, as Oriko sets her plans in motion, ongoing affairs begin to interfere, presenting unexpected challenges along the way. Having already faced many hardships, Oriko is resolved to overcome such obstacles and strive toward a better future—even if it means sacrificing the lives of others.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "[Shinyaku] Mahou Shoujo Oriko★Magica: Sadness Prayer", "[New Testament] Puella Magi Oriko Magica: Sadness Prayer", "［新約］魔法少女おりこ★マギカ～sadness prayer～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90687/Shinyaku_Mahou_Shoujo_Oriko★Magica__Sadness_Prayer", 4 },
                    { 90757, "", 14, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/159298.jpg", 4471, 7.33m, new DateTime(2008, 7, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Kenji was born in 1960. At that time, Japan was running toward the future. In the time of the economic growth, Japanese children saw a lot of cultural movement. Some are gone, some remain. \"20th century boys\" this based on that chaos. Kentaro Takekuma, who was born in the same year as Kenji, is going to reexamine the culture of that period.\n\nThis is the best guidebook to understand the background of 20th Century Boys.", "20 Seiki Shounen Tanteidan", "20th Century Detective Boys", "20世紀少年探偵団", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90757/20_Seiki_Shounen_Tanteidan", 1 },
                    { 90870, "", null, new DateTime(2016, 10, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/278721.jpg", 3587, 7.42m, new DateTime(2015, 7, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Durarara!! spin-off series that takes place after the original, starring Orihara Izaya as the main character.\n\nAn man shows up in a town far from Tokyo. All he does is facilitate the flow of information, and nudge people on the back. He is an informant; that is what this man boasts of himself. Whether or not the title is appropriate for what he does, one thing is certain: he has the power to obtain a great volume of information. He is not an ally of justice, but neither is he an abettor of villainy. He is simply unwaveringly honest to his own desires.\n\n\"Humans.\" Earnestly, he loves every one of the assortment this word encapsulates. He merely loves. Even if it causes the object of his love to break. Because this informant can equally even love broken humans.\n\n(Source: popsiclete blog)", "Orihara Izaya to Series", null, "折原臨也と シリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90870/Orihara_Izaya_to_Series", 2 },
                    { 90883, "", 17, new DateTime(1982, 1, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/159913.jpg", 36765, null, new DateTime(1980, 12, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In order to help her father solve mysterious crimes, the student Susumi Fuji takes the identity of Maboroshi Panty.", "Maboroshi Panty", null, "まぼろしパンティー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90883/Maboroshi_Panty", 3 },
                    { 90884, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/160084.jpg", 36766, null, new DateTime(2011, 6, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Taking place many years after the original manga where a new Kekkou Kamen, whose secret identity is a new teacher in a new school owned by the remaining factions of the Toenail of Satan.", "The Excellent: Kekkou Kamen Gaiden", null, "THE エクセレント～けっこう仮面外伝～", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90884/The_Excellent__Kekkou_Kamen_Gaiden", null },
                    { 90885, null, 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/159916.jpg", 36767, null, new DateTime(2013, 1, 15, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Mazinger Z Tai Kekkou Kamen", null, "マジンガーZ対けっこう仮面", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90885/Mazinger_Z_Tai_Kekkou_Kamen", null },
                    { 90908, "", 13, new DateTime(2015, 8, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/162056.jpg", 36776, null, new DateTime(2014, 9, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The second part of Fuwari! Don Patch, a spin-off of Bobobo-bo Bo-Bobo starring Don Patch.", "Honnori! Don Patch", null, "ほんのり!どんぱっち", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90908/Honnori_Don_Patch", 1 },
                    { 90993, "", 19, new DateTime(2017, 3, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/167490.jpg", 2990, 7.49m, new DateTime(2015, 8, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Twenty-five-year-old Kakushidate Yakusuke suffers from the fate of constantly stumbling into various crime scenes and ending up being the main suspect.\n\nHis last resort: Okitegami Kyouko the \"Quickest Detective.\" However, Kyouko suffers from a strange case of amnesia; whenever she falls asleep, she forgets everything that happened the previous day, making her solve the mysteries within one day.", "Okitegami Kyouko no Bibouroku", "The Memorandum of Kyoko Okitegami", "掟上今日子の備忘録", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/90993/Okitegami_Kyouko_no_Bibouroku", 5 },
                    { 91037, "Enen no Shouboutai was published in English as Fire Force by Kodansha Comics USA from November 8, 2016 to October 3, 2023, and as omnibus volumes since August 27, 2024. The series has also been published in Italian by Panini Comics under the Planet Manga imprint since May 5, 2017, in French by Kana since May 19, 2017, in Spanish by Norma Editorial since June 23, 2017, and in Polish by Waneko since December 12, 2019.", 305, new DateTime(2022, 2, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/178996.jpg", 1475, 7.75m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Still reeling from the childhood trauma of losing his family to a blaze, Shinra Kusakabe endures both the blessing and curse of being a third-generation pyrokinetic: a person gifted with the ability to freely control fire.\n\nMeanwhile, the Infernals—first-generation pyrokinetics who spontaneously combust into flaming, demonic creatures—ravage the streets of Tokyo. After he is recognized for his abilities, Shinra joins Special Fire Force Company 8, one of many fire brigades developed to combat these Infernals.\n\nAlthough working with the Fire Force seems to have fulfilled a calling, Shinra learns that becoming a hero is not as easy as it seems. Infernal sightings are worsening across the country, and his own fellow brigadiers struggle to unite against these threats. To make matters worse, Shinra's past returns to haunt him after he confronts a mysterious cult. As he endeavors to reach the truth, Shinra soon finds himself in the middle of a conspiracy that aims to engulf the world in flames.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Enen no Shouboutai", "Fire Force", "炎炎ノ消防隊", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91037/Enen_no_Shouboutai", 34 },
                    { 91209, "", 21, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/160222.jpg", 1108, 7.85m, new DateTime(2013, 7, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Novel of the second Gintama movie, written by Oosaki Tomohito, the same author of Ginpachi-sensei.\n\nWhat would have happened if the Shiroyasha never existed?\n\nEdo is thrown to chaos by a mysterious cause. Sakata Gintoki, now lives in a world where the future has changed, without him. What has happened to the Yorozuya?\n\nGintoki, who is now a ghost of the past, must once again carry the burden in order to save his friends. He must finish the biggest job ever, which may be the final job of Yorozuya.", "Gekijouban Gintama: Kanketsu-hen - Yorozuya yo Eien Nare", null, "劇場版 銀魂 完結篇 万事屋よ永遠なれ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91209/Gekijouban_Gintama__Kanketsu-hen_-_Yorozuya_yo_Eien_Nare", 1 },
                    { 91443, "", null, new DateTime(1997, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/160508.jpg", 36870, null, new DateTime(1996, 6, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "It is the year After Colony 195, and war between the Space Colonies and Earth has begun. To give the colonies an edge, they send 5 young soldiers, trained to perfection, to earth in the most powerful of Mobile Suits-Gundams. With their arrival, the tide of the war changes as they battle against the Earth forces and the Colonies of their origin.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Shin Kidou Senki Gundam Wing", null, "新機動戦記ガンダムＷ〈ウイング〉", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91443/Shin_Kidou_Senki_Gundam_Wing", 5 },
                    { 91444, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/160509.jpg", 36871, null, new DateTime(2007, 9, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After Colony 196\n\nOne year has passed since the war between Earth and its colonies ended. Heero, Duo, Trowa and Quatre bid farewell to their Gundams and jettison them to the sun. Relena Darlian is now the deputy minister of the Earth Sphere Unified Nation. But as the Gundam pilots are adjusting to the peace on Earth, Relena is kidnapped and a new threat appears, led by Marimeia Khushrenada—daughter of the late dictator Treize Khushrenada and heir to the Barton Foundation. To make matters more complicated, Gundam Nataku pilot Wufei has sided with this faction. The Gundam pilots must recover their mobile suits and once again engage in battle before Marimeia's forces succeed on their bid for global domination.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Shin Kidou Senki Gundam Wing: Endless Waltz", null, "新機動戦記ガンダムＷ〈ウイング〉 Endless Waltz", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91444/Shin_Kidou_Senki_Gundam_Wing__Endless_Waltz", 2 },
                    { 91562, "", 12, new DateTime(2016, 12, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/160919.jpg", 12538, 6.76m, new DateTime(2015, 2, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Seeking for revenge, Count Saazbaum, a Martian, attacked the Earth. Later on, the war between the Terrans and Martians ended with Earth's Terrans gaining the victory. However, nineteen months later, the battle between them continues. Martians still continues to invade the Earth and the Terrans to protect it.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Aldnoah.Zero 2nd Season", null, "ALDNOAH.ZERO 2nd Season", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91562/AldnoahZero_2nd_Season", 5 },
                    { 91706, "", null, new DateTime(2012, 10, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/161284.jpg", 36913, null, new DateTime(2012, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In A.G. 101 (the 101st year of the Advanced Generation calendar) a mysterious entity known only as \"UE\", or \"unknown enemy\", attacks and destroys the space colony Angel. This brutal attack becomes infamous as the \"The Day the Angel Fell\", and marks the beginning of humanity's war for survival. \n\nThe series begins in A.G. 108 when the UE attack the space colony Ovan, where Flit Asuno lives with his mother. Flit's mother is killed by the UE, and in her belongings (in an object called a \"AGE Device\") he discovers the blueprints for a powerful weapon from the past - the ancient messiah named \"Gundam.\" \n\nFrom these blueprints, Flit spends the next several years studying engineering at an Earth Federation base on the Nora space colony and designing the AGE-1 Gundam. Seven years later, in A.G. 115, Flit completes the Gundam, just as the UE attack Nora. Flit and his lineage's battle piloting the AGE-1 to protect mankind is about to begin. \n\n(Source: GoodAnime.net)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam AGE", "Mobile Suit Gundam AGE", "機動戦士ガンダムＡＧＥ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91706/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_AGE", 5 },
                    { 91734, "", null, new DateTime(1997, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/161336.jpg", 36921, null, new DateTime(1995, 8, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In the Year FC 60, much of mankind inhabits space colonies which orbit the Earth. Dominance over the colonies is decided once every four years by a large tournament in which each nation sends a single representative to fight the others with a giant robot called a Gundam. Domon Kashuu is selected to represent Neo-Japan in one of these tournaments, but he fights less to ensure his nation's victory than to find his brother, who has been blamed for the deaths of Domon's parents and the disappearance of a very dangerous weapon, the Dark Gundam or Devil Gundam.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Kidou Butouden G Gundam", null, "機動武闘伝Gガンダム", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91734/Kidou_Butouden_G_Gundam", 3 },
                    { 91971, "Fairy Tail Gaiden was published in English by Kodansha Comics USA from December 6, 2016, to October 23, 2018. It was also released in Brazilian Portuguese by Editora JBC from December 8, 2017, to April 20, 2018; and in Spanish by Norma Editorial from March 23, 2018, to October 31, 2018.", 52, new DateTime(2016, 9, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/171669.jpg", 6079, 7.19m, new DateTime(2015, 7, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Fairy Tail Gaiden is a trilogy detailing the adventures of Sting and Rogue, Gajeel and Levy, and Laxus and the Thunder Tribe in separate volumes.\n\n1. Kengami no Souryuu (Twin Dragons of Sabertooth)\n2. Rhodonite\n3. Raigo Issen (Lightning Gods)", "Fairy Tail Gaiden", null, "FAIRY TAIL外伝", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/91971/Fairy_Tail_Gaiden", 3 },
                    { 92131, "", 7, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/164766.jpg", 3498, 7.43m, new DateTime(2015, 8, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Boruto is the son of the 7th Hokage Naruto who completely rejects his father. Behind this, he has feelings of wanting to surpass Naruto, who is respected as a hero. He ends up meeting his father's friend Sasuke, and requests to become... his apprentice!? The curtain on the story of the new generation written by Masashi Kishimoto rises!\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Boruto: Naruto the Movie", null, "BORUTO -NARUTO THE MOVIE-", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92131/Boruto__Naruto_the_Movie", 1 },
                    { 92203, "Baccano! was simultaneously published in English by Yen Press on the same day as the Japanese release. It was published in print from January 30, 2018 to May 22, 2018.", 22, new DateTime(2017, 1, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/172600.jpg", 2983, 7.49m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Aboard the Advenna Avis in 1711, a group of alchemists summon a demon in the hopes of gaining eternal life. The demon gives them an elixir of immortality and the method of ending their existence by \"devouring\" one another. Soon after, one among them begins to devour his companions. Realizing the danger posed by staying together, they scatter across the globe.\n\nCenturies later in 1930's America, a certain federal investigator tries his best to combat the rise of organized crime during Prohibition, send a particularly infuriating terrorist to Alcatraz, and catch an outrageous thief duo. Meanwhile, the transcontinental train, the Flying Pussyfoot, begins its trail of blood across the country.\n\nIn 2002, a small group of the original Advenna Avis alchemists are on a journey to find the rest of their fellow immortals. However, there is one companion they did not expect to meet again.\n\nSeemingly unrelated events, from a sleepy Italian city in the early 1700's to a modern luxury cruise ship traveling across the Pacific, reveal themselves to be far more connected than anyone could imagine...\n\n(Source: Wikipedia, MAL Rewrite)", "Baccano!", "Baccano!", "BACCANO!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92203/Baccano", 3 },
                    { 92286, "Special one-shot included in the Naruto: Hiden - Zai no Sho - Official Movie Book (NARUTO 秘伝・在の書 オフィシャルムービーBOOK) guidebook, which was distributed exclusively at the screening of the movie.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/171855.jpg", 7826, 7.06m, new DateTime(2015, 8, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story shows Naruto Uzumaki's Hokage inauguration day.", "Boruto: Naruto the Movie Tokubetsu Bangai-hen - Naruto ga Hokage ni Natta Hi", null, "BORUTO -NARUTO THE MOVIE- 特別番外編 ナルトが火影になった日", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92286/Boruto__Naruto_the_Movie_Tokubetsu_Bangai-hen_-_Naruto_ga_Hokage_ni_Natta_Hi", null },
                    { 92299, "While Chapter 83 of Berserk, \"Shinen no Kami (2),\" was initially released in Issue 14 of the 1996 Young Animal magazine, it was omitted from the Volume 13 release of Berserk at the author's request (he felt that the chapter gave away too much information too early in the story), making the magazine issue a collector's item.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/162254.jpg", 153, 8.49m, new DateTime(1996, 7, 11, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "When Griffith realizes that he will no longer be able to actualize his dream in his debilitated state, he wishes upon his Crimson Behelit as a final resort. Doing so triggers the \"Eclipse\"—a ritual in which the invoker sacrifices something of significance in exchange for great power. Griffith ultimately chooses to offer his legion of devoted followers, the Band of the Hawk.\n\nSubsequently, Griffith transcends to the Abyss where he faces an enormous entity akin to God. The being introduces itself as the Idea of Evil. Coveted into existence by humanity's collective subconsciousness, it has gone on to manipulate the lives of humans throughout all world events.\n\nAs Griffith now exists as a part of the human consciousness, present in the Abyss, the Idea of Evil eerily declares \"Your desire is my desire... May your actions bring pain or salvation to mankind. Do as you will, Chosen One.\" With that, Griffith harvests the pain of his comrades to transform into his ideal self.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Berserk: Shinen no Kami 2", null, "ベルセルク 深淵の神②", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92299/Berserk__Shinen_no_Kami_2", null },
                    { 92625, "Sword Art Online Alternative: Gun Gale Online was published in English by Yen Press from November 14, 2017 to January 25, 2022.", 20, new DateTime(2021, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/184352.jpg", 5062, 7.27m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story follows Karen Kohiruimaki, a 183-centimeter-tall (6-foot-tall) college student who's insecure about her height, and is bad at dealing with people in the real world. She enters the world of Gun Gale Online with her avatar, Ren, who is less than 150 centimeters (5 feet) tall and wears all pink. She meets a beautiful, brown-skinned female player who goes by Pitohui. They hit it off, but one day Pitohui pressures her to participate in \"Squad Jam,\" a team battle royale variation of the Bullet of Bullets tournament.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Sword Art Online Alternative: Gun Gale Online", "Sword Art Online Alternative: Gun Gale Online", "ソードアート・オンライン オルタナティブ ガンゲイル・オンライン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92625/Sword_Art_Online_Alternative__Gun_Gale_Online", 4 },
                    { 92826, null, 12, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/163494.jpg", 10394, 6.9m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Shinmai Maou no Testament: Light!", "The Testament of Sister New Devil", "新妹魔王の契約者〈テスタメント〉 LIGHT!", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92826/Shinmai_Maou_no_Testament__Light", 1 },
                    { 92833, "", 30, new DateTime(2007, 6, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/4/163524.jpg", 37265, null, new DateTime(2004, 5, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Based on the Toei anime version of the 70's, crossover with Devilman, Mazinger Z, Great Mazinger, Grendizer, and Cutie Honey.", "Dynamic Heroes", null, "ダイナミックヒーローズ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92833/Dynamic_Heroes", 4 },
                    { 92838, "", 5, new DateTime(2011, 12, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/171859.jpg", 37267, null, new DateTime(2011, 8, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Crossover manga beteen Maou Dante and Getter Robo G.", "Maou Dante Tai Getter Robo G", "Demon Lord Dante vs. Getter Robo G", "魔王ダンテ対ゲッターロボG", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92838/Maou_Dante_Tai_Getter_Robo_G", 1 },
                    { 92839, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/163529.jpg", 17322, 6.37m, new DateTime(1998, 8, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Crossover one-shot between Mazinkaiser and Shin Getter Robo. It was included in Immortal Super Robot Encyclopedia (不滅のスーパーロボット大全).\n\nThe manga begins with the Mazinger Z and Great Mazinger fighting against an alien machine after the Diana A and Venus A have been taken down.\n\n(Source: Mazinger Wikia)", "Mazinkaiser Tai Shin Getter Robo", null, "マジンカイザー対真ゲッターロボ", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92839/Mazinkaiser_Tai_Shin_Getter_Robo", null },
                    { 92905, "The chapters were released to commemorate the theatrical opening of the live-action Bakuman. film. They were collected in the artbook Eiga Bakuman. Obata Takeshi Illustration Works (映画バクマン。 小畑健イラストワークス) which was published on October 2, 2015.", 2, new DateTime(2015, 9, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/164254.jpg", 3721, 7.41m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "While most kids his age like to play around for fun, 13-year-old Akito Takagi is determined to find his ambition in life. Manga has been his sole source of inspiration since he was a child; he always engages in reading manga when he takes a break from studying. Within school, Takagi never misses a beat, ranking first in every exam he has taken. However, this does not stop him from constantly worrying about his future, and, despite his indifference, he hopes that he can finally find a true friend he can share his destiny with.\n\nSubsequently, spurred by his love for manga, Takagi resolves himself into becoming a manga author. But before he can begin pursuing his dream, he must overcome one problem—to find an artist who would be willing to make manga with him.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Bakuman. Bangai-hen", null, "バクマン。 番外編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92905/Bakuman_Bangai-hen", null },
                    { 92906, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/164984.jpg", 37292, null, new DateTime(2015, 10, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Perfect Crime Party is about three elementary school children who decide to form a Perfect Crime Club, performing seamless acts of crime. At the beginning of the series, their crimes are as simple as putting a dirty tray on the desk of a boy that already took returned his tray without being caught, or switching seemingly identical items. The plot follows the group's efforts to commit perfect crimes within their school.\n\n(Source: Bakuman Wikia)", "PCP: Kotou no Kodomotachi", null, "PCP-完全犯罪党- 孤島の子供たち", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/92906/PCP__Kotou_no_Kodomotachi", 1 },
                    { 93027, null, null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/165948.jpg", 5346, 7.25m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Bakuman.", null, "バクマン。", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93027/Bakuman", 1 },
                    { 93088, "Getter Robo Devolution: Uchuu Saigo no 3-punkan is a full remake of the original Getter Robo series. The series was published in English as Getter Robo Devolution by Seven Seas Entertainment from June 26, 2018 to October 20, 2020.", 38, new DateTime(2019, 6, 11, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/286719.jpg", 11193, 6.84m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 11, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "They call them Devolved—strange alien creatures that attack our world through distortions in space. Tragedy has always haunted Ryouma, and when his high school comes under alien attack, he figures it's just the latest chapter in a long history of suffering. Yet beneath the monster's deadly glare, a strange professor steps forth with an offer of power. Ryouma is touched by the Getter Rays, a mysterious cosmic force that grants the power to pilot the ultimate fighting machine: Getter Robo!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Getter Robo Devolution: Uchuu Saigo no 3-punkan", "Getter Robo Devolution", "ゲッターロボ DEVOLUTION ～宇宙最後の3分間～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93088/Getter_Robo_Devolution__Uchuu_Saigo_no_3-punkan", 5 },
                    { 93097, "", 155, new DateTime(2017, 1, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/181555.jpg", 152, 8.5m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Oddities have existed throughout history, with some tales of them dating back to 600 years ago. Stories about vampires, a monkey's paw, shikigami, wanderers in the mountain mist, murderous felines, mermaids, wolves, golems, and, most terrifying of all, humans, have been collected by so-called \"oddity specialists.\" The purpose of these specialists is to combat, regulate, and, most importantly, solve the many mysteries behind the circumstances these oddities create.\n\nMonogatari Series: Off Season follows eight protagonists—some specialists, some oddities themselves—as they interact with the world of aberrations, often landing themselves in dangerous situations due to their own mischievous doings.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Monogatari Series: Off Season", null, "〈物語〉シリーズ オフシーズン", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93097/Monogatari_Series__Off_Season", 4 },
                    { 93234, "", 44, new DateTime(2019, 6, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/180909.jpg", 1980, 7.65m, new DateTime(2015, 12, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Manga adaptation of the 4th arc of the Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei series.", "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Raihousha-hen", null, "魔法科高校の劣等生 来訪者編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93234/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Raihousha-hen", 7 },
                    { 93314, "Seirei Gensouki has been published digitally in English as Seirei Gensouki: Spirit Chronicles by J-Novel Club since August 29, 2018, and in print since March 2, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/164868.jpg", 1890, 7.67m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Meet Rio: a callous orphaned boy living in the slums. At only 7-years-old, he realizes he's actually the reincarnation of Haruto Amakawa, a Japanese university student with a tragic past. While still reeling from this shocking epiphany, Rio also comes to learn that he possesses extremely potent magical abilities and uses his new powers to solve the kidnapping case of a little girl. His good deed is acknowledged, and he's rewarded by being enrolled into... a prestigious academy for noble children...?\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Seirei Gensouki", "Seirei Gensouki: Spirit Chronicles", "精霊幻想記", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93314/Seirei_Gensouki", null },
                    { 93326, "", 8, new DateTime(2003, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/164881.jpg", 37434, null, new DateTime(2002, 3, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Omnibus of stories by various light novel authors centered on \"One Year War.\"", "Gundam Novels: Senkou to Natta Senshi-tachi", null, "ガンダムNOVELS―閃光となった戦士たち―", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93326/Gundam_Novels__Senkou_to_Natta_Senshi-tachi", 1 },
                    { 93353, "", 33, new DateTime(2019, 10, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/186156.jpg", 6869, 7.13m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The world needs heroes. Kunugigaoka Magical Academy has a distinguished track record of turning out the greatest heroes in the kingdom. As a result, the students are held to extremely high standards. When a group of students consistently fails to live up to these expectations, they find themselves the target of ridicule, contempt, and discrimination in the \"E\" or End-Class.\"\n\nBefore they can give up, suddenly the Demon King appears before the class. He explains that their quirky hidden abilities, which seem to be the cause of their failure, are actually a sign that they are all special individuals. The archenemy of humanity also announces that he will act as Class-E's homeroom teacher with the sole purpose of nurturing them into heroes capable of killing him.\n\nUnder the supervision of this unkillable teacher, Koro-sensei, and the captain of the Royal Knights, Tadaomi Karasuma, Class-E embarks upon the ultimate quest. Against the opposition of their enemies—such as the Five Virtuosos, the Pope, and various monsters—the students must learn how to kill their teacher, the Big Bad, himself.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Koro-sensei Q!", null, "殺せんせーQ!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93353/Koro-sensei_Q", 5 },
                    { 93408, "", 13, new DateTime(2016, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/173952.jpg", 2900, 7.5m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "300 years after the Calamity War's end.\n\nThe powers which ruled the Earth Sphere have been overthrown, giving way to new rulers of a new world, exhausted of battle. Meanwhile, far away on Mars, the sparks which threaten to ignite a new war have been struck...\n\nOur protagonist Mikazuki Augus, a member of the private security firm Chryse Guard Security (CGS), takes on a mission as bodyguard of Kudelia Aina Bernstein, a young girl who agitates for Chryse's independence from Earth. However, when the elite Gjallarhorn unit, charged with suppressing revolutionaries, raids CGS, its higher-ups deliberately use Mikazuki and the other boys as a decoy to cover their own retreat. Orga Itsuka, leader of the boys' squad, takes this abandonment by the adults as motivation to launch a full-fledged coup d'état. With orders from Orga to hold back Gjallarhorn, Mikazuki sorties in Calamity War-era scrap that CGS had been using as a generator—the Gundam Barbatos...\n\n(Source: Gundam.info)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam: Tekketsu no Orphans", "Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans", "機動戦士ガンダム 鉄血のオルフェンズ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/93408/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam__Tekketsu_no_Orphans", 3 },
