                    { 94865, "Released to celebrate the 30th anniversary of Kochira Katsushikaku Kameari Kouenmae Hashutsujo, Chou Kochikame contains several pages of information and pictures related to the series. The volume also contains one-page tribute crossover drawings by other authors and an interview with Akimoto Osamu.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/170714.jpg", 16580, 6.45m, new DateTime(2006, 9, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Contains five crossover one-shots with other series.\n\n1. Sousha no Kyuujitsu (Crossover with Golgo 13)\n2. Ryoutsu Kankichi VS Lupin III (Crossover with Lupin III)\n3. Seigi Choujin Kameari Dai Shuuketsu!! no Maki (Crossover with Kinnikuman)\n4. Kochira Namekkusei Dragon Kouenmae Hashutsujo (Crossover with Dragon Ball)\n5. Ryoutsu VS Shuuryou Patchi!!: J Gag All Stars Katsushika Dai Soudou!! (Crossover with Pyuu to Fuku! Jaguar, Bobobo-bo Bo-bobo, Taizou Mote King Saga, Maison de Penguin)", "Chou Kochikame", null, "超こち亀", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/94865/Chou_Kochikame", 1 },
                    { 95016, "Poputepipikku has been published in English as Pop Team Epic by Vertical Inc. since October 2, 2018. It has also been published in French by Meian since October 16, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/169121.jpg", 1361, 7.78m, new DateTime(2014, 8, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Two high school girls, the short and exceptionally quick to anger Popuko, and the tall and much more calm Pipimi, do insane things and swear like sailors in this absurdist comedy filled with references and meta humor.", "Poputepipikku", "Pop Team Epic", "ポプテピピック", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95016/Poputepipikku", null },
                    { 95091, "", 5, new DateTime(2016, 2, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/176612.jpg", 19271, 5.95m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A completely original manga based on the Cyborg 009 VS Devilman OVA.", "Cyborg 009 VS Devilman: Breakdown", null, "サイボーグ009 VS デビルマン ―BREAKDOWN―", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95091/Cyborg_009_VS_Devilman__Breakdown", 1 },
                    { 95210, "Boruto: Naruto Next Generations was published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint from April 4, 2017 to August 6, 2024. The series was simulpub through MANGA Plus. The first arc of the manga is an adaptation of the Boruto film, while the following arcs take place after the current timeline of the Boruto anime series.", 81, new DateTime(2023, 4, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/181968.jpg", 11827, 6.8m, new DateTime(2016, 5, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Naruto Uzumaki has finally achieved his dream of becoming Hokage, the leader of the Hidden Leaf Village that he spent his teenage years fighting to protect. Naruto and his peers now live in a world of peace, working hard to uphold an international truce built on good will and diplomacy.\n\nHowever, this stasis comes at a personal cost for the aging hero. Naruto and the shinobi he grew up alongside find that working to upkeep the neutral world takes them away from their families, and even the legendary warriors of Naruto's generation must contend with being mediocre parents to their bitter children, including his own son Boruto.\n\nBoruto Uzumaki faces a world completely unlike that of his father, finding unique trouble in the distance between the two. Contending with a society that heaps an unbearable load of pressure on his shoulders over his status as the Hokage's son, Boruto carves his own path through the world, fighting to make a name for himself as evil forces threaten to shatter the peace his father helped create.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Boruto: Naruto Next Generations", "Boruto: Naruto Next Generations", "BORUTO-ボルト- -NARUTO NEXT GENERATIONS-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95210/Boruto__Naruto_Next_Generations", 20 },
                    { 95212, "Osomatsu-san is based on 's original TV anime series of the same title, which itself is a spin-off of Fujio Akatsuka's manga series Osomatsu-kun.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/178176.jpg", 2895, 7.5m, new DateTime(2016, 1, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Matsuno household has six naughty and mischievous sons (who are sextuplets), led by the eldest Osomatsu. They were grade schoolers back in the Showa period, but despite of still living in the same old household, the street view as well as the life style of modern day society have changed drastically.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Osomatsu-san", null, "おそ松さん", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95212/Osomatsu-san", null },
                    { 95243, "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu Ex has been published in English as Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Ex by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since November 21, 2017.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/170079.jpg", 322, 8.29m, new DateTime(2015, 6, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The first novel focuses on Lugnica king candidate Crusch Karsten, her knight Ferris, and a boy who had a profound influence on their lives. That boy is Fourier, the fourth prince of Lugnica.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu Ex", "Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Ex", "Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活Ex", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95243/Re_Zero_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu_Ex", null },
                    { 95653, "Infini-T Force: Mirai no Byousen has been published in English as Infini-T Force: Arc to the Future by Udon Entertainment since September 26, 2017.", 62, new DateTime(2020, 12, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/175310.jpg", 38216, null, new DateTime(2015, 10, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A girl named Emi uses a pencil that can grant any wish. Emi gets caught up in the robbery of a convenience store, and her life is in danger. She uses the pencil to wish for a \"hero that will save everyone.\" Four heroes appear in response to Emi's wish to change the course of the future.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Infini-T Force: Mirai no Byousen", "Infini-T Force: Arc to the Future", "Infini-T Force 未来の描線", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95653/Infini-T_Force__Mirai_no_Byousen", 10 },
                    { 95746, null, 61, new DateTime(2007, 5, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/170717.jpg", 38244, null, new DateTime(2006, 2, 12, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Maison de Penguin", null, "メゾン・ド・ペンギン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/95746/Maison_de_Penguin", 5 },
                    { 96200, "Naruto: Fuu no Sho - Sugao no Shinjitsu...!! was included in the Official Guest Book given to those who went to the Naruto Exhibition celebrating the end of the series's serialization. The story was adapted into episode 469 of the Naruto: Shippuuden anime.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/270509.jpg", 15370, 6.56m, new DateTime(2015, 4, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Set during Part I, Team 7 finishes yet another unremarkable mission. After Kakashi leaves them for the day, Naruto suggests an S-rank assignment: finding out what Kakashi looks like under his mask.\n\n(Source: Narutopedia)", "Naruto: Fuu no Sho - Sugao no Shinjitsu...!!", null, "NARUTO―ナルト― 風の書：素顔の真実…!!", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96200/Naruto__Fuu_no_Sho_-_Sugao_no_Shinjitsu", null },
                    { 96262, "", 48, new DateTime(2017, 7, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/185481.jpg", 8719, 7m, new DateTime(2016, 2, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A four-panel comedy manga that depicts King aspiring to be a manga creator. In the story, King wants to work as an assistant under professional manga creator Meliodas, and knocks on his door, but the one that answers the door is the editor—the pig Hawk.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Nanatsu no Taizai: King no Manga Michi", null, "七つの大罪 キングのまんが道", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96262/Nanatsu_no_Taizai__King_no_Manga_Michi", 3 },
                    { 96371, "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e has been published in English as Classroom of the Elite by Seven Seas Entertainment since March 1, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/261040.jpg", 7101, 7.11m, new DateTime(2016, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "From the outside, attending the Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School seems like a dream come true. Its students are given remarkable freedom, and it boasts a placement rate of almost one hundred percent. Tokyo Metropolitan can get students their places in the elite jobs and universities of their dreams—if they can win, barter, or save enough points to work their way up the ranks! Kiyotaka Ayanokouji has landed at the bottom of this cutthroat academy in the scorned Class D, where he meets Suzune Horikita, a girl who's determined to rise up the ladder to Class A. Can they beat the system in a school full of ruthless competition?\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e", "Classroom of the Elite", "ようこそ実力至上主義の教室へ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96371/Youkoso_Jitsuryoku_Shijou_Shugi_no_Kyoushitsu_e", null },
                    { 96383, "", 30, new DateTime(1995, 8, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/268484.jpg", 38431, null, new DateTime(1992, 11, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Ushio to Tora centers around the travails and battles of Ushio Aotsuki, who is constantly being stalked and aided by a gigantic, supernatural and sometimes invisible tiger-like monster.\n\nUshio's family maintains a Shinto temple in Japan, where ~500 years ago, his samurai ancestor battled that same tiger to a standstill, and eventually trapped him against a rock using a blessed spear called the \"Beast Spear,\" which in addition to its intrinsic formidability as a weapon, can also endow its wielder with the martial ability of the ancestor who originally wielded it.\n\nUshio accidentally unsealed the cave Tora was trapped in. Initially, Ushio refuses to remove the spear pinning Tora down, but Tora's unsealed presence summons various monsters who wish to fight him, and by extension Ushio. Ushio is forced to free Tora, who would like to eat Ushio, but dares not since Ushio keeps the spear close by. The series focuses on their relationship, interspersed with battles against mythological foes, and with Tora's attempts to grapple with modern life.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)", "Ushio to Tora", null, "うしおととら", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96383/Ushio_to_Tora", 4 },
                    { 96389, "Shino Kaori (志乃かをり) served as the costume designer for the series.", 39, new DateTime(2006, 2, 13, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/229552.jpg", 38435, null, new DateTime(2004, 6, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Cutie Honey SEED takes place in an alternate reality where Cutie Honey is a TV series and the Honey Kisaragi of the series is a shapeshifting alien unrelated to the main protagonist.\n\n(Source: Cutie Honey Wiki)", "Cutie Honey Seed", null, "キューティーハニーSEED", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96389/Cutie_Honey_Seed", 4 },
                    { 96390, "", 59, new DateTime(2010, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/177022.jpg", 38436, null, new DateTime(2001, 12, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "This book parodies the original Kidou Senshi Gundam TV series, and is especially centered around the character Char Aznable.", "Tony Takezaki no Gundam Manga", "Tony Takezaki presents Gundam Manga", "トニーたけざきのガンダム漫画", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96390/Tony_Takezaki_no_Gundam_Manga", 3 },
                    { 96448, null, null, new DateTime(1994, 7, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/258735.jpg", 38454, null, new DateTime(1993, 10, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "GS Mikami: Gokuraku Daisakusen!!", null, "GS美神 極楽大作戦!!", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96448/GS_Mikami__Gokuraku_Daisakusen", 3 },
                    { 96528, "Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou has been published in English as Arifureta: From Commonplace to World's Strongest by Seven Seas Entertainment since March 13, 2018.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/186402.jpg", 6151, 7.19m, new DateTime(2016, 2, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After a magical circle suddenly appears at school, Hajime Nagumo and his classmates find themselves transported inside a church where they are welcomed as honored guests. Thrust into the RPG-like world of Tortus, each student shows great promise in both strength and never-before-seen classes—everyone besides Hajime. Given the class \"Synergist,\" which boasts borderline average stats on top of being weak in combat, Hajime is soon considered to be useless by the rest of his class.  \n\nWorking towards strengthening themselves, the students descend into a dungeon, but a mishap causes the entire class to be plunged into danger. Cornered by a large demon, they are trapped on a bridge looming over an abyss, the only way out being in front of them. In an effort to save his class, Hajime declares himself as bait, hoping his sacrifice will grant a chance of escape for the others. Though he intends to escape as well, a stray fireball flies in his direction, sending him flying off the bridge and down into the depths of the dungeon. Miraculously surviving, Hajime now begins his quest of survival in an attempt to reach the surface.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou", "Arifureta: From Commonplace to World's Strongest", "ありふれた職業で世界最強", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96528/Arifureta_Shokugyou_de_Sekai_Saikyou", null },
                    { 96597, "", null, new DateTime(2016, 11, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/201561.jpg", 38495, null, new DateTime(2016, 7, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Matsuno household has six naughty and mischievous sons (who are sextuplets), led by the eldest Osomatsu. They were grade-schoolers back in the Showa period, but despite still living in the same old household, the street view, as well as the lifestyle of modern day society, have changed drastically.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Osomatsu-san", null, "おそ松さん", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96597/Osomatsu-san", 2 },
                    { 96692, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/178190.jpg", 38523, null, new DateTime(1995, 11, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Osomatsu-kun tribute manga by Masayuki Izumi portraying sextuplets as young adults.", "Osomatsu-kun", null, "おそ松くん", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96692/Osomatsu-kun", null },
                    { 96762, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/228873.jpg", 13647, 6.68m, new DateTime(2004, 8, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Kakashi orders Naruto, Sasuke, and Sakura to watch a movie before their next mission. Naruto is a big fan of the lead actress. After the movie, they see the heroine in person and being chased. They help her and Naruto asks for an autograph but she wouldn't give him one. When the three returns, Kakashi tells them about their mission: to escort the actress to the Snow Country to film a new movie. \n\n(Source: ANN)", "Naruto: Dai Katsugeki! Yuki Hime Shinobu Houjou Datteba yo!!", null, "NARUTO 大活劇!雪姫忍法帖だってばよ!!", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96762/Naruto__Dai_Katsugeki_Yuki_Hime_Shinobu_Houjou_Datteba_yo", 1 },
                    { 96763, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/228874.jpg", 16027, 6.5m, new DateTime(2005, 8, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Naruto, Shikamaru, and Sakura are executing their mission of delivering a lost pet to a certain village. However, right in the midst of things, troops led by the mysterious knight, Temujin, attack them. In the violent battle, the three become separated. Temujin challenges Naruto to a fight and at the end of the fierce battle, both fall together from a high cliff. Furthermore, Shikamaru, having been left behind, beholds a giant moving fortress as it appears before his very eyes. In order to get a grasp on the situation, he infiltrates the fortress by himself, however once there he witnesses a frightening sight... \n\n(Source: ANN)", "Gekijouban Naruto: Dai Gekitotsu! Maboroshi no Chitei Iseki Datteba yo", null, "劇場版NARUTO 大激突!幻の地底遺跡だってばよ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96763/Gekijouban_Naruto__Dai_Gekitotsu_Maboroshi_no_Chitei_Iseki_Datteba_yo", 1 },
                    { 96764, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/228880.jpg", 13974, 6.66m, new DateTime(2006, 8, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Naruto, Kakashi, Sakura, and Lee are sent to protect a prince during his trip around the world and see that he returns safely to his home in the Moon Country. The Moon Country happens to be really rich and as such the Prince tends to buy anything his heart desires, during his travels the Prince would come across a circus group that features a rare Sabre-toothed tiger that he just had to have. So he purchased the entire group. Suddenly a mission to protect just the spoiled prince that hardly listened to anything said, turns in to a mission to look after animals and a prince that doesn't listen to what they say, and in the end somehow get them all back safely to their home country. All the while there are three mysterious Ninja wielding some frightening jutsu waiting for them. Why are they attacking them? What do they want with Team Kakashi!?! \n\n(Source: NarutoFan)", "Gekijouban Naruto: Dai Koufun! Mikazuki-jima no Animal Panic Datteba yo", null, "劇場版 NARUTO 大興奮!みかづき島のアニマル騒動〈パニック〉だってばよ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96764/Gekijouban_Naruto__Dai_Koufun_Mikazuki-jima_no_Animal_Panic_Datteba_yo", 1 },
                    { 96765, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/228881.jpg", 4557, 7.32m, new DateTime(2007, 8, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Demons that once almost destroyed the world, are revived by someone. To prevent the world from being destroyed, the demon has to be sealed and the only one who can do it is the shrine maiden Shion from the country of demons, who has two powers; one is sealing demons and the other is predicting the deaths of humans. This time Naruto's mission is to guard Shion, but she predicts Naruto's death. The only way to escape it, is to get away from Shion, which would leave her unguarded, then the demon, whose only goal is to kill Shion will do so, thus meaning the end of the world. Naruto decides to challenge this \"prediction of death,\" but fails to prove Shion's prediction wrong and supposedly dies in vain.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)", "Gekijouban Naruto: Shippuuden", null, "劇場版NARUTO 疾風伝", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96765/Gekijouban_Naruto__Shippuuden", 1 },
                    { 96766, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/228882.jpg", 12696, 6.75m, new DateTime(2008, 8, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A mysterious group of ninjas makes a surprise attack on the Konohagakure, which takes great damage. The nightmare of another Shinobi World War could become a reality. Sasuke, who left Konoha to kill his brother, Itachi, appears for the second time in front of Naruto at an unknown location to prevent it from coming to fruition.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)", "Gekijouban Naruto: Shippuuden - Kizuna", null, "劇場版NARUTO 疾風伝 絆", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96766/Gekijouban_Naruto__Shippuuden_-_Kizuna", 1 },
                    { 96767, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/228884.jpg", 10147, 6.91m, new DateTime(2009, 8, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Ninjas with bloodline limits begin disappearing in all the countries and blame points toward the fire nation. By Tsunade's order, Kakashi is sacrificed to prevent an all out war. After inheriting charms left by Kakashi, Naruto fights through friends and foes to prevent his death while changing the minds of those who've inherited the will of fire.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Gekijouban Naruto: Shippuuden - Hi no Ishi wo Tsugu Mono", null, "劇場版NARUTO 疾風伝 火の意志を継ぐ者", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96767/Gekijouban_Naruto__Shippuuden_-_Hi_no_Ishi_wo_Tsugu_Mono", 1 },
                    { 96768, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/172679.jpg", 10571, 6.89m, new DateTime(2010, 8, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Assigned on a mission to capture Mukade, a missing-nin, Naruto Uzumaki sets out for the once glorious historic ruins of \"Ouran,\" where he pursues and corners the rogue ninja. Mukade's goal is revealed to be a dormant leyline within the ruins; he unleashes the power of the leyline, causing a light to envelop Naruto, sending him into the past, 20 years before the series began. When Naruto awakens, he comes into contact with the Fourth Hokage, Minato Namikaze.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)", "Gekijouban Naruto: Shippuuden - The Lost Tower", null, "劇場版NARUTO 疾風伝 ザ・ロストタワー", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96768/Gekijouban_Naruto__Shippuuden_-_The_Lost_Tower", 1 },
                    { 96769, "", 9, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/228889.jpg", 7663, 7.08m, new DateTime(2011, 7, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After being captured for attempting to assassinate the leader of Kumogakure, the Raikage, and killing Jounin from Kirigakure and Iwagakure, Naruto is imprisoned in Houzukijou, a criminal containment facility also known as the Blood Prison. \n\nThe master of the castle, Mui, uses the ultimate imprisonment jutsu to steal power from the prisoners. In this place, something is aiming for Naruto's life. The battle to prove his innocence and uncover the truth has begun for Naruto and his friends.\n\n(Source: AnimeAvenue)", "Naruto: Blood Prison", null, "NARUTO 鬼燈の城〈ブラッド・プリズン〉", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96769/Naruto__Blood_Prison", 1 },
                    { 96770, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/228890.jpg", 8239, 7.03m, new DateTime(2012, 7, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Ten years ago, a gigantic demon beast known as the Nine-Tailed Demon Fox was released from its jinchuuriki by an unknown shinobi wearing a mask. The village of Konohagakure was close to destruction by the attack of the Nine-Tails, but the village was saved by its leader. Minato Namikaze and his wife Kushina Uzumaki—who was the jinchuuriki at the time of the attack—sealed away the demon inside their new born son: Naruto Uzumaki. However, this act of saving the village cost them their lives and they left the future of the ninja world to Naruto.\n\nWith the demon fox sealed away, things continued as normal. However, the peace of the village would not last long, for Pain, Konan, Itachi Uchiha, Kisame Hoshigaki, Sasori, Deidara, Hidan and Kakuzu—members of a dreaded shinobi group called the Akatsuki—attacked Konohagakure. Naruto narrowly manages to launch a counter-attack but why have these shinobi appeared when all of them were meant to have died? The mystery remains, but the shinobi are praised by heir families for completing such a dangerous mission. However, one of them who has never known the faces of his parents, Naruto, cannot help but feel lonely. At that exact time, suddenly, the masked man makes his appearance in Konoha. Naruto and his allies are both attacked by the man's mysterious new doujutsu.\n\n(Source: Naruto Wikia)", "Road to Ninja: Naruto the Movie", null, "ROAD TO NINJA NARUTO THE MOVIE", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96770/Road_to_Ninja__Naruto_the_Movie", 1 },
                    { 96792, "Kimetsu no Yaiba ranked sixth and 17th in the 2020 and 2021 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division, respectively. Following the series' success, Koyoharu Gotouge was awarded the Special Prize at the 25th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize in 2021. As of February 2021, over 150 million copies of the series have been sold worldwide. As a part of the JUMP START initiative, the first three chapters of Kimetsu no Yaiba were published in English in VIZ Media's digital Weekly Shonen Jump on the same day as the Japanese release. VIZ Media published the volumes as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba under its Shonen Jump imprint from July 3, 2018, to August 3, 2021.", 207, new DateTime(2020, 5, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/179023.jpg", 491, 8.15m, new DateTime(2016, 2, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Tanjirou Kamado lives with his impoverished family on a remote mountain. As the oldest sibling, he took upon the responsibility of ensuring his family's livelihood after the death of his father. On a cold winter day, he goes down to the local village in order to sell some charcoal. As dusk falls, he is forced to spend the night in the house of a curious man who cautions him of strange creatures that roam the night: malevolent demons who crave human flesh.\n\nWhen he finally makes his way home, Tanjirou's worst nightmare comes true. His entire family has been brutally slaughtered with the sole exception of his sister Nezuko, who has turned into a flesh-eating demon. Engulfed in hatred and despair, Tanjirou desperately tries to stop Nezuko from attacking other people, setting out on a journey to avenge his family and find a way to turn his beloved sister back into a human.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kimetsu no Yaiba", "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba", "鬼滅の刃", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/96792/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba", 23 },
                    { 97057, "", 48, new DateTime(1991, 2, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/177595.jpg", 38604, null, new DateTime(1991, 1, 20, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story of Gundam F91 revolves around teenage space colonist Seabook Arno, his friend Cecily Fairchild, and the efforts of the Cross Bone Vanguard militia, led by Cecily's grandfather Meitzer Ronah, to establish an aristocracy known as \"Cosmo Babylonia.\"\n\nIn keeping with Gundam tradition, the civilian Seabook is forced by circumstance to pilot the F91 Gundam, coincidentally designed in part by his estranged mother, Dr. Monica Arno.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam F91: Crossbone Vanguard", null, "機動戦士ガンダムF91 クロスボーン・バンガード", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97057/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_F91__Crossbone_Vanguard", 2 },
                    { 97060, "", 10, new DateTime(1989, 3, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/229937.jpg", 38607, null, new DateTime(1988, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Set in the Universal Century 0090, between Mobile Suit Gundam ZZ and before Mobile Suit Gundam: Char's Counterattack, the plot centers around Darry Neil Guns, a member of the Monotone Mouse Corporation who was repairing Texas Colony at Side 5 -a Space Colony that was damaged from the One Year War, when they are attacked by the New Summer Project terrorist organization's Colorde forces. Both the anti-Earth Federation militant group Colorde and the New Summer Project were actually being used as a front for the resurgence of the Second Neo Zeon movement under the leadership of Char Aznable. In an attempt to resist Colorde, the Monotone Mouse Corporation is forced to team up with the Earth Federation Force's Arahas force and fight. Darry Neil Guns, a fan of the Gundam, modified his worker mobile suit to resemble the original RX-78 Mobile Suit Gundam, and through mistaken identity it is acknowledged as the actual Gundam.\n\n(Source: Gundam Wiki)", "Double Fake: Under the Gundam", null, "ダブルフェイク アンダー・ザ・ガンダム", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97060/Double_Fake__Under_the_Gundam", 1 },
                    { 97090, "Chiyu Mahou no Machigatta Tsukaikata: Senjou wo Kakeru Kaifuku Youin has been published in English as The Wrong Way to Use Healing Magic by One Peace Books since August 23, 2022.", 155, new DateTime(2020, 3, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/173367.jpg", 4060, 7.37m, new DateTime(2016, 3, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Usato, an ordinary high schooler, happens to run into two fellow students after school one rainy day. Suddenly, all three of them are engulfed in a magic circle and transported to a fantasy world. There's just one tiny problem—Usato is simply dragged along by accident! On top of that, Usato learns that he is capable of using healing magic—an incredibly rare affinity in this new world. Now Usato must spend his days with the rescue team thugs, struggling through their hellish training regimen—learning the wrong way to use healing magic. Get ready for an eccentric otherworld fantasy filled with comedy and combat!\n\n(Source: One Peace Books)", "Chiyu Mahou no Machigatta Tsukaikata: Senjou wo Kakeru Kaifuku Youin", "The Wrong Way to Use Healing Magic", "治癒魔法の間違った使い方～戦場を駆ける回復要員～", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97090/Chiyu_Mahou_no_Machigatta_Tsukaikata__Senjou_wo_Kakeru_Kaifuku_Youin", 12 },
                    { 97200, "", 7, new DateTime(2015, 12, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/175150.jpg", 753, 8m, new DateTime(2015, 9, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off of Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! that focuses on Vanir and Wiz.", "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! Spin-off: Kono Kamen no Akuma ni Soudan wo!", null, "この素晴らしい世界に祝福を！スピンオフ この仮面の悪魔に相談を！", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97200/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Shukufuku_wo_Spin-off__Kono_Kamen_no_Akuma_ni_Soudan_wo", 1 },
                    { 97324, "", 85, new DateTime(2020, 3, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/173990.jpg", 38685, null, new DateTime(2015, 4, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story is set in the year Showa 44 (1969), and it centers around Takanori Jinguuji, the 27-year-old man who eventually become the head of the Japan Shogi Association in the main 3-gatsu no Lion series.", "3-gatsu no Lion Shouwa Ibun: Shakunetsu no Toki", null, "3月のライオン昭和異聞 灼熱の時代", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97324/3-gatsu_no_Lion_Shouwa_Ibun__Shakunetsu_no_Toki", 10 },
                    { 97524, "", 18, new DateTime(2018, 3, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/185051.jpg", 9584, 6.95m, new DateTime(2016, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Calamity War that engulfed all of Earth, and the Gundams deployed then which were said to have brought it to an end. 300 years later, some have been hidden, some abandoned...\n\nArgie Mirage, a boy who carries the past of his family's death at the hands of a Gundam, meets Volco Warren, a boy who wishes to rebuild the Gundam his family left behind.\n\nTo destroy a Gundam. To rebuild a Gundam. In the midst of the two boys' intersecting fates, the Astaroth will awaken from its 300 year slumber\n\n(Source: MU)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam: Tekketsu no Orphans - Gekkou", null, "機動戦士ガンダム 鉄血のオルフェンズ 月鋼", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97524/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam__Tekketsu_no_Orphans_-_Gekkou", 4 },
                    { 97658, "", 9, new DateTime(2013, 8, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/230101.jpg", 38741, null, new DateTime(2012, 11, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 3, "In the year UC 0079, during the One Year War of the first Gundam series and eight years before the story in Zeta Gundam, a boy named Van Asiliaino and his friends attempt to flee the war, and their fates change when they meet a certain soldier.\n\n(Source: Gundam Wiki)", "Kidou Senshi Z Gundam Gaiden: Advance of Z - Toki ni Aragaishi Mono", "Advance of Z: The Traitor to Destiny", "機動戦士Zガンダム外伝 ADVANCE OF Z 刻に抗いし者", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97658/Kidou_Senshi_Z_Gundam_Gaiden__Advance_of_Z_-_Toki_ni_Aragaishi_Mono", 1 },
                    { 97664, "Gundam Pilot Retsuden: Soukyuu no Yuusha-tachi began serialization in Comic Japan (コミックジャパン), which was discontinued after its first issue. The second chapter was published in the RPG Magazine Great (RPGマガジングレイト), which was also discontinued. The third chapter went unpublished until the tankoubon was released with a newly drawn fourth chapter.", 4, new DateTime(2001, 10, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/230104.jpg", 38744, null, new DateTime(1997, 11, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Chronicles the lives of four prominent pilots of the Principality of Zeon before and during the One Year War.\n\n(Source: Gundam Wiki)", "Gundam Pilot Retsuden: Soukyuu no Yuusha-tachi", null, "ガンダムパイロット列伝 蒼穹の勇者達", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97664/Gundam_Pilot_Retsuden__Soukyuu_no_Yuusha-tachi", 1 },
                    { 97722, "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Bakuen wo! was published in English as Konosuba: An Explosion on This Wonderful World! by Yen Press from June 25, 2019 to June 23, 2020.", 21, new DateTime(2017, 12, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/187499.jpg", 1591, 7.73m, new DateTime(2016, 4, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Crimson Magic Clan members Megumin and Yunyun are at the top of their class, but they still have a lot to learn. Yunyun's begun learning advanced magic, but Megumin has gone down a different path-the path of explosion magic! Despite being warned of its limited usefulness, Megumin believes explosion magic is the way for her to become a great, voluptuous wizard, and she won't be convinced otherwise!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Bakuen wo!", "Konosuba: An Explosion on This Wonderful World!", "この素晴らしい世界に爆焔を!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/97722/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Bakuen_wo", 5 },
                    { 98118, "", 13, new DateTime(1975, 8, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/254036.jpg", 18805, 6.12m, new DateTime(1974, 8, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Great Mazinger starts after the defeat of Mazinger Z. Tetsuya Tsurugi is the new protagonist, piloting the powerful Great Mazinger, a creation of the once thought dead Kenzo Kabuto, the father of Koji Kabuto. This time the enemy is the Mycene Empire and its powerful robots.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Great Mazinger", null, "グレートマジンガー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98118/Great_Mazinger", 2 },
                    { 98255, "Uchuu Patrol Luluco is based on studio 's original TV anime series of the same title. The series has been published in English as Space Patrol Luluco by Crunchyroll since May 18, 2016.", 3, new DateTime(2016, 6, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/176066.jpg", 16263, 6.48m, new DateTime(2016, 4, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story takes place in Ogikubo, which is the name of the specially designated area in space in the Milky Way where Earthlings and aliens can live together. Luluco is a female middle school student who lives with her father, and no matter where she is, Luluco is a common, \"super normal\" girl. As she is living her normal life, one day the mysterious transfer student ΑΩ Nova abruptly appears before her. That meeting will change Luluco's fate.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Uchuu Patrol Luluco", "Space Patrol Luluco", "宇宙パトロールルル子", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98255/Uchuu_Patrol_Luluco", null },
                    { 98425, "Kemono Friends: Youkoso Japari Park e! is based on smartphone RPG Kemono Friends. The series was published in English as Kemono Friends: Welcome to Japari Park by Yen Press in a complete omnibus on February 6, 2018.", 21, new DateTime(2017, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/187856.jpg", 10573, 6.89m, new DateTime(2015, 5, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Since childhood Nana has been dreaming of becoming a caretaker at the Japari Park, all because \"Friends,\" unique human-like animals, live there. And today her dream finally came true! But will she be able to earn their trust?", "Kemono Friends: Youkoso Japari Park e!", "Kemono Friends: Welcome to Japari Park", "けものフレンズ ようこそジャパリパークへ！", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98425/Kemono_Friends__Youkoso_Japari_Park_e", 2 },
                    { 98436, "Youjo Senki has been published in English as The Saga of Tanya the Evil by Yen Press since February 6, 2018.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/186468.jpg", 280, 8.32m, new DateTime(2016, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Intrigued by the severe lack of faith a particular salaryman displayed as he drew his last breath, a godlike presence known only as \"Being X\" reincarnates him into a magical yet war-torn world to test his mettle. Under these new circumstances, Being X believes that, should this man succumb to relentless suffering, he will call upon the heavens for assistance.\n\nStarting life again as a young girl named Tanya Degurechaff, the salaryman quickly utilizes his past experiences and volunteers to the military of his country, the Empire. Wielding tremendous potential despite being a child, Tanya's prodigious capacity for strategic and magical warfare allows her to quickly ascend the ranks and consistently lead her nation to miraculous victories in the ongoing war. Even so, she does all of this for one purpose: to live in the backlines far from the warzone, effectively defying Being X's objectives.\n\nHowever, as Tanya strives to escape Being X's influence, she soon comes to know that even with her genius, there are situations that a human simply cannot overcome without divine intervention.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Youjo Senki", "The Saga of Tanya the Evil", "幼女戦記", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98436/Youjo_Senki", null },
                    { 98462, "The last 3 volumes of the Naruto Shinden Series were published in English by Viz Media from August 4, 2020 to March 2, 2021.", 28, new DateTime(2018, 7, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/204432.jpg", 8627, 7.01m, new DateTime(2016, 8, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A series of Naruto novels linking the Naruto and Boruto series.\n\n1. Konoha Shinden: Yukemuri Ninpouchou [Hinata Shou]\n2. Naruto Shinden: Oyako no Hi (Naruto's Story: Family Day) [Miyamoto Mirei]\n3. Sasuke Shinden: Shitei no Hoshi (Sasuke's Story: Star Pupil) [Esaka Jun]\n4. Shikamaru Shinden: Maichiru Hana wo Ureu Kumo (Shikamaru's Story: Mourning Clouds) [Yano Takashi]", "Naruto Shinden Series", null, "NARUTO -ナルト- 新伝シリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98462/Naruto_Shinden_Series", 4 },
                    { 98480, "Due to lack of popularity, only one volume was released before the series was cancelled.", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/203326.jpg", 38964, null, new DateTime(2006, 8, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Caught with a severe fever before his school trip, Tobio Ikuse, a second-year high school student was forced to miss out his school trip with his schoolmates on a luxury liner. Four days later, the news about the disappearance of the teachers and second-year students reaches Tobio's ears.\n\nFew months after the incident, Tobio having slowly recovered from the shock accidentally encounters one of his classmates again.\n\n(Source: High School DxD Wikia, edited)", "Slash/Dog", null, "SLASH/DOG", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98480/Slash_Dog", 1 },
                    { 98567, null, 53, new DateTime(2020, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/189790.jpg", 38985, null, new DateTime(2016, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Kidou Senshi Crossbone Gundam Dust", "Mobile Suit Cross Bone Gundam Dust", "機動戦士クロスボーン・ガンダム DUST", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98567/Kidou_Senshi_Crossbone_Gundam_Dust", 13 },
                    { 98583, null, 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/177897.jpg", 5352, 7.25m, new DateTime(2016, 5, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei SS", "The Irregular at Magic High School SS", "魔法科高校の劣等生SS", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/98583/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei_SS", 1 },
                    { 99361, null, 12, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/179908.jpg", 10935, 6.86m, new DateTime(2016, 7, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Shinmai Maou no Testament: Sweet!", "The Testament of Sister New Devil", "新妹魔王の契約者〈テスタメント〉 SWEET!", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99361/Shinmai_Maou_no_Testament__Sweet", 1 },
                    { 99386, "Sword Art Online: Project Alicization was published in English by Yen Press from December 8, 2020 to July 5, 2022.", 30, new DateTime(2021, 6, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/201451.jpg", 1003, 7.89m, new DateTime(2016, 8, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Kirito awakens in a vast, fantastical forest filled with towering trees. In his search for clues to the truth of his surroundings, he encounters a young boy who seems to know him. He ought to be a simple NPC, but the depth of his emotions seem no different than a human. As they search for the boy's parents, Kirito finds a peculiar memory returning to him. A memory from his own childhood, of this boy and a girl, too, with golden hair, and a name he should have never forgotten—Alice.\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online: Project Alicization", "Sword Art Online: Project Alicization", "ソードアート・オンライン プロジェクト・アリシゼーション", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99386/Sword_Art_Online__Project_Alicization", 5 },
                    { 99446, "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu Tanpenshuu has been published in English as Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Short Story Collection by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since August 20, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/179393.jpg", 1853, 7.68m, new DateTime(2014, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The world of Re:Zero continues to grow with every new tale and this collection of short stories is the perfect place to learn more about everyone's favorite characters! What will Rem and Ram have to deal with today? Where will Emilia's new adventures take her? And how will Subaru land himself in yet another scrape?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu Tanpenshuu", "Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Short Story Collection", "Re：ゼロから始める異世界生活 短編集", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99446/Re_Zero_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu_Tanpenshuu", null },
                    { 99593, null, null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/179768.jpg", 39261, null, new DateTime(2015, 12, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, null, "Kidou Senshi Gundam Thunderbolt Gaiden", "Mobile Suit Gundam Thunderbolt", "機動戦士ガンダム サンダーボルト 外伝", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99593/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_Thunderbolt_Gaiden", null },
                    { 99614, "Shinseiki Evangelion: Pikopiko Chuugakusei Densetsu has been published in English as Neon Genesis Evangelion: Legend of the Piko Piko Middle School Students by Dark Horse Comics since May 23, 2017.", 70, new DateTime(2018, 8, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/210797.jpg", 11321, 6.84m, new DateTime(2014, 4, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Mysterious invaders are threatening Earth...so recruit a group of elite schoolkids to play video games that secretly train them for the real fight that lies ahead! Does this plan sound familiar? Well, they'd better get a new plan, because the elite schoolkids are Shinji, Rei, Asuka, and Kaworu, and they're too busy playing games to ever get in the fricking robot!\n\n(Source: Dark Horse Comics)", "Shinseiki Evangelion: Pikopiko Chuugakusei Densetsu", "Neon Genesis Evangelion: Legend of the Piko Piko Middle School Students", "新世紀エヴァンゲリオン ピコピコ中学生伝説", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99614/Shinseiki_Evangelion__Pikopiko_Chuugakusei_Densetsu", 5 },
                    { 99758, "Sword Art Online: Hollow Realization is an adaptation of PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita game of the same title. The series was published in English by Yen Press from November 13, 2018 to August 18, 2020.", 38, new DateTime(2019, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/193355.jpg", 4945, 7.28m, new DateTime(2016, 10, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Sword Art Online: Hollow Realization takes place in Sword Art: Origin, a restoration of Aincrad with intentions of research and development in the year 2026, three years after the original Sword Art Online event.", "Sword Art Online: Hollow Realization", null, "ソードアート・オンライン ホロウ・リアリゼーション", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99758/Sword_Art_Online__Hollow_Realization", 6 },
                    { 99853, "", 23, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/180694.jpg", 9865, 6.93m, new DateTime(2016, 1, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An anthology of Trinity Seven: 7-nin no Mashotsukai by various mangaka.", "Trinity Seven: 7-nin no Mashotsukai Comic Anthology", null, "トリニティセブン 7人の魔書使い コミックアンソロジー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99853/Trinity_Seven__7-nin_no_Mashotsukai_Comic_Anthology", 1 },
                    { 99891, "Tensei shitara Ken deshita was initially released as a web novel on the user-generated site Shousetsuka ni Narou in October 2015. Micro Magazine acquired the rights to the series under the GC Novels imprint and began publishing volumes in July 2016. On May 30th, a limited edition fifth volume was released and bundled with a drama CD with voices provided by Satoshi Hino and Inori Minase, among others. Tensei shitara Ken deshita has been published digitally in English as Reincarnated as a Sword by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint since May 2, 2019, and in print since August 6, 2019.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/203310.jpg", 1592, 7.73m, new DateTime(2016, 7, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The hero of Tensei shitara Ken deshita differs from your standard otherworldly protagonist in that he is reincarnated as a sword! Beginning his quest by spawning in the middle of a beast-ridden forest, he encounters an injured girl frantically fleeing for her life. Saving her from her assailants, the pair acquaint themselves, and the girl introduces herself as Fran. She bears a heavy past, having endured the enslavement and maltreatment of her tribe, the Black Cats. \n\nAs the hero is unable to remember the name from his past life, the young and tenacious Fran bestows him the name \"Shishou\" and becomes his wielder. Thereafter, Shishou and Fran become a formidable team, embarking on quests to liberate the oppressed and exact justice!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tensei shitara Ken deshita", "Reincarnated as a Sword", "転生したら剣でした", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/99891/Tensei_shitara_Ken_deshita", null },
                    { 100039, null, 5, new DateTime(2010, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/181643.jpg", 39388, null, new DateTime(2009, 9, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Aokishi: Tetsuwan Atom Aokishi yori", null, "青騎士 -鉄腕アトム 青騎士より-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/100039/Aokishi__Tetsuwan_Atom_Aokishi_yori", 1 },
                    { 100079, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/187834.jpg", 2858, 7.51m, new DateTime(2016, 6, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Akutsu Masatora is a demon who has infiltrated a high school in the human world. His goal is to find candidates to aid Hell in the fight against their natural enemies, the angels of Heaven. Assigned a seat next to Lily Amane, another student who transferred here not long ago, Akutsu falls prey to her beauty and decides to recruit her to his cause.\n\nBut there's more to Lily than meets the eye, and Akutsu not only finds himself an accomplice to one of the very enemies he is supposed to defeat, but he also might have developed feelings for her.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Oroka na Tenshi wa Akuma to Odoru", null, "愚かな天使は悪魔と踊る", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/100079/Oroka_na_Tenshi_wa_Akuma_to_Odoru", null },
                    { 100790, "", 6, new DateTime(2016, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/196965.jpg", 2748, 7.53m, new DateTime(2015, 7, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Short stories bundled with the first press release of the Blu-Ray/DVD volumes of the High School DxD BorN anime.\n\nThe Occult Research Club faces off against invaders known as Underworld Lifeforms led by Loki that have travelled from the future. However, the future also brings a surprise visit by Issei's children.\n\n(Source: highschooldxd.wikia)", "High School DxD EX", null, "ハイスクールD×D EX", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/100790/High_School_DxD_EX", null },
                    { 101476, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/183724.jpg", 31272, null, new DateTime(2016, 9, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "\"Maou Army's strongest magician\" I'm called. Ike, a demon capable of capturing a fort alone. Clearing away enemies with immense magic, he is without a doubt a monster awed by friend and foe. However he has a secret he can't tell other demons. \"I, actually I'm human you know.\" Using modern knowledge to keep his secret, he became treated as a great commander and the driving force of the Maou's army.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Maougun Saikyou no Majutsushi wa Ningen datta", null, "魔王軍最強の魔術師は人間だった", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/101476/Maougun_Saikyou_no_Majutsushi_wa_Ningen_datta", null },
                    { 101482, "", 32, new DateTime(2019, 7, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/200962.jpg", 4033, 7.37m, new DateTime(2016, 10, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The second year has started! Mikihiko has been promoted to Course 1, Tatsuya has entered the new Magical Engineering Course, and trouble is brewing between Saegusa Mayumi's younger twin sisters and 1st year representative Shippou Takuma, a member of the 18 Assistant House's Shippou Household.", "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Double Seven-hen", null, "魔法科高校の劣等生 ダブルセブン編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/101482/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Double_Seven-hen", 3 },
                    { 101662, "Sokushi Cheat ga Saikyou sugite, Isekai no Yatsura ga Marude Aite ni Naranai n desu ga. was published digitally in English as My Instant Death Ability Is So Overpowered, No One in This Other World Stands a Chance Against Me! by J-Novel Club from September 21, 2020 to December 15, 2023, and in print by Yen Press under the J-Novel Club imprint since June 6, 2023.", 341, new DateTime(2023, 3, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/216486.jpg", 6364, 7.17m, new DateTime(2016, 10, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Awaking to absolute chaos and carnage while on a school trip, Yogiri Takatou discovers that everyone in his class has been transported to another world! He had somehow managed to sleep through the entire ordeal himself, missing out on the Gift—powers bestowed upon the others by a mysterious Sage who appeared to transport them. Even worse, he and another classmate were ruthlessly abandoned by their friends, left as bait to distract a nearby dragon. Although not terribly bothered by the thought of dying, he reluctantly decides to protect his lone companion. After all, a lowly Level 1000 monster doesn't stand a chance against his secret power to invoke Instant Death with a single thought! If he can stay awake long enough to bother using it, that is...\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Sokushi Cheat ga Saikyou sugite, Isekai no Yatsura ga Marude Aite ni Naranai n desu ga.", "My Instant Death Ability Is So Overpowered, No One in This Other World Stands a Chance Against Me!", "即死チートが最強すぎて、異世界のやつらがまるで相手にならないんですが。", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/101662/Sokushi_Cheat_ga_Saikyou_sugite_Isekai_no_Yatsura_ga_Marude_Aite_ni_Naranai_n_desu_ga", 14 },
                    { 101956, "", 16, new DateTime(1973, 3, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/254037.jpg", 40094, null, new DateTime(1972, 6, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A manga adaptation of the Devilman anime series drawn by Mitsuru Hiruta.", "Devilman", null, "デビルマン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/101956/Devilman", 2 },
                    { 102286, "", 6, new DateTime(2016, 11, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/286689.jpg", 31532, null, new DateTime(2016, 10, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An omnibus serialization of Kochikame tribute manga by various Shounen Jump authors to commemorate the 40th anniversary of the series.", "Minna no Kochikame", null, "みんなのこち亀", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102286/Minna_no_Kochikame", null },
                    { 102343, "Fumetsu no Anata e ranked third in the 2018 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. It was nominated for the 11th Manga Taisho Award in 2018 and placed fifth in the final ranking. In 2019, the manga won the 43rd Kodansha Manga Award in the shounen category, along with 5-toubun no Hanayome. The series has been simulpub digitally in English as To Your Eternity by Kodansha Comics USA. The publisher has physically released the manga since October 31, 2017. It has also been published in Spain by Milky Way Ediciones; in Argentina by Editorial Ivrea; in Brazilian Portuguese by NewPOP Editora; in French by Pika Édition; in Russian by Istari Comics; and in Polish by Kotori.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/189781.jpg", 323, 8.29m, new DateTime(2016, 11, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "It, a mysterious immortal being, is sent to the Earth with no emotions nor identity. However, It is able to take the shape of those around that have a strong impetus.\n\nAt first, It is a sphere. Then, It imitates the form of a rock. As the temperature drops and snow falls atop the moss, It inherits the moss. When an injured, lone wolf comes limping by and lays down to die, It takes on the form of the animal. Finally, It gains consciousness and begins to traverse the empty tundra until It meets a boy.\n\nThe boy lives alone in a ghost town, which the adults abandoned long ago in search of the paradise said to exist far beyond the endless sea of white tundra. However, their efforts were for naught, and now the boy is in a critical state.\n\nAcquiring the form of the boy, It sets off on a never-ending journey, in search of new experiences, places, and people.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Fumetsu no Anata e", "To Your Eternity", "不滅のあなたへ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102343/Fumetsu_no_Anata_e", null },
                    { 102484, "Sword Art Online Alternative: Clover's Regret has been published in English by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since August 20, 2024.", 14, new DateTime(2018, 8, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/186734.jpg", 8212, 7.04m, new DateTime(2016, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Asuka Empire—a VRMMORPG with a Japanese aesthetic, and the original home of the Sleeping Knights—is holding a new horror-themed event called the 108 Apparitions. Nayuta, a stoic warrior priestess, and Koyomi, an excitable ninja, are enjoying a break from the frights when they come across a mysterious monk named Yanagi. Despite knowing nothing about games, the elderly man is determined to complete a certain quest within a week, and he has agreed to pay a detective a ridiculous sum to make it happen. Just as strange as his request is the detective himself, a foxlike young man who has put all his stat points into luck. Yanagi's desired quest turns out to be none other than Ghost Orchestra, which has stumped every player who's tried it. Can this unlikely party manage what no one else has?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online Alternative: Clover's Regret", "Sword Art Online Alternative Clover's Regret", "ソードアート・オンライン オルタナティブ クローバーズ・リグレット", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102484/Sword_Art_Online_Alternative__Clovers_Regret", 3 },
                    { 102569, "Eiga Novelize Death Note: Light Up the New World was published in German as Death Note: Light up the new World by Tokyopop on February 1, 2020.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/253590.jpg", 10733, 6.88m, new DateTime(2016, 10, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Novelization of the Death Note: Light Up the New World live-action movie.", "Eiga Novelize Death Note: Light Up the New World", null, "映画ノベライズ DEATH NOTE Light up the NEW world", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102569/Eiga_Novelize_Death_Note__Light_Up_the_New_World", 1 },
                    { 102667, "Slime Taoshite 300-nen, Shiranai Uchi ni Level Max ni Nattemashita has been published in English as I've Been Killing Slimes for 300 Years and Maxed Out My Level by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since April 24, 2018.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/207976.jpg", 3244, 7.46m, new DateTime(2017, 1, 13, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After living a painful life as an office worker, Azusa ended her short life by dying from overworking. So when she found herself reincarnated as an undying, unaging witch in a new world, she vows to spend her days stress-free and as pleasantly as possible. She ekes out a living by hunting down the easiest targets—the slimes! But after centuries of doing this simple job, she's ended up with insane powers...how will she maintain her low key life now?!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Slime Taoshite 300-nen, Shiranai Uchi ni Level Max ni Nattemashita", "I've Been Killing Slimes for 300 Years and Maxed Out My Level", "スライム倒して300年、知らないうちにレベルMAXになってました", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102667/Slime_Taoshite_300-nen_Shiranai_Uchi_ni_Level_Max_ni_Nattemashita", null },
                    { 102702, "Jaku-Chara Tomozaki-kun won the 10th Shogakukan Light Novel Grand Prize. The light novel ranked four times in the top 10 in the Kono Light Novel ga Sugoi! for the Light Novels category from 2017 to 2019 and in 2021. The series has been published in English as Bottom-Tier Character Tomozaki by Yen Press since July 30, 2019.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/185942.jpg", 1419, 7.78m, new DateTime(2016, 5, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "For Fumiya Tomozaki, one of the best gamers in Japan, the \"game of life\" is the worst game in existence. Despite the fact that Tomozaki is the number one player in the video game Attack Families, he is a self-proclaimed bottom-tier character when it comes to real life. As a second-year high school student, he suffers from an absolute lack of self-esteem, leading him to completely give up on trying to improve himself as a person. Instead, he blames the real world for being completely unbalanced, with no logical way to level up your character.\n\nAoi Hinami is an immensely popular girl in Tomozaki's class with fantastic grades. She fits the role of a perfect heroine and is on the opposite end of the social spectrum from Tomozaki. However, after a chance encounter with Hinami, Tomozaki realizes that she is not a perfect character after all!\n\nSo begins a story of drama and romance revolving around Tomozaki's attempts at conquering the game of life under Hinami's guidance.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Jaku-Chara Tomozaki-kun", "Bottom-Tier Character Tomozaki", "弱キャラ友崎くん", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102702/Jaku-Chara_Tomozaki-kun", null },
                    { 102846, "", 7, new DateTime(2008, 9, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/254120.jpg", 39273, null, new DateTime(2000, 11, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "1. Toriko (pilot)\n2. Interview\n3. Girigiri Sebastian!!\n4. Eriya\n5. (Kabu) Muscle Company!\n6. Yu-u-sya\n7. Shiritsu Wild Gakuen", "Toriko Gaiden: Shimabukuro Mitsutoshi Tanpenshuu", null, "トリコ外伝 島袋光年短編集", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102846/Toriko_Gaiden__Shimabukuro_Mitsutoshi_Tanpenshuu", 1 },
                    { 102847, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/254121.jpg", 31697, null, new DateTime(2002, 1, 6, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The original pilot one-shot of Toriko, later included in the Toriko Gourmet Hunting Book.", "Toriko", null, "トリコ", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/102847/Toriko", null },
                    { 103000, "", 3, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/189156.jpg", 1636, 7.72m, new DateTime(2016, 12, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The novel focuses on the reconstruction of Soul Society after Yhwach's defeat, and on the official couples' love lives and marriage: specifically, on Rukia and Renji's childhood friend romance.\n\n(Source: TV Tropes)", "Bleach: We Do Knot Always Love You", null, "BLEACH WE DO knot ALWAYS LOVE YOU", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103000/Bleach__We_Do_Knot_Always_Love_You", 1 },
                    { 103045, "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle - Episode Ryuu was published in English as Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Familia Chronicle Episode Lyu by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint on June 26, 2018.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/192839.jpg", 1359, 7.78m, new DateTime(2017, 3, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "For the skilled former adventurer Ryu, it's another eventful day at the Benevolent Mistress! A certain couple's only daughter has been kidnapped, bringing Ryu out into the streets to search for her, in the name of justice and Astrea. Her investigation of the missing child eventually leads her to a lawless area of the Labyrinth City, the Grand Casino, where money and power decide everything!\n\nThis is the start of the Gale Wind's tale in the city of Orario, home of the Dungeon and adventure!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle - Episode Ryuu", "Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Familia Chronicle Episode Lyu", "ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうか ファミリアクロニクル episodeリュー", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103045/Dungeon_ni_Deai_wo_Motomeru_no_wa_Machigatteiru_Darou_ka__Familia_Chronicle_-_Episode_Ryuu", 1 },
                    { 103047, "Dragon Ball Gaiden: Tensei shitara Yamcha Datta Ken was published in English as Dragon Ball: That Time I Got Reincarnated as Yamcha! by VIZ Media on November 6, 2018. It was also released in Spanish by Planeta Cómic on October 15, 2019.", 5, new DateTime(2017, 8, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/202580.jpg", 8310, 7.03m, new DateTime(2016, 12, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "When a typical high school student attempts to sprint down a set of stairs to get a glimpse up a girl's skirt, he slips and hits his head. The boy wakes up to find that he now inhabits the body of Yamcha within the world of the manga Dragon Ball. Quickly recalling Yamcha's multiple deaths throughout the series and his status as a joke in the real world, the student must now utilize his extensive knowledge of the manga to avoid suffering the original Yamcha's unfortunate fate.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Dragon Ball Gaiden: Tensei shitara Yamcha Datta Ken", "Dragon Ball: That Time I Got Reincarnated as Yamcha!", "DRAGON BALL外伝 転生したらヤムチャだった件", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103047/Dragon_Ball_Gaiden__Tensei_shitara_Yamcha_Datta_Ken", 1 },
                    { 103078, "Nanatsu no Taizai: Seven Days - Touzoku to Seishoujo was published in English by Kodansha Comics USA from October 2, 2018, to December 4, 2018. It was also released in Spanish by Norma Editorial as a 2-in-1 omnibus volume on October 31, 2018; and in Brazilian Portuguese by Editora JBC on July 19, 2020.", 7, new DateTime(2017, 8, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/198159.jpg", 1862, 7.67m, new DateTime(2017, 1, 16, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Elaine always believed humans were greedy, selfish creatures. Her brother, the King of Fairies Harlequin \"King,\" told her as much, and this belief was only reinforced when tragedy ripped away a dear friend of theirs. This event resulted in King heading off for vengeance, leaving Elaine behind to guard the Fountain of Youth and the forest in which it resided. He promised to return, and so she waited.\n\nSeven hundred years later, Elaine has continued to fulfill her duty. Many humans have come to seek immortality for their own selfish reasons. Each one is the same: cruel and backstabbing. But then, Elaine meets the human bandit Ban, and he defies all of her expectations; the forest protects him, and he easily gives up on the Fountain when he learns its truth. From that point on, the two of them spend seven days together, discovering that the other might be the kindred spirit they need to end their lonely days.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Nanatsu no Taizai: Seven Days - Touzoku to Seishoujo", "The Seven Deadly Sins: Seven Days", "七つの大罪 セブンデイズ～盗賊と聖少女～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103078/Nanatsu_no_Taizai__Seven_Days_-_Touzoku_to_Seishoujo", 2 },
                    { 103144, "Released just months after the original light novel's publishing, Tensei shitara Ken deshita was serialized in the Denshi Birz magazine; the manga was then published in Comic Boost after the former magazine ended. The light novel and manga were produced and serialized concurrently. The series has been published in English as Reincarnated as a Sword by Seven Seas Entertainment since December 17, 2019.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/195150.jpg", 3098, 7.48m, new DateTime(2016, 12, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Hunted, enslaved, and killed—such is the terrible fate that befalls the members of the Black Cats tribe. Twelve-year-old Fran, a girl of the persecuted race, craves revenge for the atrocities committed against her people. She dreams of a brighter future, one for which she will not hesitate to get her hands dirty. An encounter with a talking sword, a reincarnated man looking for a beautiful wielder, turns out to be the deciding moment that will change her fate.\n\nWith the help of her new comrade, the young Fran plans to reclaim the pride and honor of her kin, slashing down all her enemies along the way. With an unshakable resolve, she embarks on a journey with her miraculous sword.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tensei shitara Ken deshita", "Reincarnated as a Sword", "転生したら剣でした", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103144/Tensei_shitara_Ken_deshita", null },
                    { 103244, "", 20, new DateTime(2020, 4, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/195232.jpg", 1241, 7.82m, new DateTime(2017, 4, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In 2022, the world of virtual reality was upended by the arrival of a new invention from a genius programmer, Akihiko Kayaba, called NerveGear. It was the first full-dive system, and with it, came endless possibilities to VRMMORPGs.\n\nIn 2026, a new machine called the Augma is developed to compete against the NerveGear and its successor, the Amusphere. A next-gen wearable device, the Augma doesn't have a full-dive function like its predecessors. Instead, it uses Augmented Reality (AR) to get players into the game. It is safe, user-friendly and lets users play while they are conscious, making it an instant hit on the market. The most popular game on the system is \"Ordinal Scale\" (OS), an ARMMORPG developed exclusively for the Augma.\n\nAsuna and the gang have already been playing OS for a while, by the time Kirito decides to join them. They're about to find out that Ordinal Scale isn't all fun and games...\n\n(Source: Aniplex USA)", "Gekijouban Sword Art Online: Ordinal Scale", "Sword Art Online Ordinal Scale", "劇場版 ソードアート・オンライン -オーディナル・スケール-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103244/Gekijouban_Sword_Art_Online__Ordinal_Scale", 5 },
                    { 103392, "", 8, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/189153.jpg", 2133, 7.62m, new DateTime(2014, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off of Nanatsu no Taizai showing how Ban and Elaine met in more detail.\n\nIn the land north of Britannia, there is a forest where humans are not allowed to go, and it is known as the \"Fairy King's Forest.\" The one known as the Fairy King, Harlequin, has not been seen for 700 years. His younger sister Elaine guards the Fountain of Youth from human greed by herself. After many partings and 700 years of isolation, her tears are about to dry up. Then, a young man appears seeking the Fountain of Youth. That young man's name is Ban.\n\nOver the course of seven days with Ban, Elaine's heart is healed. The distance between them closes, but...\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Nanatsu no Taizai: Seven Days", null, "七つの大罪 セブンデイズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103392/Nanatsu_no_Taizai__Seven_Days", 1 },
                    { 103647, "", 3, new DateTime(2016, 12, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/189930.jpg", 17031, 6.41m, new DateTime(2016, 9, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "Amakawa Haruto is a young man who died before reuniting with his childhood friend who disappeared five years ago. Rio is a boy living in the slums who wants revenge for his mother who was murdered in front of him when he was five years old.\n\nEarth and another world. Two people with completely different backgrounds and values. For some reason, the memories and personality of Haruto who should've died is resurrected in Rio's body. As the two are confused over their memories and personalities fusing together, Rio (Haruto) decide to live in this new world.\n\nAlong with Haruto's memories, Rio awakens an unknown \"special power,\" and it seems that if he uses it well, he can live a better life. But before that, Rio encountered a kidnapping that turns out to be two princesses of the Bertram Kingdom that he lives in.\n\nAfter saving the princesses, Rio is given a scholarship to the Royal Academy, a school for the rich and powerful. Being a poor orphan in a school of nobles turns out to be an extremely detestable place to be.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Seirei Gensouki", null, "精霊幻想記", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103647/Seirei_Gensouki", null },
                    { 103701, "Beastars won the 11th Manga Taisho Award in 2018. In the same year, it also won the New Work Prize at the 22nd Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize and the 42nd Kodansha Manga Award in the Shounen category. In 2020, VIZ Media's translation of the manga was nominated for the Eisner Award in the Best U.S. Edition of International Material—Asia category. The series was published in English by VIZ Media under the VIZ Signature imprint from July 16, 2019, to January 17, 2023. It has also been published in Argentina by Editorial Ivréa, in French by Éditions Ki-oon from January 24, 2019, to June 2, 2022, and in Spain by Milky Way Ediciones.", 196, new DateTime(2020, 10, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/189832.jpg", 380, 8.23m, new DateTime(2016, 9, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In a world populated by anthropomorphic animals, there exists a bias: carnivores are just mindless predators in the eyes of many herbivores. However, when an alpaca named Tem is murdered within the walls of Cherryton High School, the fear toward carnivores skyrockets to an all-time high. \n\nLegoshi, a student at this school, is a gray wolf who is quite awkward despite his fearsome appearance. When turmoil affects his school life, he is forced to confront the divide between herbivores and carnivores, as well as his own place in this society. This is further complicated by his supposedly romantic feelings toward a herbivore, which might not be what they seem.\n\nBeastars details Legoshi's struggles against his inner demons while living in a society that is unforgiving toward his kind.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Beastars", "Beastars", "BEASTARS", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103701/Beastars", 22 },
                    { 103761, "Kono Yuusha ga Ore Tueee Kuse ni Shinchou sugiru was published in English as The Hero Is Overpowered But Overly Cautious by Yen Press from June 18, 2019 to October 5, 2021.", 157, new DateTime(2019, 12, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/221751.jpg", 3132, 7.47m, new DateTime(2017, 2, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 3, "The story begins when the goddess Rista summons a hero to help her in a hard mode video game-like world. The hero, Seiya, is exceptional in every way, but he is incredibly cautious. He does things like buy three sets of armor (one to wear, a spare, and a spare for the spare) and go full power against weak slimes (just in case).\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Kono Yuusha ga Ore Tueee Kuse ni Shinchou sugiru", "The Hero Is Overpowered But Overly Cautious", "この勇者が俺TUEEEくせに慎重すぎる", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103761/Kono_Yuusha_ga_Ore_Tueee_Kuse_ni_Shinchou_sugiru", 7 },
                    { 103807, "", 8, new DateTime(2017, 2, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/192597.jpg", 15310, 6.56m, new DateTime(2016, 10, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "When Kirito took on a random quest on the 76th floor to kill time, he didn't expect to be transported to a bedroom and find himself wearing pajamas. To his surprise, the One Thousand and One Nights quest summons various girls that he is acquainted with, all of whom are tricked into thinking that they have to share a bed with Kirito to complete the quest. The true goal of the quest, however, is for Kirito to survive till morning without getting into bed with them. If he fails, there will be a penalty for the girls...\n\n(Source: Dreadful Decoding)", "Sword Art Online: Kirito no Aincrad Night", "Sword Art Online: Aincrad Night of Kirito", "ソードアート・オンライン キリトの千夜一夜物語〈アインクラッドナイト〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103807/Sword_Art_Online__Kirito_no_Aincrad_Night", 1 },
                    { 103808, "", 3, new DateTime(2017, 2, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/257896.jpg", 40530, null, new DateTime(2016, 10, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off of the Sword Art Online series focusing on Kibaou.", "Sword Art Online Iden: Kibaou-han!", null, "ソードアート・オンライン異伝 キバオウはん！", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103808/Sword_Art_Online_Iden__Kibaou-han", null },
                    { 103897, "Dr. Stone won the 64th Shogakukan Manga Award in the Shounen category in 2019. The manga ranked 17th in the 2020 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. As a part of the JUMP START initiative, the first three chapters of the manga were published in English in VIZ Media's digital Weekly Shonen Jump on the same day as the Japanese release. After, the series was added to VIZ Media's Weekly Shonen Jump lineup, and it was also simulpub through MANGA Plus. The volumes were published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint from September 4, 2018, to July 4, 2023. It has also been released in Brazilian Portuguese by Panini Comics since September 2018.", 237, new DateTime(2023, 12, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/197883.jpg", 444, 8.19m, new DateTime(2017, 3, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "When a mysterious light suddenly engulfs Earth, humanity is left petrified, frozen in stone. Thousands of years later, the world is teeming with vegetation, and forests have taken the places of cities that once stood proudly. One of the very first to emerge from their stone prison is Taiju Ooki, who finds that his good friend, a brilliant young scientist named Senkuu, has been preparing for his awakening. While Taiju wishes to save the girl he loves, Senkuu is determined to figure out the cause behind the strange phenomenon and restore the world to its former glory.\n\nBut when they free the infamously powerful Tsukasa Shishiou in order to gain an upper hand against the dangers in an unfamiliar world, they realize that their new comrade has other plans. Tsukasa sees their predicament as a chance to start over; free from the corruption and destruction wrought by technology, he will stop at nothing to achieve his goals. With both sides unable to see eye to eye, Senkuu and his devotion to science will clash with Tsukasa and his primal nature in what will truly be a battle of the ages.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Dr. Stone", "Dr. Stone", "Dr.STONE", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103897/Dr_Stone", 27 },
                    { 103907, "", 4, new DateTime(2017, 2, 16, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/190479.jpg", 18782, 6.13m, new DateTime(2017, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After the sun exploded, 100 people were put on a ship to find a new planet to live on, but when main character wakes up only five kids are still alive and their ship is on a planet that can somehow grant their wishes.\n\n(Source: MangaHelpers)", "Kamisama no Iutoori 0", null, "神さまの言うとおり零", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103907/Kamisama_no_Iutoori_0", null },
                    { 103910, "", 13, new DateTime(1976, 2, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/270441.jpg", 40557, null, new DateTime(1964, 7, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A collection of Tetsuwan Atom short stories written after the series's original run.", "Tetsuwan Atom Bekkan", null, "鉄腕アトム 別巻", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/103910/Tetsuwan_Atom_Bekkan", 1 },
                    { 104064, "Little Witch Academia was published in English by Yen Press from June 26, 2018, to May 21, 2019. It was also released in Polish by Studio JG from April 26, 2019, to September 27, 2019; and in Brazilian Portuguese by Editora JBC in November 2023.", 17, new DateTime(2018, 8, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/196656.jpg", 4382, 7.33m, new DateTime(2016, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "When Atsuko \"Akko\" Kagari was a little girl, she attended the Magical Festa magic show hosted by the witch Shiny Chariot. Ever since then, she has dreamed of also becoming a witch by enrolling at Luna Nova, the academy her idol attended. Akko befriends two fellow witches—Lotte Yansson and Sucy Manbavaran—who she believes will share in her fantastical, magical school experience... However, although Luna Nova Academy is filled to the brim with magic and witches, it is not quite what she expected.\n\nSeen as an inept, rebellious, and talentless witch, Akko struggles daily to prove she is worthy of her place at the academy. One day, an opportunity to demonstrate her merit presents itself—she must defeat an ancient dragon thought to be previously sealed. Can Akko emerge as the successful witch she desperately yearns to be?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Little Witch Academia", "Little Witch Academia", "リトルウィッチアカデミア", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/104064/Little_Witch_Academia", 3 },
