                    { 104841, "Kidou Senshi Gundam: The Origin MSD - Cucuruz Doan no Shima has been published in English as Mobile Suit Gundam: The Origin MSD - Cucuruz Doan's Island by Kodansha USA under the Vertical Comics imprint since October 1, 2024.", 29, new DateTime(2019, 5, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/272620.jpg", 40813, null, new DateTime(2016, 6, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Former Zeon mobile suit squad leader Cucuruz Doan has deserted, taking up residence on a small island where he helped to raise a number of orphaned children. But what about the other members of his squad? While the original story was told from federation pilot Amuro Ray's perspective, Ohno's limited series goes beyond the original television episode to explore the ramifications of Doan's actions on his own troops, bringing us a multilayered and emotionally complex view of the events from Zeon's perspective.\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam: The Origin MSD - Cucuruz Doan no Shima", "Mobile Suit Gundam: The Origin MSD - Cucuruz Doan's Island", "機動戦士ガンダム THE ORIGIN MSD ククルス・ドアンの島", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/104841/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam__The_Origin_MSD_-_Cucuruz_Doan_no_Shima", 5 },
                    { 104897, "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle - Episode Ryuu was published in English as Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Familia Chronicle Episode Lyu from November 13, 2018 to February 18, 2020.", 22, new DateTime(2018, 10, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/192776.jpg", 2047, 7.64m, new DateTime(2017, 2, 22, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In Orario, the only place in the world that hosts the entrance to the massive subterranean Dungeon, there's a certain tavern where the most desperate and vulnerable bring their troubles. There, the ex-adventurer Lyu Lion uses her terrifying strength to wrest what justice she can from the shadows of the Labyrinth City! But when a girl goes missing and all evidence points toward the powerful Grand Casino, she may need more than brute force to help...!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle - Episode Ryuu", "Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Familia Chronicle Episode Lyu", "ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうか ファミリアクロニクル episodeリュー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/104897/Dungeon_ni_Deai_wo_Motomeru_no_wa_Machigatteiru_Darou_ka__Familia_Chronicle_-_Episode_Ryuu", 6 },
