                    { 105125, null, 37, new DateTime(2007, 7, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/192813.jpg", 8787, 7m, new DateTime(2004, 11, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Tsurezure Nichijou Ekotoba Colourful Bleach", null, "徒然日常絵詞 カラフル ブリーチ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/105125/Tsurezure_Nichijou_Ekotoba_Colourful_Bleach", null },
                    { 105579, null, 4, new DateTime(2017, 7, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/195401.jpg", 19086, 6.04m, new DateTime(2017, 4, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Ichigo 100%: East Side Story", null, "いちご100% EAST SIDE STORY", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/105579/Ichigo_100__East_Side_Story", null },
                    { 105837, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/211412.jpg", 5963, 7.2m, new DateTime(2016, 11, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "It is the 16th year of the Meiji era. Five years have passed since Kenshin Himura stopped the uprising of Makoto Shishio. Though the flames of his budding revolution were extinguished, the scars left in its wake are still felt across Japan. Remnants of his group—though scattered—still exist. Some have found peace while others continue to fight.\n\nAfter a remaining faction tried to revive the revolution, Shishio's old sword fell into the hands of Ashitarou Hasegawa, an orphan boy who has never known a home. The conflict also leaves both Aran Inoue, a 16-year-old half-Japanese, half-American boy, and a mercenary girl named Asahi Kubota with a hefty price to pay off, with nowhere else to go. But luckily for these individuals, the Kamiya dojo has always been a place to accept wanderers without prying into their pasts.\n\nThe three are keen to start fresh, so when two members of Asahi's former clan show up demanding her return, Asahi refuses and things start to get ugly. In the midst of the chaos, the clan members drop a package containing a picture of dojo proprietor Kaoru Kamiya's presumably deceased father and his location—Hakodate, Hokkaido. With only this information, the members of the Kamiya dojo embark on an adventure across the sea in the hopes of finding news about Kaoru's father and the reason he is being targeted.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Rurouni Kenshin: Meiji Kenkaku Romantan - Hokkaido-hen", "Rurouni Kenshin: Hokkaido Arc", "るろうに剣心－明治剣客浪漫譚・北海道編－", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/105837/Rurouni_Kenshin__Meiji_Kenkaku_Romantan_-_Hokkaido-hen", null },
                    { 106113, "", 28, new DateTime(2018, 1, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/228184.jpg", 12204, 6.78m, new DateTime(2017, 5, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The novel will center around Boruto entering the ninja academy along with Sarada, Shikadai, Inojin, and Chouchou to face a coming threat to their school life.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Boruto: Naruto Next Generations Novel", null, "BORUTO -NARUTO NEXT GENERATIONS- NOVEL", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106113/Boruto__Naruto_Next_Generations_Novel", 5 },
                    { 106156, "", 31, new DateTime(2021, 3, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/224554.jpg", 15615, 6.54m, new DateTime(2017, 3, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off of Boruto: Naruto Next Generations focusing on Boruto and his team.", "Boruto: Saikyo Dash Generations", null, "BORUTO-SAIKYO DASH GENERATIONS-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106156/Boruto__Saikyo_Dash_Generations", 4 },
                    { 106204, "Majo to Yajuu went on a two-month hiatus starting on January 22, 2023, due to the author's poor health. The hiatus was extended indefinitely after an official announcement on March 22, 2023. The series has been published in English as The Witch and the Beast by Kodansha USA since October 27, 2020. It has also been published in Italian by Panini Comics since February 16, 2023.", 58, new DateTime(2023, 1, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/200778.jpg", 445, 8.19m, new DateTime(2016, 11, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 3, "In a fantasy world, there exist witches capable of curses nearly impossible to remove except by very few methods: receive a loving kiss from a prince, hope the wrathful witch has a change of heart, or attempt a third possibility.\n\nGuideau and Ashaf are an unusual duo working for the Order of Magical Resonance, an organization that deals with any case related to magic. Guideau, a young woman with the eyes of a beast and a knack for rushing into things head-on, has a deeply personal grudge against witches. Ashaf, a refined yet enigmatic man who carries a coffin on his back, keeps his partner in check with a calm manner and presence of mind. Together, they investigate magical mysteries and crimes, all while looking for the witch who cursed Guideau.\n\nThe pair arrive in a city where they have heard a witch resides; however, much to their surprise, the people of the city consider the witch to be a hero protecting them. Both Guideau and Ashaf believe that only trouble follows a witch wherever she goes—but that remains to be seen here.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]\n\nIncluded one-shot:\nVolume 6: Majo no Kimagure (Witch and Whim)", "Majo to Yajuu", "The Witch and the Beast", "魔女と野獣", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106204/Majo_to_Yajuu", 10 },
                    { 106218, null, 34, new DateTime(2019, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/194472.jpg", 3582, 7.42m, new DateTime(2016, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Nichijou wo!", null, "この素晴らしい世界に日常を！", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106218/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Nichijou_wo", 3 },
                    { 106285, "Super Dragon Ball Heroes: Ankoku Makai Mission! is based on the Super Dragon Ball Heroes arcade game.", 21, new DateTime(2020, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/228478.jpg", 16754, 6.44m, new DateTime(2016, 8, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story follows Xeno Trunks soon after the defeat of Cell in his own timeline, becoming a Time Patroller and assisting Chronoa in confronting the Time Breakers, later known as the Dark Empire Forces from the Demon Realm. The Dark Empire having revived their leader, Mechikabura, plan to retrieve artifacts known as the Dark Dragon Balls, which have scattered across time and space, in order to restore him back into the prime of his youth. However, the Dark Dragon Balls have merged with past villains, giving them new found might. Now it is up to Xeno Trunks, along with new allies such as Xeno Goku and Xeno Vegeta from stopping their plans from coming to fruition.\n\n(Source: Dragon Ball Wiki)", "Super Dragon Ball Heroes: Ankoku Makai Mission!", null, "スーパードラゴンボールヒーローズ 暗黒魔界ミッション!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106285/Super_Dragon_Ball_Heroes__Ankoku_Makai_Mission", 3 },
                    { 106374, "", null, new DateTime(2016, 10, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/235046.jpg", 41571, null, new DateTime(2012, 6, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Fourteen-year-old Madoka Kaname lives with her four magical girl siblings: the motherly eldest sister, Mami Tomoe; the ravenous second sister, Kyouko Sakura; the vigilant third sister, Homura Akemi; and the rash fourth sister, Sayaka Miki.\n\nDespite wanting to become a magical girl herself someday, Madoka finds that handling the whimsical habits of her family is already troublesome enough. Even so, between the eccentric duties of a magical girl and the mundane, normal responsibilities, the daily lives of these five girls are filled with fun, memorable stories to tell!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Madoka☆Engawa", null, "まどか☆えんがわ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106374/Madoka☆Engawa", 3 },
                    { 106602, "Bleach: Can't Fear Your Own World was published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint from July 7, 2020 to April 20, 2021.", 32, new DateTime(2018, 12, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/291343.jpg", 281, 8.32m, new DateTime(2017, 8, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Quincies's Thousand Year Blood War is over, but the embers of turmoil still smolder in the Soul Society. Tokinada Tsunayashiro, elevated to head of his clan after a slew of assassinations take out every other claimant to the title, has a grand plan to create a new Soul King. His dark ambitions soon sow the seeds of a new total war across the realms, but all is not lost. There is one unlikely Soul Reaper who holds the key to defusing the conflict—Shuhei Hisagi, assistant captain of the Ninth Company and reporter for the Seireitei Bulletin!\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Bleach: Can't Fear Your Own World", "Bleach: Can't Fear Your Own World", "BLEACH Can't Fear Your Own World", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106602/Bleach__Cant_Fear_Your_Own_World", 3 },
                    { 106677, "Shousetsu Berserk: Enryuu no Kishi was published in English as Berserk: The Flame Dragon Knight by Dark Horse on April 17, 2019.", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/266240.jpg", 14188, 6.64m, new DateTime(2017, 6, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Flame Dragon Knight traces the rise of the warrior Grunbeld from humble beginnings to the all-powerful Apostle who will one day face Guts in mortal combat!\n\n(Source: Dark Horse)", "Shousetsu Berserk: Enryuu no Kishi", "Berserk: The Flame Dragon Knight", "小説 ベルセルク 炎竜の騎士", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106677/Shousetsu_Berserk__Enryuu_no_Kishi", 1 },
                    { 106755, "Kimi to Boku no Saigo no Senjou, Aruiwa Sekai ga Hajimaru Seisen has been published in English as Our Last Crusade or the Rise of a New World by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since September 24, 2019.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/196122.jpg", 2432, 7.57m, new DateTime(2017, 5, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "For years, a great war has raged on between the scientifically advanced Empire and a paradise of witches known as the Nebulis Sovereignty. This age-old battle sets the scene for a fateful encounter between two young combatants: an imperial swordsman, Iska, and the witch princess, Aliceliese. As sworn enemies, they vow to cut each other down in order to unite their worlds, and yet Iska finds himself entranced by her beauty and righteousness, while Aliceliese is moved by his strength and resolve. In the midst of a never-ending war that forbids them from being together, they have no choice but to destroy each other—or can they find another way?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Kimi to Boku no Saigo no Senjou, Aruiwa Sekai ga Hajimaru Seisen", "Our Last Crusade or the Rise of a New World", "キミと僕の最後の戦場、あるいは世界が始まる聖戦", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106755/Kimi_to_Boku_no_Saigo_no_Senjou_Aruiwa_Sekai_ga_Hajimaru_Seisen", null },
                    { 106764, "", 6, new DateTime(2014, 8, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/248960.jpg", 41780, null, new DateTime(2011, 10, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "1. Kiseki no Kyuuseishu Densetsu no Maki\n2. Kinnikuman Gaiden: Benkiman - Ushinawareta Inca no Kioku\n3-4. The Machineguns Kuuhaku no Mikkakan\n5. Choujin Ketsumeigun, Kessei Hiwa\n6. Ramenman to Brocken Jr.: Onshuu no Kanata ni", "Kinnikuman: Yomikiri Kessakusen 2011-2014", null, "キン肉マン 読切傑作選2011-2014", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106764/Kinnikuman__Yomikiri_Kessakusen_2011-2014", 1 },
                    { 106810, "Chiyu Mahou no Machigatta Tsukaikata: Senjou wo Kakeru Kaifuku Youin has been published in English as The Wrong Way to Use Healing Magic by One Peace Books since November 22, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/201048.jpg", 4231, 7.35m, new DateTime(2017, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Ken Usato is a normal high-schooler in every sense of the word—average grades, dreams, and a tendency to dislike extraordinary people. However, when he encounters the president and the vice president of the student council, both popular and extraordinary, he immediately befriends them. All of this is interrupted when Usato's new friends are summoned into another world—and he accidentally gets summoned as well!\n\nDejected and with no way to return, he resigns himself to staying quietly in the new world—until he finds out he has an affinity for healing magic, a very rare form of magic which gives him both self-confidence and the attention of all mages. However, not all attention is good, which is something Usato realizes when he is noticed by a crazy fellow healing magic user.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Chiyu Mahou no Machigatta Tsukaikata: Senjou wo Kakeru Kaifuku Youin", "The Wrong Way to Use Healing Magic", "治癒魔法の間違った使い方～戦場を駆ける回復要員～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106810/Chiyu_Mahou_no_Machigatta_Tsukaikata__Senjou_wo_Kakeru_Kaifuku_Youin", null },
                    { 106813, "", 24, new DateTime(2018, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/195614.jpg", 41795, null, new DateTime(2016, 11, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Tekkadan has now become a direct affiliate of Teiwaz after procuring a new trade agreement with Arbrau. With its newfound funds and prestige, Tekkadan finds both its list of allies and enemies growing. Meanwhile, the flames of the Gjallarhorn power struggle continue to rage in full force. As a part of her efforts to make Mars financially independent from Earth, Kudelia Aina Bernstein founds the Admoss Company and enlists Tekkadan as her business partner.\n\nThe stakes are getting higher as the Tekkadan family continues to grow. Will Orga, Mikazuki, and the rest of the Tekkadan faction be able to keep up, or will Kudelia's dream of Martian independence die out?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kidou Senshi Gundam: Tekketsu no Orphans 2", "Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans", "機動戦士ガンダム 鉄血のオルフェンズ 弐", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/106813/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam__Tekketsu_no_Orphans_2", 4 },
                    { 107295, "", 9, new DateTime(2014, 7, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/219847.jpg", 36291, null, new DateTime(2013, 5, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "New disasters for ESPer Saiki Kusuo… Nendou starts talking about Nietzsche, Kaidou becomes a Wizard at Kitsune High…!? Caught in the trap of a jumbo ramen challenge, and what’s the reason Saiki is absent from school…!? A novelized compilation of daily life stories. Celebrating the 1 year anniversary of serialization for the popular JUMP manga Saiki Kusuo no PSI nan! What new disasters await Saiki? A collection of 5 short stories, 4 extra short stories, illustrations, and pull out posters.\n\n(Source: Official site)", "Saiki Kusuo no Ψ-nan: Extra Story of Psychics", null, "斉木楠雄のΨ難　EXTRA STORY OF PSYCHICS", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/107295/Saiki_Kusuo_no_Ψ-nan__Extra_Story_of_Psychics", 2 },
                    { 107339, "", null, new DateTime(2020, 8, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/198483.jpg", 5774, 7.22m, new DateTime(2017, 7, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "\"Why does no one remembers the true world...!\"\n\nThe era when the great race of the five tribes competing for hegemony on the ground ended with the victory of mankind led by hero Sid. However, that world was suddenly \"overwritten\" in front of a boy Kai. In the rewritten world, Kai saw the scene where humans lost to the five tribal wars because of the absence of hero Sid—here dragons and demons dominate the ground, and Kai is a forgotten existence from all human beings. However, after encountering the mysterious girl Rinne, Kai decides to break this rewritten destiny. In a world without heroes, he inherits the hero's sword and martial art and challenges the mighty enemy races who reign.\n\n(Source: Official site)", "Naze Boku no Sekai wo Daremo Oboeteinai no ka?", null, "なぜ僕の世界を誰も覚えていないのか？", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/107339/Naze_Boku_no_Sekai_wo_Daremo_Oboeteinai_no_ka", 9 },
                    { 107525, "Kemono Friends: Comic à la Carte - Japari Park-hen has been published in English by Yen Press from November 19, 2019 to October 20, 2020.", 62, new DateTime(2019, 3, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/227963.jpg", 33407, null, new DateTime(2017, 3, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An anthology comic of Kemono Friends by various mangaka.", "Kemono Friends: Comic à la Carte - Japari Park-hen", "Kemono Friends: À la Carte - Japari Park Edition", "けものフレンズ コミックアラカルト ジャパリパーク編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/107525/Kemono_Friends__Comic_à_la_Carte_-_Japari_Park-hen", 4 },
                    { 107562, "Kusuriya no Hitorigoto has been published in English as The Apothecary Diaries by Square Enix since December 8, 2020. It has also been published digitally by Square Enix through Manga UP! The series has also been released in Polish as Zapiski zielarki by Studio JG since April 23, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/201154.jpg", 86, 8.62m, new DateTime(2017, 5, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "In a certain imperial court, it has been a few months since a 17-year-old girl known as Maomao was kidnapped and forced to work as a low-level servant at the emperor's palace. Still, she manages to retain her curious and pragmatic spirit, planning to work until her years of servitude are over. One day, however, she catches wind of the fact that the emperor's two infants have fallen gravely ill. She decides to secretly take action, drawing on her experience as a pharmacist raised in the poor red-light district.  \n\nDespite Maomao's attempts to remain anonymous, she soon catches the eye of Jinshi, an influential eunuch who recognizes her talents. Maomao soon finds herself in the emperor's inner court, where she gradually makes a name for herself by utilizing her knowledge and eccentric personality to solve various medical mysteries.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kusuriya no Hitorigoto", "The Apothecary Diaries", "薬屋のひとりごと", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/107562/Kusuriya_no_Hitorigoto", null },
                    { 107908, "MF Ghost has been published digitally in English by Kodansha USA since January 11, 2022. The series has also been simulpub through K Manga.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/205248.jpg", 4038, 7.37m, new DateTime(2017, 9, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "By the 2020s, cars with internal combustion engines have largely been phased out, replaced by self-driving electric and fuel cell vehicles instead. Though these fossil fuel-running cars are at risk of disappearing completely, a dedicated group in Japan known as the MFG strives to maintain interest in them through road races streamed online. With 10 billion yen at stake and more than three hundred drivers competing, only the \"Godly Fifteen\"—the top 15 racers in the circuit—have a chance at advancing and taking the coveted prize.\n\nFresh off a plane from England, 19-year-old Kanata Rivington is eager to take on the fourth installment of the MFG competition. Trained at an elite driving school in his home country, the half-Japanese driver vies for the competition's top spot in his hand-me-down Toyota 86 GT. Despite the disadvantages that come with a dated car, the newcomer is determined to become one of this year's Godly Fifteen.\n\nKanata adopts his father's last name, taking on the moniker \"Kanata Katagiri.\" Conquering the Japanese racing circuit is only a stepping stone towards his real goal: discovering the whereabouts of his missing father.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "MF Ghost", "MF Ghost", "MFゴースト", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/107908/MF_Ghost", null },
                    { 108166, "Yari no Yuusha no Yarinaoshi has been published in English as The Reprise of the Spear Hero by One Peace Books since November 12, 2019.", 56, new DateTime(2023, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/204824.jpg", 8712, 7.01m, new DateTime(2017, 8, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Motoyasu Kitamura is summoned to another world to serve as the Spear Hero, but something eventually manages to kill him. When he dies Motoyasu suddenly finds himself back on the day he was first summoned to the new world―without losing any of his power! It's the start of a new game in god mode! This time he's determined to get things right―for the sake of his beloved Filo-tan, the magnificent filolials, and his \"father,\" the Shield Hero.\n\n(Source: One Peace Books)", "Yari no Yuusha no Yarinaoshi", "The Reprise of the Spear Hero", "槍の勇者のやり直し", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108166/Yari_no_Yuusha_no_Yarinaoshi", 11 },
                    { 108167, "Yari no Yuusha no Yarinaoshi has been published digitally in English by One Peace Books as The Reprise of the Spear Hero since October 16, 2018.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/200835.jpg", 5360, 7.25m, new DateTime(2017, 9, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Summoned to another world to serve as the Spear Hero, Motoyasu Kitamura is a pitiful young man who eventually finds himself only able to love filolials. But after being fatally injured in battle, Motoyasu wakes up yet again in the exact circumstances of when he was first summoned. It turns out that his spear possesses an ability known as Time Reversal! With his stats unaffected by the reset, Motoyasu decides to fight once more. His motivation: to once again see the smile of Filo, the filolial that he loves more than any other! Could this be considered the start of a new game in god mode?! The long-awaited otherworldly redemption fantasy begins!\n\n(Source: One Peace Books)", "Yari no Yuusha no Yarinaoshi", "The Reprise of the Spear Hero", "槍の勇者のやり直し", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108167/Yari_no_Yuusha_no_Yarinaoshi", null },
                    { 108177, "", null, new DateTime(2021, 8, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/198051.jpg", 137, 8.52m, new DateTime(2017, 7, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "\"It's chic to go saving a girl who has nothing to do with you every once in a while.\" Female students from Naoetsu High School have gone missing one after the other. When the mummified bodies of the girls are discovered, there's a very distinctive marking left on the napes of their necks...? Koyomi Araragi, now a first year university student, goes on the move to track down the culprit!\n\n(Source: Kodansha, Bakemonogatari Wikia)", "Monogatari Series: Monster Season", null, "〈物語〉シリーズ モンスターシーズン", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108177/Monogatari_Series__Monster_Season", 6 },
                    { 108199, "", 12, new DateTime(2017, 5, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/198596.jpg", 12480, 6.76m, new DateTime(2016, 6, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "At first glance, the Fukuoka city seems like a peaceful one, but under the surface, crime is running rampant. The city's Hakata ward is home to the professionals of the underworld: professional killers, detectives, informants, professional revenge seekers, those skilled in torture, and more. And according to urban legend, even a \"killer of professional killers\" exists in the city. When stories of the men in the underworld are told, a \"professional killer murder\" appears.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Hakata Tonkotsu Ramens", null, "博多豚骨ラーメンズ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108199/Hakata_Tonkotsu_Ramens", 2 },
                    { 108240, "Arifureta Nichijou de Sekai Saikyou has been published in English as Arifureta: I Heart Isekai by Seven Seas Entertainment since December 10, 2019.", 61, new DateTime(2023, 1, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/209378.jpg", 6061, 7.19m, new DateTime(2017, 7, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Hajime and the beautiful women around him pause their epic fantasy adventures for some slice-of-life comedy. Follow the everyday antics of the crew in this new collection of 4-panel manga!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Arifureta Nichijou de Sekai Saikyou", "Arifureta: I Heart Isekai", "ありふれた日常で世界最強", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108240/Arifureta_Nichijou_de_Sekai_Saikyou", 5 },
                    { 108274, "", 13, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/247364.jpg", 42260, null, new DateTime(2017, 5, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An anthology comic of Kemono Friends by various mangaka.", "Kemono Friends: Comic Anthology - Japari Man-hen", null, "けものフレンズ こみっくあんそろじー じゃぱりまん編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108274/Kemono_Friends__Comic_Anthology_-_Japari_Man-hen", 1 },
                    { 108306, "Seirei Gensouki has been published digitally in English as Seirei Gensouki: Spirit Chronicles by J-Novel Club since June 11, 2019.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/204985.jpg", 12291, 6.77m, new DateTime(2017, 7, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Amakawa Haruto is a young man who died before reuniting with his childhood friend who disappeared five years ago. Rio is a boy living in the slums who wants revenge for his mother who was murdered in front of him when he was five years old.\n\nEarth and another world. Two people with completely different backgrounds and values. For some reason, the memories and personality of Haruto who should've died is resurrected in Rio's body. As the two are confused over their memories and personalities fusing together, Rio (Haruto) decide to live in this new world.\n\nAlong with Haruto's memories, Rio awakens an unknown \"special power,\" and it seems that if he uses it well, he can live a better life. But before that, Rio encountered a kidnapping that turns out to be two princesses of the Bertram Kingdom that he lives in.\n\nAfter saving the princesses, Rio is given a scholarship to the Royal Academy, a school for the rich and powerful. Being a poor orphan in a school of nobles turns out to be an extremely detestable place to be.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Seirei Gensouki", "Seirei Gensouki: Spirit Chronicles", "精霊幻想記", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108306/Seirei_Gensouki", null },
