                    { 108725, "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e: √Horikita has been published digitally in English as Classroom of the Elite: Horikita by Seven Seas Entertainment since July 4, 2023.", 12, new DateTime(2018, 5, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/203312.jpg", 12037, 6.79m, new DateTime(2017, 6, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Suzune Horikita wants nothing to do with her annoying classmates. All she wants is her distant older brother, the student council president, to acknowledge her presence. Horikita turns to a student almost as antisocial as she is, Kiyotaka Ayanokouji, for help. Despite a rocky start, Horikita and Ayanokouji spark a friendship. But can their growing relationship survive the suffocating and cutthroat atmosphere of their elite school?\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e: √Horikita", "Classroom of the Elite: Horikita", "ようこそ実力至上主義の教室へ √堀北", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108725/Youkoso_Jitsuryoku_Shijou_Shugi_no_Kyoushitsu_e__√Horikita", 2 },
                    { 108906, "", 6, new DateTime(2017, 12, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/204863.jpg", 8410, 7.03m, new DateTime(2017, 9, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story takes place in Dragon Country. Nonoko is a newly appointed dentist and her mission is to protect the dragon, the guardian of the country, from tooth-cavity bacteria.\n\nOne day, amid increasingly fierce battles with the neighboring country, Nonoko finds on the dragon's tooth an unconscious boy soldier from the enemy country. His name is Bell, and he has been resurrected from inside the tooth by the dragon—a supernatural phenomenon that legend says occurs before a major disaster. As Nonoko and Bell go through a series of fierce battles, they eventually learn to accept their fate.\n\n(Source: Official website)", "Ryuu no Haisha", "The Dragon Dentist", "龍の歯医者", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/108906/Ryuu_no_Haisha", 1 },
