                    { 110668, "Kamisama Hajimemashita: Sonogo no Futari was published in English in a hardcover artbook that was bundled together with the limited edition of volume 25 of the main series.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/213115.jpg", 4176, 7.35m, new DateTime(2016, 12, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A special 32-page chapter included in the official fan book.", "Kamisama Hajimemashita: Sonogo no Futari", null, "神様はじめました その後の2人", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/110668/Kamisama_Hajimemashita__Sonogo_no_Futari", null },
                    { 110830, "", 9, new DateTime(2017, 11, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/232215.jpg", 5451, 7.24m, new DateTime(2017, 7, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A collection of short stories from the perspective of \"normal people\" who have encountered the Straw Hat Pirates.", "One Piece Novel: Mugiwara Stories", null, "ONE PIECE novel 麦わらストーリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/110830/One_Piece_Novel__Mugiwara_Stories", 1 },
                    { 110898, null, 3, new DateTime(2018, 2, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/204687.jpg", 17290, 6.38m, new DateTime(2017, 12, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Saint Seiya: Episode Zero", null, "聖闘士星矢 EPISODE ZERO", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/110898/Saint_Seiya__Episode_Zero", null },
                    { 110929, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/207249.jpg", 1831, 7.68m, new DateTime(2017, 8, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "In the East is a land ruled by an emperor, whose consorts and serving women live in a sprawling complex known as the hougong, the rear palace. Maomao, an unassuming girl raised in an unassuming town by her apothecary father, never imagined the rear palace would have anything to do with her—until she was kidnapped and sold into service there.\n\nThough she looks ordinary, Maomao has a quick wit, a sharp mind, and an extensive knowledge of medicine. That's her secret, until she encounters a resident of the palace at least as perceptive as she is: the head eunuch, Jinshi. He sees through Maomao's façade and makes her a lady-in-waiting to none other than the Emperor's favorite consort... so she can taste the lady's food for poison!\n\nAt her lady's side, Maomao starts to learn about everything that goes on in the rear palace—not all of it seemly. Can she ever lead a quiet life, or will her powers of deduction and insatiable curiosity bring her ever more adventures, and ever more dangers?\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Kusuriya no Hitorigoto: Maomao no Koukyuu Nazotoki Techou", null, "薬屋のひとりごと 猫猫の後宮謎解き手帳", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/110929/Kusuriya_no_Hitorigoto__Maomao_no_Koukyuu_Nazotoki_Techou", null },
                    { 111192, "Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo Gaiden: Hannin-tachi no Jikenbo originally ended with 10 volumes on April 15, 2020. Serialization resumed for 12 more chapters on March 2, 2022.", 136, new DateTime(2022, 5, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/204688.jpg", 23295, null, new DateTime(2017, 7, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off of Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo introducing a comedic look back at some of Kindaichi's old cases, but this time through the eyes of the criminals he's caught.", "Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo Gaiden: Hannin-tachi no Jikenbo", null, "金田一少年の事件簿外伝 犯人たちの事件簿", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111192/Kindaichi_Shounen_no_Jikenbo_Gaiden__Hannin-tachi_no_Jikenbo", 11 },
                    { 111225, "Nozomanu Fushi no Boukensha has been published digitally and physically in English as The Unwanted Undead Adventurer by J-Novel Club since November 12, 2019, and in print since September 21, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/210029.jpg", 4186, 7.35m, new DateTime(2017, 11, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Rentt Faina, a twenty-five-year-old adventurer, has been hacking away at monsters for a decade. However, without much talent for the job, Rentt finds himself stuck hunting slimes and goblins for meager amounts of coin every day. Little does he know, all this is about to change when he comes across a seemingly undiscovered path in the Labyrinth of the Moon's Reflection. What awaits him at the end of the path, however, is neither treasure nor riches, but a legendary dragon that wastes no time swallowing him whole! Waking up a short time later, Rentt finds himself not quite dead, but not very alive either—he is nothing more than a pile of bones! Armed with nothing but his trusty sword, tool belt, and ghoulish new looks, Rentt sets off on his quest as a newly reborn Skeleton to achieve Existential Evolution, hoping to one day return to civilization with a more human form.\n\nWill Rentt succeed, or will the labyrinth consume him for the rest of his un-death...?\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Nozomanu Fushi no Boukensha", "The Unwanted Undead Adventurer", "望まぬ不死の冒険者", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111225/Nozomanu_Fushi_no_Boukensha", null },
                    { 111453, "", 23, new DateTime(2019, 9, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/231226.jpg", 23375, null, new DateTime(2018, 1, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Inazuma Eleven Ares will be set in a parallel world, taking place after the events of the first game, and develop the story from the perspectives of three protagonists—Ryouhei Haizaki, Asuto Inamori, and Yuuma Nosaka.\n \nThe story revolves around a group of boys living on an island who love to play soccer. Their soccer club is suddenly abolished, and the only way they can regain it is to win the Football Frontier. Protagonist Asuto Inamori and company leave the island for Tokyo to attend Raimon Junior High School and take on the Football Frontier. But their first match is against the number one-ranked Seishou Gakuen.\n \n(Source: Gematsu)", "Inazuma Eleven: Ares no Tenbin", null, "イナズマイレブン アレスの天秤", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111453/Inazuma_Eleven__Ares_no_Tenbin", 4 },
                    { 111587, "Jaku-Chara Tomozaki-kun Comic has been published digitally in English as Bottom-Tier Character Tomozaki through Comikey since June 17, 2022, and by Square Enix through Manga UP!", 30, new DateTime(2021, 2, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/209980.jpg", 12556, 6.75m, new DateTime(2017, 12, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "With the username \"nanashi,\" Fumiya Tomozaki is the number one player in Japan in the online game \"Attack Family,\" also known as \"Tackfam.\" Despite having such a prestigious title, he struggles in high school due to a lack of social skills. He blames the perplexing mechanics and unjust rules of life for his lack of friends, forcing him to give up and consider himself the lowest-tier character in the \"game.\"\n\nFumiya was surprised to learn the identity of the number two Tackfam player after a fateful encounter—a popular, clever, and outgoing female classmate of his, Aoi Hinami. Aoi was taken aback to learn that the inept Fumiya was behind the username \"nanashi,\" and she became determined to assist him in winning the \"greatest game of all.\" With Aoi's help, Fumiya begins to progress in the wonderful \"game of life\" by overcoming the harsh challenges of social interaction and human relationships.\n\n(Source: Comikey Media)", "Jaku-Chara Tomozaki-kun Comic", "Bottom-Tier Character Tomozaki", "弱キャラ友崎くん-COMIC-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111587/Jaku-Chara_Tomozaki-kun_Comic", 6 },
                    { 111710, "Mazinger Z: Alter Ignition was published in Italian by Edizioni BD under the J-Pop imprint on September 27, 2018.", 5, new DateTime(2017, 11, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/222478.jpg", 23448, null, new DateTime(2017, 5, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A retelling of the origins of Mazinger Z.", "Mazinger Z: Alter Ignition", null, "マジンガーＺ アルターイグニッション", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111710/Mazinger_Z__Alter_Ignition", 1 },
                    { 111970, "", 5, new DateTime(1995, 9, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/290960.jpg", 23493, null, new DateTime(1994, 4, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Mad Wang 1160 takes place in the year UC 1160. The three main characters, Shiva Yips, Decoder S. Wallenstein and Mell Mekanika awake from cold sleep (cryonics) in each of their colonies and are swallowed up in the Earth vs. the Outer Space Alliance's battle.\n\n(Source: Gundam Wiki)", "Kyouka Ningen Monogatari: Mad Wang 1160", null, "強化人間物語 MAD WANG 1160", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111970/Kyouka_Ningen_Monogatari__Mad_Wang_1160", 1 },
                    { 111971, "", 11, new DateTime(1992, 5, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/290961.jpg", 23494, null, new DateTime(1991, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The story is set in U.C. 0088 on Island 7, an independent research colony used by Anaheim Electronics to test Mobile Suit technologies for Newtypes.\n\n(Source: Gundam Wiki)", "Kyouka Ningen Monogatari: Another Z Gundam Story", null, "強化人間物語 ANOTHER Z GUNDAM STORY", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/111971/Kyouka_Ningen_Monogatari__Another_Z_Gundam_Story", 1 },
                    { 112031, "Koukaku Kidoutai Shousetsu Anthology was published in English as The Ghost in the Shell: Five New Short Stories by Vertical Inc. on April 4, 2017.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/287133.jpg", 23501, null, new DateTime(2017, 3, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Neither a utopia nor a dystopia, it's still a world of nations at strife, as dominated by corporations as ever. Technology hasn't made humans nearly obsolete, but rather bettered us, if you will, attaching to our bodies and even brains as enhancements—for those who can afford it.\n\nComics artist Masamune Shirow's vision of our coming society, animated to global acclaim and finally the basis of a major Hollywood production, branches out in five original stories by some of the most beloved SF novelists working in Japan today. A standalone collection, it requires no familiarity with the franchise to be enjoyed but is indispensable for fans for its thoughtful exploration of the series' implications.\n\nWhile reality may never become virtual, it will be increasingly networked and augmented. Navigate herein age-old questions about man that will return, not so ironically, in full force: What is the self? Is there such a thing as the soul?\n\n(Source: Vertical Inc.)", "Koukaku Kidoutai Shousetsu Anthology", "The Ghost in the Shell: Five New Short Stories", "攻殻機動隊小説アンソロジー", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112031/Koukaku_Kidoutai_Shousetsu_Anthology", 1 },
                    { 112268, "Sono Bisque Doll wa Koi wo Suru ranked 16th in the 2020 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. The series has been published in English as My Dress-Up Darling by Square Enix since April 14, 2020. It has also been published digitally in English by the publisher through Manga UP! The manga has also been released in French by Kana since October 25, 2019; in German by Egmont Manga since October 7, 2020; in Polish by Studio JG since May 6, 2021; in Italian by J-POP since January 26, 2022; and in Spain and Brazilian Portuguese by Panini Comics since January 27, 2022, and February 3, 2023, respectively.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/215054.jpg", 751, 8m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Engrossed in the family business of traditional doll making, Wakana Gojou is a reserved high school freshman without friends. Harboring painful memories of a childhood friend's disdain toward his interest, Gojou cannot relate to his classmates and their pastimes, eventually isolating himself.\n\nGojou has yet to perfect his crafting of dolls' faces, but is exceptionally skilled at making their clothes. His finesse with the sewing machine is soon discovered by his beautiful classmate Marin Kitagawa, whose boldness and honesty Gojou both admires and envies. Instantly, she shares with Gojou her own hobby: she likes to cosplay as characters from erotic video games.\n\nHowever, Kitagawa cannot sew her own costumes, leading her to seek Gojou's expertise. Now, as he is dragged along to the charming girl's endless cosplay-related affairs, Kitagawa becomes his first friend who fully accepts him. Thus, although polar opposites, their relationship slowly blossoms through their aptitude in helping each other in the intricate world of cosplay.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Sono Bisque Doll wa Koi wo Suru", "My Dress-Up Darling", "その着せ替え人形〈ビスク・ドール〉は恋をする", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112268/Sono_Bisque_Doll_wa_Koi_wo_Suru", null },
                    { 112318, "Jigokuraku ranked 16th in the 2019 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. The series was simulpub in English as Hell's Paradise: Jigokuraku by VIZ Media since May 17, 2018. The volumes were published in English by VIZ Media under the VIZ Signature imprint from March 17, 2020, to March 15, 2022. It was also published in Polish as Piekielny Raj by Japonica Polonica Fantastica from May 9, 2019, to June 23, 2022.", 128, new DateTime(2021, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/208522.jpg", 381, 8.23m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Gabimaru the Hollow, a ninja of Iwagakure Village known for being cold and emotionless, was set up by his fellow ninja and is now on death row. Tired of killing and betrayal, he wants to die. However, no method of execution works on him because as much as the seemingly apathetic Gabimaru refuses to admit it, he does have a reason to live. He wants to return to his wife, who was the reason why he softened up and failed to be an effective assassin. Thus, he refuses to die.\n\nAsaemon the Decapitator, a famous executioner, sees this and has a proposal for the ninja. She wants Gabimaru to join an expedition to an island south of Japan in search of the elixir of life in exchange for a full pardon by the Shogunate. However, this island is not a normal island: it is believed to be Paradise.\n\nHowever the island is full of mysteries, and the exploring team—consisting of those marked for death—might not be fully prepared to handle them.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Jigokuraku", "Hell's Paradise: Jigokuraku", "地獄楽", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112318/Jigokuraku", 13 },
                    { 112322, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/210476.jpg", 6093, 7.19m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 22, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "This is the sequel to the popular Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo franchise, set 20 years after the original version.\n\nHajime is no longer a student detective, but is a poor office worker who has to deal with the daily pains of adulthood. No longer wanting to solve cases anymore, he keeps his head down and tries to go about his daily work as quietly as possible.\n\nBut crime never takes a break, and it isn't long before Kindaichi gets dragged into cases that occur around him. Starting off the new series, we revisit Uta Island, for the fourth edition of the Opera House Murder Case, where the Phantom of the Opera is planning a bloody revenge.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Kindaichi 37-sai no Jikenbo", null, "金田一37歳の事件簿", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112322/Kindaichi_37-sai_no_Jikenbo", null },
                    { 112744, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/209985.jpg", 7042, 7.12m, new DateTime(2017, 5, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The manga stars the black-silhouetted \"criminal\" who appears in Meitantei Conan series who represents the mystery culprits.", "Meitantei Conan: Hannin no Hanzawa-san", null, "名探偵コナン 犯人の犯沢さん", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112744/Meitantei_Conan__Hannin_no_Hanzawa-san", null },
                    { 112807, "Boku no Kokoro no Yabai Yatsu ranked third and ninth in the 2020 and 2021 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division, respectively. It also ranked first in the Best Web Manga category at the sixth Tsugi ni Kuru Manga Awards in 2020. The manga was nominated for the 13th Manga Taisho Award and placed 11th in the final ranking. The series has been published in English as The Dangers in My Heart by Seven Seas Entertainment since July 20, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/213349.jpg", 379, 8.24m, new DateTime(2018, 3, 7, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Kyoutaro Ichikawa may look like your average middle school student, but in his heart, he dreams of murder. Thus, it is no surprise that the one he wants to kill the most is never far off from his mind: the class idol, Anna Yamada.\n\nReading alone in his beloved school library, he inadvertently begins to rendezvous with Yamada, who comes to secretly gorge on her beloved candies and sweets. Through their interactions, Ichikawa discovers just how much of a ditz Yamada is, and cannot help but support her from the sidelines. Meanwhile, Yamada herself cannot help but tease Ichikawa relentlessly due to his flustered reactions.\n\nWith an array of heartwarming daily interactions, the distant bond between the two grows into something more than just library acquaintances. Perhaps, in time, Ichikawa will come to realize that his murderous desires have turned into something else entirely.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Boku no Kokoro no Yabai Yatsu", "The Dangers in My Heart", "僕の心のヤバイやつ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112807/Boku_no_Kokoro_no_Yabai_Yatsu", null },
                    { 112907, "Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou Zero was published in English as Arifureta: From Commonplace to World's Strongest Zero by Seven Seas Entertainment from September 10, 2019 to May 2, 2023.", 43, new DateTime(2022, 6, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/221478.jpg", 5682, 7.22m, new DateTime(2018, 2, 22, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Long before any child of Earth came to the world of Tortus, the Liberators fought their own war: a struggle against the gods themselves. Oscar Orcus was never the type to seek out that kind of conflict. He lives a simple life as a magical craftsman. But when the powerful magician Miledi Reisen barges into his life, he's swept up into the tides of history. When the two of them meet, sparks fly that will set the whole world ablaze!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Arifureta Shokugyou de Sekai Saikyou Zero", "Arifureta: From Commonplace to World's Strongest Zero", "ありふれた職業で世界最強 零", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/112907/Arifureta_Shokugyou_de_Sekai_Saikyou_Zero", 8 },
                    { 113010, "Bakemonogatari was published in English by Vertical from October 1, 2019 to August 20, 2024. It was also released in Spanish by Milky Way Ediciones from December 27, 2018, to February 28, 2024; and in Brazilian Portuguese by Panini Comics from September 5, 2019, to March 23, 2024.", 193, new DateTime(2023, 3, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/210355.jpg", 156, 8.49m, new DateTime(2018, 3, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Koyomi Araragi is no stranger to the abnormal. During the spring break of his third year in high school, a fateful encounter with vampire Kiss-Shot Acerola-Orion Heart-Under-Blade turns him into a vampire himself. Thrust into the world of oddities, Araragi finds himself catching classmate Hitagi Senjougahara when she falls down the school stairs one day—but something is amiss. After being confronted by the girl in question, Araragi learns that her weight was stolen by a mythical crab. In spite of Senjougahara's blunt threats, he manages to convince her to let him help. In need of a solution to an abnormal problem, the two visit the mysterious Meme Oshino, a wanderer who saved Araragi from his vampirism.\n\nBakemonogatari is a tale about the monsters that reside within everyone, but just how deep do they dwell in the people Araragi meets?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Bakemonogatari", "Bakemonogatari", "化物語", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/113010/Bakemonogatari", 22 },
                    { 113138, "As a part of the JUMP START initiative, the first three chapters of Jujutsu Kaisen were published in English in VIZ Media's digital Weekly Shonen Jump on the same day as the Japanese release. After, the series was added to the MANGA Plus simulpub service, and has been released in print by the same publisher since December 3, 2019. It has also been released in Brazilian Portuguese by Panini Comics since August 21, 2020; and in Polish by Waneko since May 5, 2021.", 271, new DateTime(2024, 9, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/210341.jpg", 291, 8.32m, new DateTime(2018, 3, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Hidden in plain sight, an age-old conflict rages on. Supernatural monsters known as Curses terrorize humanity from the shadows, and powerful humans known as Jujutsu sorcerers use mystical arts to exterminate them. When high school student Yuuji Itadori finds a dried-up finger of the legendary Curse Sukuna Ryoumen, he suddenly finds himself joining this bloody conflict.\n\nAttacked by a Curse attracted to the finger's power, Yuuji makes a reckless decision to protect himself, gaining the power to combat Curses in the process but also unwittingly unleashing the malicious Sukuna into the world once more. Though Yuuji can control and confine Sukuna to his own body, the Jujutsu world classifies Yuuji as a dangerous, high-level Curse who must be exterminated.\n\nDetained and sentenced to death, Yuuji meets Satoru Gojou—a teacher at Jujutsu High School—who explains that despite his imminent execution, there is an alternative for him. Being a rare vessel to Sukuna, if Yuuji were to die, then Sukuna would perish too. Therefore, if Yuuji were to consume the many other remnants of Sukuna, then Yuuji's subsequent execution would truly eradicate the malicious demon. Taking up this chance to make the world safer and live his life for a little longer, Yuuji enrolls in Tokyo Prefectural Jujutsu High School, jumping headfirst into a harsh and unforgiving battlefield.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Jujutsu Kaisen", "Jujutsu Kaisen", "呪術廻戦", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/113138/Jujutsu_Kaisen", 30 },
                    { 113275, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/231230.jpg", 23749, null, new DateTime(2018, 3, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The legendary team has returned!! Their opponent this time is Barcelona?!\n\n(Source: Shogakukan, translated)", "Inazuma Eleven: Reloaded", null, "イナズマイレブン リローデッド", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/113275/Inazuma_Eleven__Reloaded", null },
                    { 113491, "Sword Art Online: Integral Factor - Prologue Comic was digitally published in English in March 2018. It is a prologue of Bandai Namco Entertainment's Sword Art Online: Integral Factor mobile game.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/237620.jpg", 13118, 6.72m, new DateTime(2017, 9, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In 2022, a genius by the name of Akihiko Kayaba created the first FullDive VRMMORPG: Sword Art Online. However, this game has a terrifying secret: You can't log out until the game is beaten, and dying in game means death in real life... This is the story of a player trapped in this deadly game, dreaming of conquering Aincrad. Your story.\n\n(Source: Bandai Namco Entertainment)", "Sword Art Online: Integral Factor - Prologue Comic", "Sword Art Online: Integral Factor - Prologue Comic", "ソードアート・オンライン インテグラル・ファクター PROLOGUE COMIC", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/113491/Sword_Art_Online__Integral_Factor_-_Prologue_Comic", 1 },
                    { 113839, "", 12, new DateTime(2016, 10, 7, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/256721.jpg", 26824, null, new DateTime(2016, 6, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Zenji Banba and his partner Xianming Lin come to visit Tokyo City to see a baseball game when an unfortunate predicament leaves them with none of their possessions and money. Needing to make quick money, they take the request to hunt down a bounty hunter. Along their adventure in the ward of Ikebukuro they encounter the local residents, from the normal average high schooler or rowdy bounty hunters to the city legends that are the mischievous informant from Shinjuku and a super-human man in a bartender uniform.\n\n(Source: NovelUpdates)", "Durarara!! x Hakata Tonkotsu Ramens", null, "デュラララ!!×博多豚骨ラーメンズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/113839/Durarara_x_Hakata_Tonkotsu_Ramens", 1 },
                    { 114175, "Shin no Nakama ja Nai to Yuusha no Party wo Oidasareta node, Henkyou de Slow Life suru Koto ni Shimashita has been published in English as Banished from the Hero's Party, I Decided to Live a Quiet Life in the Countryside by Yen Press since April 5, 2022.", 74, new DateTime(2024, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/223659.jpg", 6542, 7.15m, new DateTime(2018, 5, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After finding himself unable to keep up with the hellish fighting on the front lines of the war against the demon lord's army, Red is finally kicked out of the Hero's party. Ashamed of his inadequacy, he moves to a distant frontier region where nobody would know his face or past. However, once he gets over the funk of having to leave his adventuring days behind, he's actually excited to begin a quiet life as an apothecary...which becomes a whole lot more lively when a former party member and actual princess, Rit, pays him an unexpected visit!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Shin no Nakama ja Nai to Yuusha no Party wo Oidasareta node, Henkyou de Slow Life suru Koto ni Shimashita", "Banished from the Hero's Party, I Decided to Live a Quiet Life in the Countryside", "真の仲間じゃないと勇者のパーティーを追い出されたので、辺境でスローライフすることにしました", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114175/Shin_no_Nakama_ja_Nai_to_Yuusha_no_Party_wo_Oidasareta_node_Henkyou_de_Slow_Life_suru_Koto_ni_Shimashita", 14 },
                    { 114219, "", 13, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/239136.jpg", 4880, 7.29m, new DateTime(2016, 12, 22, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An anthology revolving around Megumin and her daily activities.", "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! Megumin Anthology", null, "この素晴らしい世界に祝福を！　めぐみんアンソロジー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114219/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Shukufuku_wo_Megumin_Anthology", 1 },
                    { 114227, "Trinity Blood: Reborn on the Mars was left unfinished due to the death of author Sunao Yoshida. The first three volumes were published in English by Tokyopop from August 14, 2007 to November 3, 2009.", 32, new DateTime(2003, 10, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/259303.jpg", 23940, null, new DateTime(2001, 2, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "A mysterious terrorist organization is hell-bent on orchestrating a war between the New Human Empire and the Vatican. Special Ops AX Agent Abel Nightroad teams up with a spunky young novice named Esther to try and stop Gyula, the bloodthirsty Marquis of Hungary, from unleashing the legendary Star of Sorrow.Set against a neo-gothic backdrop, this second Trinity Blood series—connected to the Rage Against the Moons series—promises plenty of action and intrigue as Esther and Abel struggle to save the lives of humans and vampires alike!\n\n(Source: Tokyopop)", "Trinity Blood: Reborn on the Mars", "Trinity Blood: Reborn on the Mars", "トリニティ・ブラッド Reborn on the Mars", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114227/Trinity_Blood__Reborn_on_the_Mars", 6 },
                    { 114279, "Shin no Nakama ja Nai to Yuusha no Party wo Oidasareta node, Henkyou de Slow Life suru Koto ni Shimashita began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on October 21, 2017. A revised and illustrated version has been published by Kadokawa under its Kadokawa Sneaker Bunko label since June 1, 2018. The series has been published in English as Banished from the Hero's Party, I Decided to Live a Quiet Life in the Countryside by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since September 22, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/223658.jpg", 3898, 7.38m, new DateTime(2018, 5, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Red was once a member of the Hero's party, a powerful group destined to save the world from the evil forces of Taraxon, the Raging Demon Lord. That is, until one of his comrades kicked him out. Hoping to live the easy life on the frontier, Red's new goal is to open an apothecary. However, keeping the secret of his former life may not be as simple as he thinks. Especially when the beautiful Rit, an adventurer from his past, shows up and asks to move in with him!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Shin no Nakama ja Nai to Yuusha no Party wo Oidasareta node, Henkyou de Slow Life suru Koto ni Shimashita", "Banished from the Hero's Party, I Decided to Live a Quiet Life in the Countryside", "真の仲間じゃないと勇者のパーティーを追い出されたので、辺境でスローライフすることにしました", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114279/Shin_no_Nakama_ja_Nai_to_Yuusha_no_Party_wo_Oidasareta_node_Henkyou_de_Slow_Life_suru_Koto_ni_Shimashita", null },
                    { 114372, "Otousan wa Shinpaishou was originally published as a one-shot in the May 1983 issue of Ribon before official serialization began in the November 1984 issue. The series was adapted to a live-action drama series which aired for 5 episodes from April 12, 1994 to May 17, 1994.", 65, new DateTime(1988, 10, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/231011.jpg", 23969, null, new DateTime(1983, 4, 1, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "How much chaos can one meddling, overly worried father cause? In the case of Koutarou Sasaki, middle-aged widower consumed by his extreme worry for his teenage daughter Noriko, the answer is a lot. Noriko herself is only trying to live a normal high school life together with her boyfriend Kitano—a seemingly impossible task in the face of the increasingly bizarre incidents and situations her father's antics cause, all in the name of keeping his daughter off the delinquent path!\n\n(Source: MU)\n\nIncluded one-shots:\nVolume 6: Kojin Kyouju", "Otousan wa Shinpaishou", null, "お父さんは心配症", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114372/Otousan_wa_Shinpaishou", 6 },
                    { 114379, "", 60, new DateTime(2022, 5, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/211287.jpg", 3193, 7.46m, new DateTime(2018, 5, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga focuses on the life of the triple agent as he attempts to keep all his different roles in check.\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)", "Meitantei Conan: Zero no Tea Time", "Detective Conan: Zero's Tea Time", "名探偵コナン ゼロの日常〈ティータイム〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114379/Meitantei_Conan__Zero_no_Tea_Time", 6 },
                    { 114393, "Naze Boku no Sekai wo Daremo Oboeteinai no ka? has been published digitally in English as Why Does Nobody Remember Me in This World? by Kadokawa since October 23, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/210734.jpg", 7888, 7.06m, new DateTime(2018, 2, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "\"Why does no one remembers the true world...!\"\n\nThe era when the great race of the five tribes competing for hegemony on the ground ended with the victory of mankind led by hero Sid. However, that world was suddenly \"overwritten\" in front of a boy Kai. In the rewritten world, Kai saw the scene where humans lost to the five tribal wars because of the absence of hero Sid—here dragons and demons dominate the ground, and Kai is a forgotten existence from all human beings. However, after encountering the mysterious girl Rinne, Kai decides to break this rewritten destiny. In a world without heroes, he inherits the hero's sword and martial art and challenges the mighty enemy races who reign.\n\n(Source: Official site)", "Naze Boku no Sekai wo Daremo Oboeteinai no ka?", "Why Does Nobody Remember Me in This World?", "なぜ僕の世界を誰も覚えていないのか?", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114393/Naze_Boku_no_Sekai_wo_Daremo_Oboeteinai_no_ka", null },
                    { 114435, "Dino Getter was originally serialized on the Dynamic Planning website from April 24, 2014 to November 28, 2014. A compiled volume of the series was included with the Metamor-Force \"Jeegfried\" figure released on July 1, 2022.", 8, new DateTime(2014, 11, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/305597.jpg", 23977, null, new DateTime(2014, 4, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Dino Getter is a manga series by Kazumi Hoshi for the 40th anniversary of Getter Robo. It introduces the Dino Getter Robo in an original eight chapter story about a battle between the Dinosaur Empire.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Dino Getter", null, "ダイノゲッター", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114435/Dino_Getter", 1 },
                    { 114548, "Edens Zero has been published in English by Kodansha USA since November 6, 2018, and it was also simulpub.", 293, new DateTime(2024, 6, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/212094.jpg", 7269, 7.1m, new DateTime(2018, 6, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "On the planet of Granbell, Shiki has led an isolated life growing up as the only human in Granbell Kingdom—an amusement park operated by machines. However, that changes when Rebecca Bluegarden and her feline companion Happy arrive, unaware that they are the first to visit this abandoned amusement park in one hundred years. Hoping to make fun videos for their B-Cube channel, they instead find and befriend the socially awkward Shiki.\n\nWhen the machines make Granbell too dangerous for them, the trio flee and return to Rebecca and Happy's home planet, Blue Garden. There, Shiki registers as an adventurer for the Shooting Starlight guild and learns about the mysterious goddess, Mother. Curious about the familiar feeling he gets from her, he decides to set out on a journey to find her, a feat no one has ever accomplished. Opting to tag along, Rebecca and Happy help Shiki begin the search for Mother, shooting cool videos and making new friends along the way!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Edens Zero", "Edens Zero", "EDENS ZERO", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114548/Edens_Zero", 33 },
                    { 114586, "", 14, new DateTime(2018, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/215331.jpg", 4725, 7.3m, new DateTime(2017, 11, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Tanya Degurechaff is a reincarnated Japanese salesman-turned-sociopathic child soldier, forced by the almighty Being X to fight an endless war...\n\nBut soldiers need to eat, too. So join Tanya as she samples fine wartime meals.\n\n(Source: MangaDex)", "Youjo Senki Shokudou", null, "幼女戦記食堂", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114586/Youjo_Senki_Shokudou", 2 },
                    { 114664, "", 12, new DateTime(2019, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/217631.jpg", 3857, 7.39m, new DateTime(2018, 2, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After Wiz wastes all the money Vanir made from Kazuma's patents on high quality Manatite, Vanir is forced to take up a job in consulting to pay the monthly rent of the shop. Aqua couldn't fall asleep, and decided to invade Wiz's shop to inquire about her and Vanir's past. Various characters consult Vanir for help.\n\n(Source: CGtranslations)", "Kono Kamen no Akuma ni Soudan wo!", null, "この仮面の悪魔に相談を！", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114664/Kono_Kamen_no_Akuma_ni_Soudan_wo", 2 },
                    { 114679, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/306759.jpg", 24038, null, new DateTime(2013, 7, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A short story included with the limited-edition Blu-ray/DVD of Blue Exorcist: The Movie.", "Souvenir in Blue Exorcist: The Movie - Okumura Yukio Saiaku no Mikkakan", null, "Souvenir in BLUE EXORCIST THE MOVIE ～奥村雪男最悪の三日間～", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114679/Souvenir_in_Blue_Exorcist__The_Movie_-_Okumura_Yukio_Saiaku_no_Mikkakan", 1 },
                    { 114701, "Fairy Tail: 100 Years Quest has been published in English by Kodansha USA since August 20, 2019. The series has also been simulpub through K Manga.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/213604.jpg", 3137, 7.47m, new DateTime(2018, 7, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The 100 Years Quest: a mission so challenging and hazardous that it has remained unaccomplished for over a century. While countless mages have attempted to take on this gruelling objective, their results ended in either overwhelming defeat or worse. Nonetheless, Natsu Dragneel and his friends—Lucy Heartfilia, Gray Fullbuster, Erza Scarlet, and Wendy Marvell, along with the exceeds Happy and Charlés—ambitiously embark on the quest. \n\nA year after the Fairy Tail guild has overcome the diabolical forces of Acnologia and Zeref, Natsu and his team trek into the northern continent of Guiltina, where they seek out the employer of the 100 Years Quest and receive their nearly impossible mission: to seal away the Five Dragon Gods—a group of individuals with such vast power that, if left alone, could cause global devastation. Meanwhile, a spirited new member named Touka is recruited to Fairy Tail. Although her vibrant energy and passionate nature makes her perfect for the guild, there seems to be more to her than meets the eye.  \n\nDetermined to accomplish their seemingly insurmountable mission, Natsu and his friends begin their treacherous search for the Dragon Gods. However, once encountering a new dark guild named Diabolos, along with the newest recruit of Fairy Tail revealing her true colors, Natsu and his team will find that the 100 Years Quest isn't the only challenge they face.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Fairy Tail: 100 Years Quest", "Fairy Tail: 100 Years Quest", "FAIRY TAIL 100 YEARS QUEST", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114701/Fairy_Tail__100_Years_Quest", null },
                    { 114745, "Blue Lock won the 45th Kodansha Manga Awards in the Shounen category in 2021. The series has been published digitally in English by Kodansha Comics USA since March 16, 2021, and in print since June 21, 2022. The series has also been simulpub through K Manga. It has also been released in French by Pika Édition since June 2, 2021; in Italian by Panini Comics since July 29, 2021; and in Polish by Waneko since August 5, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/5/213340.jpg", 160, 8.48m, new DateTime(2018, 7, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After reflecting on the current state of Japanese soccer, the Japanese Football Association decides to hire the enigmatic and eccentric coach Jinpachi Ego to achieve their dream of winning the World Cup. Believing that Japan has lacked an egoistic striker hungry for goals, Jinpachi initiates the Blue Lock—a prison-like facility where three hundred talented strikers from high schools all over Japan are isolated and pitted against each other. The sole survivor of Blue Lock will earn the right to become the national team's striker, and those who are defeated shall be banned from joining the team forever. \n\nSelected to join this risky project is Yoichi Isagi, a striker who failed to bring his high school soccer team to the national tournament. After choosing to pass to a teammate who missed instead of scoring on his own, he could not help but wonder if the results would have been different had he been more selfish. Using this golden opportunity given by the Blue Lock Project, Yoichi aims to clear his doubts and chase his ultimate desire—to become the greatest striker in the world and lead Japan to World Cup glory.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Blue Lock", "Blue Lock", "ブルーロック", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114745/Blue_Lock", null },
                    { 114760, "Shokugeki no Sanji is a one-shot special written by Shokugeki no Souma creators Tsukuda Yuuto and Saeki Shun to celebrate the 21st anniversary of One Piece. A continuation was written to celebrate the series's 1000th chapter. It was published in English as One Piece: Shokugeki no Sanji by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on March 12, 2024.", 6, new DateTime(2022, 7, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/265963.jpg", 7209, 7.11m, new DateTime(2018, 7, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "On the morning before he meets the crew of the Straw Hat Pirates, young sous-chef Sanji enjoys a peaceful day at work onboard the floating restaurant Baratie. His momentary stasis is broken by the arrival of a food critic with gourmet tastes—a woman who is completely unimpressed with the food she's served by Baratie's staff.\n\nWith Baratie's head chef Zeff away on business, Sanji must deliver a meal capable of silencing the complaining critic before she can depart with a bad taste in her mouth.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Shokugeki no Sanji", "One Piece: Shokugeki no Sanji", "食戟のサンジ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114760/Shokugeki_no_Sanji", 1 },
                    { 114779, "Hazurewaku no \"Joutai Ijou Skill\" de Saikyou ni Natta Ore ga Subete wo Juurin suru made has been published digitally in English as Failure Frame: I Became the Strongest and Annihilated Everything With Low-Level Spells by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint since December 10, 2020, and in print since March 9, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/226074.jpg", 5078, 7.27m, new DateTime(2018, 7, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Abruptly catapulted into a fantasy world, Mimori Touka and his classmates have been summoned by the world’s resident goddess to serve as heroes. Luckily, most of the students display amazing skills upon arrival—except for Mimori, whose abilities bottom out at a measly E-rank. With no further use for him, the goddess banishes Mimori to a dungeon from which no one has ever returned alive. Yet, as it turns out, Mimori’s skills aren’t so much worthless as they are abnormal. Abnormally powerful, even. If Mimori can only claw his way back to the surface, nothing will stand in his way from getting revenge.\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Hazurewaku no \"Joutai Ijou Skill\" de Saikyou ni Natta Ore ga Subete wo Juurin suru made", "Failure Frame: I Became the Strongest and Annihilated Everything With Low-Level Spells", "ハズレ枠の【状態異常スキル】で最強になった俺がすべてを蹂躙するまで", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114779/Hazurewaku_no_Joutai_Ijou_Skill_de_Saikyou_ni_Natta_Ore_ga_Subete_wo_Juurin_suru_made", null },
                    { 114787, null, null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/210424.jpg", 501, 8.15m, new DateTime(2018, 7, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, null, "Shin High School DxD", null, "真ハイスクールD×D", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114787/Shin_High_School_DxD", null },
                    { 114862, null, 62, new DateTime(2001, 4, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/306013.jpg", 24059, null, new DateTime(1994, 9, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Kindaichi Shounen no Jikenbo", "The New Kindaichi Files", "金田一少年の事件簿", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114862/Kindaichi_Shounen_no_Jikenbo", 9 },
                    { 114892, "Fairy Tail: Happy no Daibouken was published digitally in English as Fairy Tail: Happy's Heroic Adventure by Kodansha USA from September 17, 2019 to February 16, 2021.", 80, new DateTime(2020, 4, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/219513.jpg", 14075, 6.65m, new DateTime(2018, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "One day, while Happy and Natsu are on a quest, the big face of an old man appears in the sky. When they are spotted by the mysterious face, it captures them both in its mouth, but then spits Natsu out, resulting in only Happy being eaten. Regaining consciousness, Happy notices that he is in a completely different world—populated only by talking animals. He proceeds to meet Detective Bull, who explains that in this place, humans and magic exist only in fairy tales. Desperately trying to escape and return home, he is captured by the Bull. However, to his surprise, all the villagers are referring to him as Lord Happy!\n\nHappy meets Elder Tortoise, who tells him a tale that has been passed down for generations. Legend says that an animal with blue hair and white wings is to be the hero and savior of this village called Animar. The hero will be sent by an angel and fall down from the sky. Additionally, Elder Tortoise has been safekeeping an item called a Smile Heart, which only the hero is capable of using. After each heroic deed performed, the Smile Heart will increase in power.\n\nHappy realizes that this item may be the only way to take him home, so he affirms that he is the hero of legend. However, Animar is a very peaceful place with no disasters or monsters to speak of. With no idea what lies ahead of him, he needs to find a way to complete the Smile Heart and return home to everybody in Fairy Tail.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Fairy Tail: Happy no Daibouken", "Fairy Tail: Happy's Heroic Adventure", "FAIRY TAIL ハッピーの大冒険", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114892/Fairy_Tail__Happy_no_Daibouken", 8 },
                    { 114925, "Sokushi Cheat ga Saikyou sugite, Isekai no Yatsura ga Marude Aite ni Naranai n desu ga. ΑΩ has been published digitally in English as My Instant Death Ability Is So Overpowered, No One in This Other World Stands a Chance Against Me! —AΩ— by J-Novel Club since September 28, 2021, and in print by Yen Press under the J-Novel Club imprint since June 20, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/216485.jpg", 11520, 6.82m, new DateTime(2018, 3, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After waking up to absolute chaos and carnage while on a school trip, Yogiri Takatou discovers that everyone in his class has been transported to another world! He had somehow managed to sleep through the entire ordeal himself, missing out on the Gift—powers bestowed upon the others by a mysterious Sage who appeared to transport them. Even worse, he and another classmate were ruthlessly abandoned by their friends, left as bait to distract a nearby dragon. Although not terribly bothered by the thought of dying, he reluctantly decides to protect his lone companion. After all, a lowly Level 1000 monster doesn't stand a chance against his secret power to invoke Instant Death with a single thought! If he can stay awake long enough to bother using it, that is...\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Sokushi Cheat ga Saikyou sugite, Isekai no Yatsura ga Marude Aite ni Naranai n desu ga. ΑΩ", "My Instant Death Ability Is So Overpowered, No One in This Other World Stands a Chance Against Me! —AΩ—", "即死チートが最強すぎて、異世界のやつらがまるで相手にならないんですが。－AΩ－", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114925/Sokushi_Cheat_ga_Saikyou_sugite_Isekai_no_Yatsura_ga_Marude_Aite_ni_Naranai_n_desu_ga_ΑΩ", null },
                    { 114927, "", 38, new DateTime(2018, 12, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/231233.jpg", 24080, null, new DateTime(2018, 4, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An official Inazuma Eleven spin-off series—Ryouhei Haizaki's story starts here! Read about his life, from his first encounter with the genius playmaker Yuuto Kidou, to his daily shenanigans with his teammates—the other members of the Seishou Eleven (not to mention, guest appearances from popular characters of the Inazuma Eleven series). Chock full of scenes that are not shown in the anime, the magic of Inapen starts here...!\n\n(Source: MU)", "Inazuma Eleven: Penguin wo Tsugu Mono", null, "イナズマイレブン～ペンギンを継ぐ者～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114927/Inazuma_Eleven__Penguin_wo_Tsugu_Mono", 3 },
                    { 114989, "", 27, new DateTime(2020, 5, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/217951.jpg", 1899, 7.67m, new DateTime(2018, 2, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In these new adventures, Megumin wants to become a thief after meeting a famous group of thieves who managed to steal a treasure from the royal family.\n\nAccompanied by Yunyun, Cecily, and the mysterious Alice they will try to help the fatherless and the widow by robbing the corrupted and other wicked nobles.\n\nHowever, as usual, instead of honors, it is mainly the problems that they obtain. Will Megumin help her neighbor like a real thief? And above all, will she meet her models again?\n\n(Source: toshokan.moe)", "Zoku Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Bakuen wo!", null, "続・この素晴らしい世界に爆焔を！", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/114989/Zoku_Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Bakuen_wo", 4 },
                    { 115017, null, 6, new DateTime(2018, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/217644.jpg", 8994, 6.99m, new DateTime(2018, 4, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Kaichou Senkyo-hen", null, "魔法科高校の劣等生 会長選挙編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115017/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Kaichou_Senkyo-hen", 1 },
                    { 115498, "Mushoku Tensei: Roxy datte Honki desu was published in English as Mushoku Tensei: Roxy Gets Serious by Seven Seas Entertainment from April 30, 2019 to September 10, 2024.", 64, new DateTime(2023, 7, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/298290.jpg", 2395, 7.58m, new DateTime(2017, 12, 20, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Roxy's life is a lonely one—out of all her tribe, she's the only one without the power of telepathy. Her days pass in silence, while people speak words she can never hear. But when she saves the life of a wandering witch, Roxy gets the chance of a lifetime: the opportunity to study as a magician's apprentice, and leave her strange home behind!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Mushoku Tensei: Roxy datte Honki desu", "Mushoku Tensei: Roxy Gets Serious", "無職転生～ロキシーだって本気です～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115498/Mushoku_Tensei__Roxy_datte_Honki_desu", 12 },
                    { 115579, "", 13, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/223610.jpg", 24179, null, new DateTime(2018, 1, 10, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An anthology comic of the fictitious series Hoshi-iro GirlDrop by various mangaka.", "Hoshi-iro Girldrop: Comic Anthology", null, "星色ガールドロップ コミックアンソロジー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115579/Hoshi-iro_Girldrop__Comic_Anthology", 1 },
                    { 115627, "", 49, new DateTime(2019, 6, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/222839.jpg", 24185, null, new DateTime(2018, 6, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga revolves around a normal student that looks like the popular One Piece character Koby.\n\nIncluded one-shot:\nVolume 3: Chiyoko-chan wa Dojicchau", "One Piece: Koby-ni no Kobiyama - Uri Futatsunagi no Daihihou", null, "ONE PIECE コビー似の小日山 〜ウリふたつなぎの大秘宝〜", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115627/One_Piece__Koby-ni_no_Kobiyama_-_Uri_Futatsunagi_no_Daihihou", 3 },
                    { 115710, "Jujutsu Kaisen 0: Tokyo Toritsu Jujutsu Koutou Senmon Gakkou is the prototype serialization of Jujutsu Kaisen. The story remains canon to the main series and it features a different central cast. Character designs used in this prototype were later altered in the main series; for instance, Toge Inumaki's initial design was later used for Jujutsu Kaisen's main protagonist Yuuji Itadori, while Toge underwent a redesign. It was published in English as Jujutsu Kaisen 0 by VIZ Media under the Shounen Jump imprint on January 5, 2021.", 4, new DateTime(2017, 7, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/219336.jpg", 615, 8.08m, new DateTime(2017, 4, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Yuuta Okkotsu is haunted. Ever since his childhood friend Rika died in a traffic accident, her ghost has stuck with him. But her spirit does not appear as the sweet girl Yuuta once knew. Instead, she manifests as a monstrous and powerful entity who fiercely protects him. Unable to control Rika's violent behavior, Yuuta is helpless to stop the bloodshed that follows from her brutal vengeance. As a result, when apprehended by \"Jujutsu\" sorcerers—the secret guardians of the world, trained to combat forces like Rika—Yuuta wishes to be completely isolated so that no one else can get hurt.\n\nYet his apprehender, the master sorcerer Satoru Gojou, has different plans for him: he will join Tokyo Prefectural Jujutsu High School and learn to control Rika in order to help people. Now a first-year at this school, Yuuta starts to learn Jujutsu arts and combat malignant beings. Alongside his new classmates Maki Zenin, a Jujutsu weapons expert; Toge Inumaki, a spellcaster who uses his words as weapons; and Panda, a seemingly walking and talking panda bear, Yuuta begins to find his place in the world and, for once, to feel comfortable with his abilities. However, as his training progresses, Yuuta comes to learn that the dangers of the Jujutsu world go far beyond that of wicked spirits.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Jujutsu Kaisen 0: Tokyo Toritsu Jujutsu Koutou Senmon Gakkou", "Jujutsu Kaisen 0", "呪術廻戦 0 東京都立呪術高等専門学校", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115710/Jujutsu_Kaisen_0__Tokyo_Toritsu_Jujutsu_Koutou_Senmon_Gakkou", 1 },
                    { 115713, "", 15, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/309553.jpg", 24204, null, new DateTime(2018, 8, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A novelization of the first Nanatsu no Taizai movie.", "Shousetsu Gekjouban Nanatsu no Taizai: Tenkuu no Torawarebito", null, "小説 劇場版 七つの大罪 天空の囚われ人", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115713/Shousetsu_Gekjouban_Nanatsu_no_Taizai__Tenkuu_no_Torawarebito", 1 },
