                    { 115900, null, 23, new DateTime(2020, 6, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/221788.jpg", 9273, 6.97m, new DateTime(2018, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Tate no Yuusha no Toaru Ichinichi", null, "盾の勇者のとある一日", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115900/Tate_no_Yuusha_no_Toaru_Ichinichi", 3 },
                    { 115922, "Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute! has been published in English as The Eminence in Shadow by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since August 11, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/269801.jpg", 184, 8.45m, new DateTime(2018, 11, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Shadowbrokers are those who go unnoticed, posing as unremarkable people, when in truth, they control everything from behind the scenes. Sid wants to be someone just like that more than anything, and something as insignificant as boring reality isn't going to get in his way! He trains in secret every single night, preparing for his eventual rise to power—only to denied his destiny by a run-of-the-mill (yet deadly) traffic accident. But when he wakes up in a another world and suddenly finds himself at the head of an actual secret organization doing battle with evil in the shadows, he'll finally get a chance to act out all of his delusional fantasies!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute!", "The Eminence in Shadow", "陰の実力者になりたくて！", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115922/Kage_no_Jitsuryokusha_ni_Naritakute", null },
                    { 115996, "Beast Complex has been published in English by VIZ Media under their VIZ Signature imprint since March 16, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/220754.jpg", 2256, 7.6m, new DateTime(2016, 3, 2, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "A tiger and a beaver who grew up together defy peer pressure to end their friendship and join forces to fight injustice. A camel journalist who passed judgment on carnivores for years spends a life-changing night with a seductive wolf. A crocodile and a gazelle must find a way to work together as chef and assistant on a cooking show with flagging ratings. A fox and a chameleon wrestle with stereotypes about each other—and themselves. And much more...\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Beast Complex", "Beast Complex", "BEAST COMPLEX", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/115996/Beast_Complex", null },
                    { 116216, "Overlord: Prologue was included with volumes 4 and 6 of the limited-edition Blu-Ray/DVDs of the first season of Overlord.", null, new DateTime(2016, 2, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/266202.jpg", 24277, null, new DateTime(2015, 12, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Overlord: Prologue is a short story that takes place before Yggdrasil's final days. It tells the story about the founding of the guild \"Ainz Ooal Gown,\" Momonga becoming a guildmaster and the conquering of the Great Tomb of Nazarick.", "Overlord: Prologue", null, "オーバーロード プロローグ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116216/Overlord__Prologue", 2 },
                    { 116463, "Fairy Tail: City Hero was published digitally in English by Kodansha USA from September 24, 2019 to August 11, 2020.", 46, new DateTime(2019, 11, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/219511.jpg", 9260, 6.97m, new DateTime(2018, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spinoff from the Fairy Tail universe—with Lucy now on assignment as a police officer—and lots of your old friends appearing in an unexpected new setting! The Magic Police can handle any case! A heartwarming police story!! The members of Fairy Tail are now police officers! Rookie cop Lucy has just been assigned to Team Fairy Tail, a special unit of the Magnolia Police Department. Together with its completely over-the-top members, including Natsu, she'll protect Fiore City from wrongdoers like motorcycle gangs, stalkers, bank robbers, and masked thieves!! The curtain rises on a Magic Police story featuring the all-star cast of Fairy Tail!\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)", "Fairy Tail: City Hero", "Fairy Tail: City Hero", "FAIRY TAIL CITY HERO", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116463/Fairy_Tail__City_Hero", 4 },
                    { 116651, "Overlord: Fushisha no Oh! has been published in English as Overlord: The Undead King Oh! by Yen Press since November 12, 2019.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/221258.jpg", 5991, 7.2m, new DateTime(2017, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "A compilation of non-canon short stories that revolve around the interactions between the members of the Great Tomb of Nazarick.", "Overlord: Fushisha no Oh!", "Overlord: The Undead King Oh!", "オーバーロード 不死者のOh!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116651/Overlord__Fushisha_no_Oh", null },
                    { 116678, null, 125, new DateTime(1994, 6, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/259304.jpg", 24335, null, new DateTime(1993, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Kidou Senshi V Gundam", "Mobile Suit V Gundam", "機動戦士Vガンダム", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116678/Kidou_Senshi_V_Gundam", 5 },
                    { 116772, "Kono Yuusha ga Ore Tueee Kuse ni Shinchou sugiru was published in English as The Hero Is Overpowered but Overly Cautious by Yen Press from February 4, 2020 to October 24, 2023.", 36, new DateTime(2022, 10, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/221749.jpg", 7109, 7.11m, new DateTime(2018, 11, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In the celestial realm, deities oversee countless worlds in need of help; a goddess's task is to summon heroes and aid their quest to defeat the evil in each. Rookie goddess Ristarte, however, has been dealt a terrible hand: she must save Gaeabrande, a world labeled with the S-rank difficulty. While sifting through the hero resumés, she comes across a sheet detailing the abilities of a certain Seiya Ryuuguuin and is astonished by his ridiculously high stats. An elated Ristarte wastes no time in summoning Seiya to the celestial realm, failing to notice the comment on his personality: unbelievably cautious.\n\nRistarte soon despairs at his bizarre insistence on caution. He has no qualms with unleashing his most powerful ability to vaporize a weak slime, buying out a pharmacy's entire stock of potions, or refusing to do battle unless he is 600% certain of the outcome. However, Seiya's rabid obsession with safety might just be what is needed to save Gaeabrande.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kono Yuusha ga Ore Tueee Kuse ni Shinchou sugiru", "The Hero Is Overpowered but Overly Cautious", "この勇者が俺TUEEEくせに慎重すぎる", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116772/Kono_Yuusha_ga_Ore_Tueee_Kuse_ni_Shinchou_sugiru", 6 },
                    { 116778, "Chainsaw Man ranked fourth and first in the 2020 and 2021 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division, respectively. The series was nominated for the 13th Manga Taisho Award in 2020. In 2021, it won the 66th Shogakukan Manga Award in the Shounen category, along with Karakai Jouzu no Takagi-san. As part of the JUMP START initiative, the first three chapters of Chainsaw Man were published in English in VIZ Media's digital Weekly Shounen Jump on the same day as the Japanese release. It has been published digitally as an English simulpub through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since October 6, 2020. The manga has also been released in German by Egmont since October 6, 2020. The first part of the series ended with 97 chapters on December 14, 2020. Serialization of the second part began on Shounen Jump+ with the release of chapter 98 on July 13, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/216464.jpg", 56, 8.71m, new DateTime(2018, 12, 2, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Denji has a simple dream—to live a happy and peaceful life, spending time with a girl he likes. This is a far cry from reality, however, as Denji is forced by the yakuza into killing devils in order to pay off his crushing debts. Using his pet devil Pochita as a weapon, he is ready to do anything for a bit of cash.\n\nUnfortunately, he has outlived his usefulness and is murdered by a devil in contract with the yakuza. However, in an unexpected turn of events, Pochita merges with Denji's dead body and grants him the powers of a chainsaw devil. Now able to transform parts of his body into chainsaws, a revived Denji uses his new abilities to quickly and brutally dispatch his enemies. Catching the eye of the official devil hunters who arrive at the scene, he is offered work at the Public Safety Bureau as one of them. Now with the means to face even the toughest of enemies, Denji will stop at nothing to achieve his simple teenage dreams.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Chainsaw Man", "Chainsaw Man", "チェンソーマン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116778/Chainsaw_Man", null },
                    { 116786, "", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/307327.jpg", 24350, null, new DateTime(2017, 3, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A side story focusing on the backstory of Eiji and Yuna which was given to those who watched Sword Art Online the Movie: Ordinal Scale in its third week of screening.", "Sword Art Online: Hopeful Chant", null, "ソードアート・オンライン ホープフル・チャント", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116786/Sword_Art_Online__Hopeful_Chant", 1 },
                    { 116788, "", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/307329.jpg", 24351, null, new DateTime(2017, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A sequel to the Sword Art Online the Movie: Ordinal Scale which was included with the limited edition Blu-Ray and DVD release of the movie.", "Sword Art Online: Cordial Chords", null, "ソードアート･オンライン コーディアル・コード", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116788/Sword_Art_Online__Cordial_Chords", 1 },
                    { 116808, "Giji Harem is a web manga released on the author's Twitter account from June 20, 2018 to March 5, 2021. Official serialization started in Gessan on January 12, 2019.", 157, new DateTime(2021, 3, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/219464.jpg", 1128, 7.85m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Eiji Kitahama, a second year high school student, just wants to be popular. To help him realize this dream, Rin Nanakura, his junior in the drama club, uses her acting skills to create a harem of loving girls for him. Though the various \"girls\" all show fondness toward Eiji, the affection of the actress behind them is very real. Rin's colorful acting continuously delights Eiji, but will the starlet herself ever make her way into his heart?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Giji Harem", null, "疑似ハーレム", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116808/Giji_Harem", 6 },
                    { 116880, "Mato Seihei no Slave has been published in English as Chained Soldier by Yen Press since August 16, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/260475.jpg", 2197, 7.61m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After his high school graduation, Yuuki Wakura realizes it has been five years since his sister's disappearance during a \"Mato disaster.\" Throughout Japan, mysterious entrances have opened to a dimension called \"Mato\"—a demonic metropolis filled with disastrous monsters known as the \"Shuuki\" that threaten the safety of humans. However, a new hope arose, as the discovery of a Mato fruit that grants supernatural abilities exclusively to women allowed them to fight against the Shuuki. Due to this, a new matriarchal government was formed, establishing a female organization called the Demon Defense Force, which caused men to fall to the bottom of society.\n\nWhen Yuuki suddenly finds himself in Mato, he is unable to escape on his own. But just as he anticipates a gruesome end by the Shuuki, a girl in a militia outfit appears and protects him. As the chief of the Seventh Unit of the Demon Defense Force, Kyouka Uzen is ambitious yet devalued by her own peers due to her power being deemed unusual. Now in a life-or-death situation, Kyouka takes the opportunity to find out the true potential of her superpower by using Yuuki: in order to defeat the Shuuki, he has to become her slave.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Mato Seihei no Slave", "Chained Soldier", "魔都精兵のスレイブ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116880/Mato_Seihei_no_Slave", null },
                    { 116905, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/229357.jpg", 7768, 7.07m, new DateTime(2006, 12, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In Karakura Town, there has been a sudden outbreak of unidentifiable spirits called \"blanks\" (vacant souls) while in the skies of Soul Society, the real world has been reflected. A mysterious female shinigami called Senna has appeared before Ichigo along with a man named Ganryu, leading a group called the \"Dark Ones.\"\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Gekijouban Bleach: Memories of Nobody", null, "劇場版BLEACH ―MEMORIES OF NOBODY―", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116905/Gekijouban_Bleach__Memories_of_Nobody", 1 },
                    { 116943, "Kimi to Boku no Saigo no Senjou, Aruiwa Sekai ga Hajimaru Seisen has been published in English as Our Last Crusade or the Rise of a New World by Yen Press since November 5, 2019.", 43, new DateTime(2021, 3, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/223262.jpg", 10215, 6.91m, new DateTime(2018, 5, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Empire endowed with an advanced level of knowledge, and the Nebulis Imperial Household Agency feared as the 'Country of Witches.' On the long-lasting battlefield between these two countries, a boy and girl met.\n\nThe ice witch princess praised as the strongest in all of the Imperial Household Agency―Aliceliese.\n\nThe swordsman who became the ultimate force on the battlefield at the youngest age throughout all the Empire's history―Iska.\n\n\"If you capture me, your dream may also be fulfilled.\"\n\"Likewise, if you defeat me, it will become a step in the unification of your world.\"\n\nThe two arch enemies were to kill each other. However, the boy had his heart stolen by the girl's beauty and nobility. And the girl was attracted to the boy's strength and way of living. Even if walking alongside one another would not be permitted and the only path before them was to defeat each other.\n\n(Source: Novel Updates)", "Kimi to Boku no Saigo no Senjou, Aruiwa Sekai ga Hajimaru Seisen", "Our Last Crusade or the Rise of a New World", "キミと僕の最後の戦場、あるいは世界が始まる聖戦", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116943/Kimi_to_Boku_no_Saigo_no_Senjou_Aruiwa_Sekai_ga_Hajimaru_Seisen", 7 },
                    { 116987, "", 10, new DateTime(2018, 4, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/232888.jpg", null, 6.84m, new DateTime(2017, 3, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Each chapter features a heroine of Fuuka and the main character Yuu Haruna displaying their feelings for each other.", "Fuuka: Yacchau!? Heroine to no Mousou Hatsutaiken - Special Edition", null, "風夏 ヤっちゃう!? ヒロインとの妄想初体験 SPECIAL EDITION", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/116987/Fuuka__Yacchau_Heroine_to_no_Mousou_Hatsutaiken_-_Special_Edition", 1 },
