                    { 117445, "Little Witch Academia: Detarame Majo to Yousei no Kuni was published in English as Little Witch Academia: The Nonsensical Witch and the Country of the Fairies by Yen Press on August 6, 2019.", 9, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/269566.jpg", 24422, null, new DateTime(2017, 4, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "I'm Atsuko Kagari, but you can call me Akko! It's been my lifelong dream to become. Awitch, and I came all the way from Japan to attend the prestigious Luna Nova Witchcraft Academy. But then I found out all we ever do is study, study, study! I swear! What's with this place?!\n\nWell, we finally left our desks to go on a class trip to Doras Hill, and things were going smoothly for once!...That is, until I met the guardian of the hill, Sifla. Wait, whadja say, Sifla? Did your cat and dog run away from home? Don't worry. Lotte, Sucy, and I will find them for you! After all, we're three hearts that beat as one, right?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Little Witch Academia: Detarame Majo to Yousei no Kuni", "Little Witch Academia: The Nonsensical Witch and the Country of the Fairies", "リトルウィッチアカデミア でたらめ魔女と妖精の国", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117445/Little_Witch_Academia__Detarame_Majo_to_Yousei_no_Kuni", 1 },
                    { 117544, "Super Dragon Ball Heroes: Universe Mission!! is an adaptation of the Super Dragon Ball Heroes arcade game.", 12, new DateTime(2020, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/228479.jpg", 17662, 6.33m, new DateTime(2018, 4, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The plot involves the mysterious Fu, who after kidnapping Future Trunks, lures Goku and Vegeta to the Prison Planet, an experimental area which Fu created and has filled with strong warriors from different planets and eras in order to force them into a game where they must collect the seven Special Dragon Balls if they wish to escape.\n\n(Source: Dragon Ball Wiki)", "Super Dragon Ball Heroes: Universe Mission!!", null, "スーパードラゴンボールヒーローズ ユニバースミッション!!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117544/Super_Dragon_Ball_Heroes__Universe_Mission", 2 },
                    { 117572, "", 8, new DateTime(2018, 8, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/240770.jpg", 24439, null, new DateTime(2018, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Manga adaptation of the twenty-first Meitantei Conan movie.", "Meitantei Conan: Karakurenai no Love Letter", "Detective Conan the Movie: The Crimson Love Letter", "名探偵コナン から紅の恋歌〈ラブレター〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117572/Meitantei_Conan__Karakurenai_no_Love_Letter", 2 },
                    { 117692, "", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/290005.jpg", 24472, null, new DateTime(2018, 11, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "U.C. 0097, one year after the opening of \"Laplace's Box.\" Despite the revelation of the Universal Century Charter that acknowledges the existence and rights of Newtypes, the framework of the world has not been greatly altered.\n\nThe conflict later dubbed the \"Laplace Incident\" is thought to have ended with the downfall of the Neo Zeon remnants known as the Sleeves. In its final battle, two full psycho-frame mobile suits displayed power beyond human understanding. The white unicorn and the black lion were sealed away to remove this danger from people's consciousness, and they should now be completely forgotten.\n\nHowever, the RX-0 Unicorn Gundam 03, which disappeared two years earlier, is now about to show itself in the Earth Sphere once more. A golden phoenix... named Phenex.\n\n(Source: gundam.info)", "Shousetsu Kidou Senshi Gundam NT", "Mobile Suit Gundam Narrative", "小説 機動戦士ガンダムNT〈ナラティブ〉", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117692/Shousetsu_Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_NT", 1 },
                    { 117693, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/227250.jpg", 24473, null, new DateTime(2018, 11, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "U.C. 0097, one year after the opening of \"Laplace's Box.\" Despite the revelation of the Universal Century Charter that acknowledges the existence and rights of Newtypes, the framework of the world has not been greatly altered.\n\nThe conflict later dubbed the \"Laplace Incident\" is thought to have ended with the downfall of the Neo Zeon remnants known as the Sleeves. In its final battle, two full psycho-frame mobile suits displayed power beyond human understanding. The white unicorn and the black lion were sealed away to remove this danger from people's consciousness, and they should now be completely forgotten.\n\nHowever, the RX-0 Unicorn Gundam 03, which disappeared two years earlier, is now about to show itself in the Earth Sphere once more. A golden phoenix... named Phenex.\n\n(Source: gundam.info)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam NT", "Mobile Suit Gundam Narrative", "機動戦士ガンダムNT〈ナラティブ〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117693/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_NT", null },
                    { 117695, "", 30, new DateTime(2021, 8, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/214835.jpg", 24475, null, new DateTime(2018, 4, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off about Umibouzu's work at the Cat's Eye cafe in modern-day Shinjuku.", "City Hunter Gaiden: Ijuuin Hayato-shi no Heion naranu Nichijou", "Mr. Hayato Ijuin's not so peaceful life", "CITY HUNTER外伝 伊集院隼人氏の平穏ならぬ日常", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117695/City_Hunter_Gaiden__Ijuuin_Hayato-shi_no_Heion_naranu_Nichijou", 5 },
                    { 117886, "Sekai Saikou no Ansatsusha, Isekai Kizoku ni Tensei suru has been published in English as The World's Finest Assassin Gets Reincarnated in Another World as an Aristocrat by Yen Press since February 9, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/222486.jpg", 8945, 6.99m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The most dangerous prey... When the most accomplished assassin on Earth meets his end just before retirement, he finds himself standing before a goddess. Her world is headed for disaster, and she has need of his particular set of skills. Armed with powerful new abilities and decades of deadly knowledge, he begins his second life as Lugh, young scion of the Tuatha Dé clan of assassins. His mission: to find and eliminate the strongest individual in this world—the hero!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sekai Saikou no Ansatsusha, Isekai Kizoku ni Tensei suru", "The World's Finest Assassin Gets Reincarnated in Another World as an Aristocrat", "世界最高の暗殺者、異世界貴族に転生する", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117886/Sekai_Saikou_no_Ansatsusha_Isekai_Kizoku_ni_Tensei_suru", null },
                    { 117956, "Overlord: Koushiki Comic à la Carte was published in English as Overlord à la Carte by Yen Press from August 27, 2019 to February 18, 2020.", 47, new DateTime(2018, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/221257.jpg", 7724, 7.07m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An anthology comic of Overlord by various mangaka.", "Overlord: Koushiki Comic à la Carte", "Overlord à la Carte", "オーバーロード 公式コミックアラカルト", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/117956/Overlord__Koushiki_Comic_à_la_Carte", 3 },
                    { 118108, "Hitoribocchi no Isekai Kouryaku began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on October 12, 2016. Overlap began releasing a revised and illustrated version of the series on January 25, 2019 under its Overlap Bunko label. The series has been published in English as Loner Life in Another World by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint since August 3, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/215580.jpg", 8441, 7.02m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Haruka, who spends his high school life as a loner, was suddenly summoned to another world one day along with all his classmates. When ol' God enters the picture, Haruka believes he can just choose whatever cheat skill he wants to help him survive in the new world... But, contrary to his expectations, that list of cheat skills works on a first come, first serve basis. And so, his classmates pick out all the cheat skills. His choices now limited to leftovers, Haruka finds himself incapable of assembling a party due to his own \"loner\" skill. Even though it's a different world, it seems his adventuring days will be, as per usual, a solitary affair...\n\nAfter becoming aware of a crisis looming over his classmates, Haruka makes a silent vow to save them. No relying on cheats! He will walk a heretical path of strength that transcends the need for them. The curtain rises on the strongest loner's otherworld strategy guide!\n\n(Source: Overlap, translated)", "Hitoribocchi no Isekai Kouryaku", "Loner Life in Another World", "ひとりぼっちの異世界攻略", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118108/Hitoribocchi_no_Isekai_Kouryaku", null },
                    { 118123, "", 7, new DateTime(2018, 10, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/215595.jpg", 17632, 6.34m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Having won a photon sword in a mini game, Yui decided that it would be the perfect gift for Kirito. However, convinced that a present is more impactful when it's delivered as a surprise, Yui enlisted the help of Asuna and the other girls. The girls would face Kirito in battle during a new GGO event and create an opportunity for the perfect surprise: using slime guns to blind him during the fight, thus allowing Yui to present her gift to the unsuspecting Kirito just as he regains his vision. However, Yui did not foresee one thing: that her surprise gift will have to compete in impactfulness with Kirito's mastery at getting himself into all kinds of ecchi situations...\n\n(Source: Dreadful Decoding)", "Sword Art Online: Kirito no Gun Gale Wars", "Sword Art Online: Kirito's Gun Gale Wars", "ソードアート・オンライン　キリトの千夜一夜騒動〈ガンゲイルウォーズ〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118123/Sword_Art_Online__Kirito_no_Gun_Gale_Wars", 1 },
                    { 118251, "Hitoribocchi no Isekai Kouryaku has been published digitally in English as Loner Life in Another World by Kaiten Books since March 31, 2020, and physically since August 19, 2020. It has also been published in French by Meian since November 18, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/224110.jpg", 16536, 6.46m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Haruka, who spends his high school life as a loner, was suddenly summoned to another world one day along with all his classmates. When ol' God enters the picture, Haruka believes he can just choose whatever cheat skill he wants to help him survive in the new world... But, contrary to his expectations, that list of cheat skills works on a first come, first serve basis. And so, his classmates pick out all the cheat skills. His choices now limited to leftovers, Haruka finds himself incapable of assembling a party due to his own \"loner\" skill. Even though it's a different world, it seems his adventuring days will be, as per usual, a solitary affair...\n\nAfter becoming aware of a crisis looming over his classmates, Haruka makes a silent vow to save them. No relying on cheats! He will walk a heretical path of strength that transcends the need for them. The curtain rises on the strongest loner's otherworld strategy guide!\n\n(Source: Overlap, translated)", "Hitoribocchi no Isekai Kouryaku", "Loner Life in Another World", "ひとりぼっちの異世界攻略", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118251/Hitoribocchi_no_Isekai_Kouryaku", null },
                    { 118326, "Tenshi Girl was published digitally in English as Angel Girl by Irodori Comics on January 4, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/223039.jpg", 14209, 6.64m, new DateTime(2018, 12, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "One day, Sayaka finds a banana on the street, which is summarily consumed by a loitering Yoshiko. Later that night, Sayaka is visited by the spirit of the banana, who transforms her into an angel and tasks her to go help souls in need. She eventually winds up at A-kun's house, where she now has to grant his true heart's desire... to marry Sayaka? Find out just what on earth is going on in this parody spin-off to Hiroyuki's wildly popular Aho Girl series!\n\n(Source: Irodori Comics)", "Aho Girl dj - Tenshi Girl", "Angel Girl", "天使ガール", 6, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118326/Aho_Girl_dj_-_Tenshi_Girl", 1 },
                    { 118456, "", 13, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/239328.jpg", 6564, 7.15m, new DateTime(2018, 10, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The second anthology revolving around Megumin and her daily life.", "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo! Megumin Anthology Aka", null, "この素晴らしい世界に祝福を！　めぐみんアンソロジー　紅Aka", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118456/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Shukufuku_wo_Megumin_Anthology_Aka", 1 },
                    { 118522, null, null, new DateTime(2011, 12, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/234241.jpg", 24698, null, new DateTime(2007, 6, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "4-koma Chibi Maruko-chan", null, "4コマちびまる子ちゃん", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118522/4-koma_Chibi_Maruko-chan", 13 },
                    { 118801, null, 7, new DateTime(2019, 2, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/216668.jpg", 24767, null, new DateTime(2018, 8, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Trinity Seven: Seven Days", null, "トリニティセブン セブンデイズ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/118801/Trinity_Seven__Seven_Days", 1 },
                    { 119022, "Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute! has been published in English as The Eminence in Shadow by Yen Press since November 23, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/227280.jpg", 356, 8.26m, new DateTime(2018, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Great heroes and diabolical villains are the types of characters that people long to be—but not Cid Kagenou. He longs to become the true mastermind behind it all, pulling the strings, and having his machinations drive the entire story. In his previous life in modern-day Japan, he was not able to achieve his goals. But now, reborn into a world of magic, he will show the true eminence of shadow!\n\nAs Cid pretends to be just another average mob character, he recruits members to his (fake) organization Shadow Garden, aiming to take down the mysterious cult who lurks in the shadows. With plenty of ad-libs, Cid leads his (fake) organization against the foul (yet surprisingly real) Cult of Diablos.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute!", "The Eminence in Shadow", "陰の実力者になりたくて!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119022/Kage_no_Jitsuryokusha_ni_Naritakute", null },
                    { 119161, "Spy x Family ranked first in the 2020 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. It was nominated for the 13th Manga Taisho Award in 2020 and placed second in the final ranking. In the same year, it was also nominated for the 44th Kodansha Manga Award in the Shounen category. In 2021, the manga was nominated for the 14th Manga Taisho Award and placed 10th in the final ranking. In 2023, it won the Grand Prize in the Comic Division at the 52nd Japan Cartoonists Association Awards. The series has been simulpub in English through MANGA Plus. It has been published physically in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since June 2, 2020. The manga has also been released in Polish by Waneko since April 30, 2020; in Spanish by Editorial Ivrea since June 11, 2020; in Brazilian Portuguese and Italian by Panini Comics since September 15, 2020, and November 5, 2020, respectively; and in German by Kazé Deutschland since October 1, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/219741.jpg", 144, 8.5m, new DateTime(2019, 3, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "For the agent known as \"Twilight,\" no order is too tall if it is for the sake of peace. Operating as Westalis' master spy, Twilight works tirelessly to prevent extremists from sparking a war with neighboring country Ostania. For his latest mission, he must investigate Ostanian politician Donovan Desmond by infiltrating his son's school: the prestigious Eden Academy. Thus, the agent faces the most difficult task of his career: get married, have a child, and play family.\n\nTwilight, or \"Loid Forger,\" quickly adopts the unassuming orphan Anya to play the role of a six-year-old daughter and prospective Eden Academy student. For a wife, he comes across Yor Briar, an absent-minded office worker who needs a pretend partner of her own to impress her friends. However, Loid is not the only one with a hidden nature. Yor moonlights as the lethal assassin \"Thorn Princess.\" For her, marrying Loid creates the perfect cover. Meanwhile, Anya is not the ordinary girl she appears to be; she is an esper, the product of secret experiments that allow her to read minds. Although she uncovers their true identities, Anya is thrilled that her new parents are cool secret agents! She would never tell them, of course. That would ruin the fun.\n\nUnder the guise of \"The Forgers,\" the spy, the assassin, and the esper must act as a family while carrying out their own agendas. Although these liars and misfits are only playing parts, they soon find that family is about far more than blood relations.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Spy x Family", "Spy x Family", "SPY×FAMILY", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119161/Spy_x_Family", null },
                    { 119184, "Solo Leveling began as a web novel on KakaoPage, where 243 web chapters were released from July 25, 2016, to July 28, 2017. They were published in print by D&C Media under its Papyrus imprint from November 4, 2016, to October 27, 2017. The series was published in English by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint from February 16, 2021, to July 18, 2023. It was also released in German by Altraverse from March 19, 2021, to March 20, 2023; and in Brazilian Portuguese by NewPOP Editora. The three releases are based on the 8-volume reissue from 2019.", 150, new DateTime(2017, 10, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/265759.jpg", 201, 8.42m, new DateTime(2016, 11, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "E-rank hunter Jinwoo Sung has no money, no talent, and no prospects to speak of—and apparently, no luck, either! When he enters a hidden double dungeon one fateful day, he's abandoned by his party and left to die at the hands of some of the most horrific monsters he's ever encountered. But just before the last, fatal blow...\n \nPING! [Congratulations on becoming a Player.]\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Solo Leveling", "Solo Leveling", "나 혼자만 레벨업", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119184/Solo_Leveling", 13 },
                    { 119295, null, 23, new DateTime(2020, 11, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/234409.jpg", 8025, 7.05m, new DateTime(2019, 3, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Steeplechase-hen", null, "魔法科高校の劣等生 スティープルチェース編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119295/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Steeplechase-hen", 3 },
                    { 119296, null, 35, new DateTime(2022, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/234410.jpg", 8463, 7.02m, new DateTime(2019, 3, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Koto Nairan-hen", null, "魔法科高校の劣等生 古都内乱編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119296/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Koto_Nairan-hen", 5 },
                    { 119385, "", null, new DateTime(2018, 12, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/223799.jpg", 24877, null, new DateTime(2016, 12, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A mysterious monster called the High Beast has taken control of the regions of Eurasia and Africa. Japan has cut off from the mainland to protect itself from this threat. The daughter of a legendary mahjong player discovers that monsters attack whenever a mahjong piece is hit across the board. This allows humans to be separated from the battle and for mahjong players to effectively combat the monsters with robots controlled through mahjong moves.\n\n(Source: Getter Robo Wiki)", "Getter Robo Hai", "Getter Robot High", "ゲッターロボ牌", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119385/Getter_Robo_Hai", 3 },
                    { 119534, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/234226.jpg", 14875, 6.59m, new DateTime(2000, 1, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "One night, Shuuichi Saitou reveals something incredible to his girlfriend, Kirie Goshima: he has recently discovered a new spiral-shaped galaxy. Filled with excitement, Kirie shares the news with her teacher, who invites his astronomer friend to confirm the discovery. The astronomer, Mr. Torino, is shocked at the existence of the galaxy and realizes that it will bring Shuuichi endless fame. The envious Torino, soon corrupted by the spiral, goes to great lengths to steal credit for Shuuichi's work. But this isn't the only new finding in Kurouzu-cho...\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Uzumaki Tokubetsu-hen: Ginga", null, "うずまき特別編 銀河", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119534/Uzumaki_Tokubetsu-hen__Ginga", null },
                    { 119688, "", 19, new DateTime(1974, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/300910.jpg", 24913, null, new DateTime(1973, 8, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A compilation of the Ken Ishikawa and previously uncompiled Yuu Okazaki versions of Cutie Honey.", "Cutie Honey: The Another", null, "キューティーハニー THE ANOTHER", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119688/Cutie_Honey__The_Another", 1 },
                    { 119696, "Overlord: Boukoku no Kyuuketsuki was sold as part of a mail-order campaign for those who purchased all 3 Blu-ray volumes of the Overlord III anime.", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/269384.jpg", 2713, 7.53m, new DateTime(2019, 4, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An alternative version of the Overlord series, based on a short story Kugane Maruyama released on their Twitter account.", "Overlord: Boukoku no Kyuuketsuki", "Overlord: The Vampire Princess of the Lost Country", "オーバーロード 亡国の吸血姫", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119696/Overlord__Boukoku_no_Kyuuketsuki", 1 },
                    { 119852, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/230124.jpg", 960, 7.91m, new DateTime(2019, 5, 12, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "What do Karasuno High School's volleyball rivals get up to when they are not training for a tournament? From scouting out a video game tournament and debunking ghost myths, to arguing over bunk bed assignments and having troubles with girls—nothing is boring about what this colorful cast of characters can get into during their downtime! Though their competitive spirit is fierce, their comedic potential is just as strong.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Haikyuu-bu!!", null, "ハイキュー部!!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119852/Haikyuu-bu", null },
                    { 119886, "Utakata ni Warau is a continuation of the two-part story of the same title included in volume 1 of Donten ni Warau.", 5, new DateTime(2019, 5, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/224884.jpg", 8604, 7.01m, new DateTime(2018, 11, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Six hundred years ago, Kagemitsu Kumou was brought to Lake Biwa and asked to give up his life of farming to become the head of the shrine there. His new duties would include acting as a shield for the spiritual being, Botan, who resided in the shrine. An entire clan of onmyouji needed to be sacrificed to summon the normally gentle yet immensely powerful demon, but her existence was necessary to seal the cursed \"Orochi,\" a giant snake and disaster incarnate which reawakens every 300 years.\n\nWhen the Orochi was last sealed, Botan's fate became intertwined with that of Hirari Abeno, a man who professed to have loved her since his childhood. From that point forward, the two are bound to meet time and time again and eventually remember their feelings for each other. In this lifetime, will they be able to defeat the Orochi once and for all with the help of their allies? And can they break free from this endless cycle of loss and reunion to find happiness together?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Utakata ni Warau", null, "泡沫に笑う", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119886/Utakata_ni_Warau", 1 },
                    { 119908, "Naruto Retsuden Series was published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint from July 26, 2022 to March 28, 2023.", 24, new DateTime(2019, 10, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/253962.jpg", 2404, 7.58m, new DateTime(2019, 6, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In the Naruto Retsuden series:\n\n1. Kakashi Retsuden: Rokudaime Hokage to Ochikobore no Shounen (Kakashi's Story: The Sixth Hokage and the Failed Prince)\n2. Sasuke Retsuden: Uchiha no Matsuei to Tenkyuu no Hoshikuzu (Sasuke's Story: The Uchiha and the Heavenly Stardust)\n3. Naruto Retsuden: Uzumaki Naruto to Rasen no Tenmei (Naruto's Story: Uzumaki Naruto and the Spiral Destiny)", "Naruto Retsuden Series", null, "NARUTO -ナルト- 烈伝シリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/119908/Naruto_Retsuden_Series", 3 },
                    { 120206, "The Ultraman was published partially in English as Ultraman Classic: Battle of the Ultra-Brothers in 5 issues by Viz Media under the Viz Manga Heroes imprint in 1994.", 28, new DateTime(1978, 12, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/286023.jpg", 24970, null, new DateTime(1974, 12, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Continuing from either one of Uchiyama's Ultraman Leo manga series, the story centers around Zoffy, Melos and the Ultra Brothers taking on numerous Kaiju threats to both the Land of Light (known as the Land of Ultra in the manga) and Planet Earth.\n\n(Source: Ultraman Wiki)", "The Ultraman", "Ultraman Classic: Battle of the Ultra-Brothers", "ザ・ウルトラマン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120206/The_Ultraman", 4 },
                    { 120401, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/222841.jpg", 15189, 6.57m, new DateTime(2018, 6, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The premise of this gag manga spinoff is about three high school students: a young male student, his girlfriend and a third wheel who is a One Piece fanatic. Their names are similar to the Straw Hat Pirates and the group form a fan club dedicated to One Piece. Each chapter is a parody of the series.\n\n(Source: One Piece Wiki)", "Koisuru One Piece", null, "恋するワンピース", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120401/Koisuru_One_Piece", null },
                    { 120412, "", 28, new DateTime(2021, 5, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/219338.jpg", 3863, 7.39m, new DateTime(2018, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Long ago, a great war raged between the royal military of Lugunica and the demi-humans. On that battlefield, a noteworthy young warrior was born—Wilhelm Trias, dubbed the Sword Devil. But despite his skill with a blade, the boy would need to grow much more before he could become a true hero. This is the story of a legendary swordsman—and how he learned to love.\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Kenki Renka: Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu†Shinmeitan", null, "剣鬼恋歌 Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活†真銘譚", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120412/Kenki_Renka__Re_Zero_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu†Shinmeitan", 4 },
                    { 120548, "Sekai Saikou no Ansatsusha, Isekai Kizoku ni Tensei suru began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on July 29, 2018. Kadokawa has released a revised and illustrated version of the series since February 1, 2019 under its Kadokawa Sneaker Bunko label. The series has been published in English as The World's Finest Assassin Gets Reincarnated in Another World as an Aristocrat by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since December 29, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/222487.jpg", 4163, 7.36m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The greatest assassin on Earth knew only how to live as a tool for his employers—until they stopped letting him live. Reborn by the grace of a goddess into a world of swords and sorcery, he's offered a chance to do things differently this time around, but there's a catch... He has to eliminate a super-powerful hero who will bring about the end of the world unless he is stopped. Now known as Lugh Tuatha Dé, the master assassin certainly has his hands full, particularly because of all the beautiful girls who constantly surround him. Lugh may have been an incomparable killer, but how will he fare against foes with powerful magic?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sekai Saikou no Ansatsusha, Isekai Kizoku ni Tensei suru", "The World's Finest Assassin Gets Reincarnated in Another World as an Aristocrat", "世界最高の暗殺者、異世界貴族に転生する", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120548/Sekai_Saikou_no_Ansatsusha_Isekai_Kizoku_ni_Tensei_suru", null },
                    { 120656, "", 8, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/230439.jpg", 886, 7.94m, new DateTime(2019, 8, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The world's greatest exposition of the pirates, by the pirates, for the pirates—the Pirates Festival. Luffy and the rest of the Straw Hat Crew receive an invitation from its host Buena Festa who is known as the Master of Festivities. They arrive to find a venue packed with glamorous pavilions and many pirates including the ones from the Worst Generation. The place is electric.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Gekijouban One Piece: Stampede", null, "劇場版 ONE PIECE STAMPEDE", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120656/Gekijouban_One_Piece__Stampede", 1 },
                    { 120680, "Mahou Shoujo ni Akogarete has been published in French as Looking up to Magical Girls by Meian since February 24, 2021. It has been published digitally in English as Gushing over Magical Girls by J-Novel Club since June 1, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/230579.jpg", null, 7.91m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Hiiragi Utena has always looked up to magical girls and fantasized about transforming into a cool heroine who fights evil. So, when a doll-like figure approaches her one evening, claiming that she has magical power lying dormant within, she trembles in excitement. But her colorful dream is quickly shattered in an ironic turn of events when she transforms into a villain!\n\nDisinterested in associating with the forces of evil, she tries to quit when a group of magical girls appear and declare war.  A battle ensues and Hiiragi soon discovers that she enjoys inflicting pain on others as her true nature starts to emerge.\n\nMahou Shoujo ni Akogarete follows Hiiragi as she begins her new life as the leader of villains, fighting against magical girls and indulging in her newfound sadistic nature to her heart's content. \n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Mahou Shoujo ni Akogarete", "Gushing over Magical Girls", "魔法少女にあこがれて", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120680/Mahou_Shoujo_ni_Akogarete", null },
                    { 120974, "2.5-jigen no Ririsa has been published in English as 2.5 Dimensional Seduction by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Ghost Ship imprint since February 8, 2022. The series has also been published digitally as a simulpub through MANGA Plus.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/265196.jpg", 6257, 7.18m, new DateTime(2019, 6, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "\"I have no interest in real girls!\" So claims Okumura, the president of the school's manga club. He's your typical otaku, obsessed with a sexy (fictional) 2D manga character known as Lilliel. Then the new school year starts, and a (real!) 3D girl named Lilysa whose passion is cosplay joins the club. Lilysa convinces Okumura to become her photographer—and guess who her favorite manga character is? Not only that, but Lilysa is into modeling the fetishy stuff! The boundaries between 2D and 3D start to blur as this hot-blooded romantic comedy unfolds.\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "2.5-jigen no Ririsa", "2.5 Dimensional Seduction", "2.5次元の誘惑〈りりさ〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/120974/25-jigen_no_Ririsa", null },
                    { 121118, "Kimetsu no Yaiba: Shiawase no Hana was published in English as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - The Flower of Happiness by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on October 25, 2022. It was also released in Polish by Waneko on November 25, 2021.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/229952.jpg", 3297, 7.45m, new DateTime(2019, 2, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A mystical flower offers a prosperous future for its bearer. Determined to find the flower for Nezuko, Tanjiro makes a harrowing journey up a mountain—but Inosuke reveals the flower’s true worth. In other tales, Zenitsu recalls the day he battled a demon to save a crying girl, a fortune-teller warns Zenitsu that he’ll die if a girl falls for him, Kanao helps Aoi learn her value apart from killing demons, and when Kimetsu Academy students search for the recipe to win over Mr. Tomioka, Mr. Rengoku ropes them into cooking!\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Kimetsu no Yaiba: Shiawase no Hana", "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - The Flower of Happiness", "鬼滅の刃 しあわせの花", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121118/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba__Shiawase_no_Hana", 1 },
                    { 121119, "Kimetsu no Yaiba: Kataha no Chou was published in English as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - One-Winged Butterfly by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on February 28, 2023.", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/229953.jpg", 2107, 7.63m, new DateTime(2019, 10, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Shinobu and Kanae ask Himejima to teach them how to slay demons. After he refuses, they must complete the impossible task of moving a giant rock to convince him to introduce them to trainers. In other tales, Zenitsu tricks Inosuke into helping him dig a hot spring under Uzui's training, Mitsuri grapples with her reason for becoming a Demon Slayer, Genya discusses his family with Sumi, the Hashiras try to make Tomioka smile, and Kimetsu Academy forms a rock band—much to Shinobu's chagrin!\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Kimetsu no Yaiba: Kataha no Chou", "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - One-Winged Butterfly", "鬼滅の刃 片羽の蝶", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121119/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba__Kataha_no_Chou", 1 },
                    { 121357, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/226099.jpg", 16145, 6.49m, new DateTime(2019, 8, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "\"Maou Army’s strongest magician\" I'm called. Ike, a demon capable of capturing a fort alone. Clearing away enemies with immense magic, he is without a doubt a monster awed by friend and foe. However he has a secret he can’t tell other demons. \"I, actually I'm human you know.\" Using modern knowledge to keep his secret, he became treated as a great commander and the driving force of the Maou's army.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Maougun Saikyou no Majutsushi wa Ningen datta", null, "魔王軍最強の魔術師は人間だった", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121357/Maougun_Saikyou_no_Majutsushi_wa_Ningen_datta", null },
                    { 121496, "Solo Leveling is a webtoon series which has been officially published in book format by D&C Media (디앤씨미디어) since September 26, 2019. It originally ended with 179 chapters on December 29, 2021, and side stories began serialization on January 20, 2023. The side stories are drawn by Disciples after the death of original artist Sung-rak Jang. The series has been published digitally in English by Tappytoon since June 4, 2020, and in print by Yen Press since March 2, 2021. It has also been published in French by Delcourt since April 7, 2021.", 201, new DateTime(2023, 5, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/222295.jpg", 68, 8.66m, new DateTime(2018, 3, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Ten years ago, \"the Gate\" appeared and connected the real world with the realm of magic and monsters. To combat these vile beasts, ordinary people received superhuman powers and became known as \"Hunters.\" Twenty-year-old Sung Jin-Woo is one such Hunter, but he is known as the \"World's Weakest,\" owing to his pathetic power compared to even a measly E-Rank. Still, he hunts monsters tirelessly in low-rank Gates to pay for his mother's medical bills. \n\nHowever, this miserable lifestyle changes when Jin-Woo—believing himself to be the only one left to die in a mission gone terribly wrong—awakens in a hospital three days later to find a mysterious screen floating in front of him. This \"Quest Log\" demands that Jin-Woo completes an unrealistic and intense training program, or face an appropriate penalty. Initially reluctant to comply because of the quest's rigor, Jin-Woo soon finds that it may just transform him into one of the world's most fearsome Hunters. \n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Solo Leveling", "Solo Leveling", "나 혼자만 레벨업", 4, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121496/Solo_Leveling", null },
                    { 121504, "Yubisaki to Renren ranked ninth and 17th in the 2021 and 2022 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Female Readers division, respectively. The manga was nominated for the Kodansha Manga Award in the Shoujo category for four consecutive years from 2021 to 2024. The series has been published digitally in English as A Sign of Affection by Kodansha Comics USA since March 31, 2020, and in print since February 23, 2021. The series has also been simulpub through K Manga. Kodansha Comics USA has also published the manga as 3-in-1 omnibus volumes. It has also been released in Polish as Znaki naszych uczuć by Studio JG since May 12, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/5/262471.jpg", 158, 8.49m, new DateTime(2019, 7, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Yuki Itose is a hearing-impaired university student whose world has been shrouded with silence since birth. She has lived in the same place her whole life, and rarely interacts with others save for her best friend, Rin Fujishiro. During her commute one day, she meets the silver-haired and multilingual Itsuomi Nagi, a mutual friend of Rin. Unlike most, Itsuomi is unwavering when he learns of Yuki's impairment; this, along with his experiences abroad, fascinates and touches her. After they part, her fondness of him starts to grow. A new world begins to open for both Yuki and Itsuomi as they learn about each other's different lives.\n\nYubisaki to Renren is a lighthearted, romantic comedy that illustrates the silent life of a university student and how one man sharing his world starts to change her own.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Yubisaki to Renren", "A Sign of Affection", "ゆびさきと恋々", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121504/Yubisaki_to_Renren", null },
                    { 121505, "Koukaku Kidoutai: The Human Algorithm has been published digitally in English as The Ghost in the Shell: The Human Algorithm by Kodansha USA since November 20, 2019, and in print since June 23, 2020, and it has also been simulpub.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/232394.jpg", 5415, 7.24m, new DateTime(2019, 9, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Hackers attempt to assassinate a politician during a speech preaching the advantages of cybernetic prosthetics. Fortunately, Togusa is there to whisk her to safety, and the investigation leads Batou to a suspicious factory in the artificial islands in southern Japan. Meanwhile, Chief Aramaki hears of a disturbing discovery at the other end of the country: dozens of artificial bodies, illegally dumped near a village where an anti-cyberization sect conducts their training and \"rites.\" Among the empty shells is one formerly inhabited by the woman who embodied Section 9 until she left it behind and disappeared: Major Motoko Kusanagi...\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)", "Koukaku Kidoutai: The Human Algorithm", "The Ghost in the Shell: The Human Algorithm", "攻殻機動隊 THE HUMAN ALGORITHM", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121505/Koukaku_Kidoutai__The_Human_Algorithm", null },
                    { 121597, "Dosanko Gal wa Namara Menkoi was published digitally in English as Hokkaido Gals Are Super Adorable! through MANGA Plus.", null, new DateTime(2024, 9, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/224525.jpg", 6600, 7.15m, new DateTime(2019, 9, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Tsubasa Shiki has just moved from Tokyo to Hokkaido, in the middle of winter. Not quite appreciating how far apart towns are in the country, he gets off the taxi at the next town over from his destination so he can see the sights around his home. But he is shocked when he learns the \"next town\" is a 3 hour walk away. But he also meets a cute Dosanko (born and raised in Hokkaido) gyaru named Minami Fuyuki who is braving negative 8 degree weather in the standard gyaru outfit of short skirts and bare legs!\n\n(Source: MU)", "Dosanko Gal wa Namara Menkoi", "Hokkaido Gals Are Super Adorable!", "道産子ギャルはなまらめんこい", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121597/Dosanko_Gal_wa_Namara_Menkoi", 14 },
                    { 121951, "", 13, new DateTime(2020, 11, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/243865.jpg", 1238, 7.82m, new DateTime(2019, 10, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A spin-off taking place 7 years before the events of Meitantei Conan which focuses on Rei Furuya, Jinpei Matsuda, Kenji Hagiwara, Wataru Date, and Hiromitsu Morifushi during their time at the Metropolitan Police Academy.", "Meitantei Conan: Keisatsu Gakkou-hen - Wild Police Story", null, "名探偵コナン 警察学校編 Wild Police Story", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/121951/Meitantei_Conan__Keisatsu_Gakkou-hen_-_Wild_Police_Story", 2 },
                    { 122058, "Nageki no Bourei wa Intai shitai: Saijaku Hunter ni Yoru Saikyou Party Ikuseijutsu has been published in English as Let This Grieving Soul Retire! Woe Is the Weakling Who Leads the Strongest Party by Yen Press since December 21, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/233330.jpg", 15757, 6.52m, new DateTime(2019, 4, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "It's the golden age of treasure hunters who seek wealth, honor, power and glory, and explore treasures around the world without regard to danger. \"Let's become treasure hunters,\" said Kurai Andolihy, who swore an oath with his childhood friends to become the strongest... but he discovered during his first quest that he has no talent. But that was only the beginning of his adventure.\n\n\"I can't do this anymore. I want to quit.\"\n\"Oh, I see. In other words, we should fight harder and cover for you, that's a good handicap.\"\n\"Rest assured, Kurai. We'll protect you!\"\n\"Oh, wait. If you step on that, the trap will destroy you without leaving a speck of dust behind. Be careful, Leader!\"\n\nProtected by his overpowered childhood friends, sought out by newbies and nobles, they aim to be heroes and find powerful treasures. Will Kruai really be able to retire safely from being a treasure hunter?\n\n(Source: Kadokawa/Shousetsuka ni Narou, translated)", "Nageki no Bourei wa Intai shitai: Saijaku Hunter ni Yoru Saikyou Party Ikuseijutsu", "Let This Grieving Soul Retire! Woe Is the Weakling Who Leads the Strongest Party", "嘆きの亡霊は引退したい ～最弱ハンターによる最強パーティ育成術～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122058/Nageki_no_Bourei_wa_Intai_shitai__Saijaku_Hunter_ni_Yoru_Saikyou_Party_Ikuseijutsu", null },
                    { 122105, null, 2, new DateTime(2019, 5, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/227241.jpg", 8243, 7.03m, new DateTime(2019, 4, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "To LOVE-Ru: Rito to Sayaka no Houkago", null, "To LOVEる -とらぶる- -リトと紗弥香の放課後-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122105/To_LOVE-Ru__Rito_to_Sayaka_no_Houkago", null },
                    { 122150, "Isekai Shikkaku has been published in English as No Longer Allowed in Another World by Seven Seas Entertainment since January 3, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/269897.jpg", 2702, 7.53m, new DateTime(2019, 10, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "An adventure in another world with cute girls by your side and video game-like powers—sounds like an anime fan's dream, right? Not so for melancholic author Osamu Dazai, who would quite literally prefer to drop dead. Video games haven't even been invented yet when he gets yanked into another world in 1948. Really, all the fantastical adventure he keeps running into is just getting in the way of his poetic dream of finding the perfect place to die. But no matter how much he risks his hide, everything seems to keep turning out okay. Follow a miserable hero like no other in this cheerfully bleak isekai comedy!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Isekai Shikkaku", "No Longer Allowed in Another World", "異世界失格", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122150/Isekai_Shikkaku", null },
                    { 122239, null, 6, new DateTime(2008, 1, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/291491.jpg", 25286, null, new DateTime(2007, 10, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Saint Seiya Episode G 0", null, "聖闘士星矢EPISODE.G 0", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122239/Saint_Seiya_Episode_G_0", 1 },
                    { 122305, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/233977.jpg", 12358, 6.77m, new DateTime(2019, 8, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Koby is a teenager who has recently transferred to the New World Academy. Fed up with his former upperclassman Alvida's dealings, Koby is willing to make one hundred friends at his new school. It is not long until he meets a boy made of rubber named Monkey D. Luffy, with whom he becomes inseparable in a matter of minutes.\n\nUnder the guidance of their apathetic teacher, Koby and Luffy are bound to have eventful lives and interact with their eccentric classmates. During their everyday adventures at the academy, they face the seven most powerful students in the school, the Shichibukai, and defy the rules imposed by the student council headed by the teachers' lackey, Lucci Rob.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "One Piece Gakuen", null, "ONE PIECE学園", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122305/One_Piece_Gakuen", null },
                    { 122365, "Ninja Batman was published in French as Batman Ninja by Kana from September 20, 2019 to January 31, 2020.", 13, new DateTime(2019, 8, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/226817.jpg", 25310, null, new DateTime(2018, 6, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Batman Ninja takes a journey across the ages as Gorilla Grodd's time displacement machine transports many of Batman's worst enemies to feudal Japan—along with the Dark Knight and a few of his allies. The villains take over the forms of the feudal lords that rule the divided land, with the Joker taking the lead among the warring factions. As his traditional high-tech weaponry is exhausted almost immediately, Batman must rely on his intellect and his allies—including Catwoman and the extended Bat-family—to restore order to the land, and return to present-day Gotham City.\n\n(Source: Warner Bros.)", "Ninja Batman", "Batman Ninja", "ニンジャバットマン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122365/Ninja_Batman", 2 },
                    { 122464, "Dr. Stone Reboot: Byakuya was simulpub in English through MANGA Plus service. It was published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on March 2, 2021.", 9, new DateTime(2019, 12, 22, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/227742.jpg", 1521, 7.74m, new DateTime(2019, 10, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "What did humanity's final astronaut, Byakuya Ishigami, do when he saw everyone on earth turn to stone from the international space station? A special side story written and drawn by Boichi Sensei himself! The first simultaneous series and side story serialization in Weekly Shonen Jump history!\n\n(Source: MANGA Plus)", "Dr. Stone Reboot: Byakuya", "Dr. Stone Reboot: Byakuya", "Dr.STONE reboot：百夜", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122464/Dr_Stone_Reboot__Byakuya", 1 },
                    { 122473, "Mashima Hero's was published in English by Kodansha USA on December 1, 2020.", 10, new DateTime(2019, 12, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/229267.jpg", 5304, 7.25m, new DateTime(2019, 10, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A crossover of Rave, Fairy Tail, and Edens Zero to celebrate the 60th anniversary of Shounen Magazine.", "Mashima Hero's", "Mashima Hero's", "Mashima HERO's", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122473/Mashima_Heros", 1 },
                    { 122557, "", null, new DateTime(2020, 1, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/235047.jpg", 25339, null, new DateTime(2018, 10, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The novels feature a new heroine named Yuki Hashibami, a magician assassin who is not a magician herself. She challenges Tatsuya in the story.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Shiba Tatsuya Ansatsu Keikaku", "The Irregular at Magic High School: Plan to Assassinate Tatsuya Shiba", "魔法科高校の劣等生 司波達也暗殺計画", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122557/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Shiba_Tatsuya_Ansatsu_Keikaku", 3 },
                    { 122650, "Hazurewaku no \"Joutai Ijou Skill\" de Saikyou ni Natta Ore ga Subete wo Juurin suru made has been published in English as Failure Frame: I Became the Strongest and Annihilated Everything With Low-Level Spells by Seven Seas Entertainment since April 13, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/226075.jpg", 13526, 6.69m, new DateTime(2019, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Along with his entire class, Touka Mimori was summoned to another world by the Goddess Vicius. While most were ranked quite powerful, Touka was the weakest among them, so it was only natural that he be disposed of. Vicius' first impression as a generous and loving woman soon gives way to her true, cruel nature, and she rallies his classmates against him, casting him into a cavernous labyrinth of death and despair.\n\nDespite being the weakest, even he has a personal skill: Abnormal State Skill. This ability, combined with his low level \"poison\" and \"paralyze\" powers, proves to be a deadly medley—hindering the movement of monsters, then letting poison whittle away at their health until they die without having a chance to fight back. \n\nGaining new abilities and companions along the way, Touka aims to exact revenge on that spiteful goddess who cast him into this hellscape.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Hazurewaku no \"Joutai Ijou Skill\" de Saikyou ni Natta Ore ga Subete wo Juurin suru made", "Failure Frame: I Became the Strongest and Annihilated Everything With Low-Level Spells", "ハズレ枠の【状態異常スキル】で最強になった俺がすべてを蹂躙するまで", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122650/Hazurewaku_no_Joutai_Ijou_Skill_de_Saikyou_ni_Natta_Ore_ga_Subete_wo_Juurin_suru_made", null },
                    { 122663, "Tower of God has been published digitally in English by LINE Webtoon since June 30, 2014, and in print by Wattpad Webtoon Studios under its Webtoon Unscrolled imprint since November 22, 2022. It has also been released in Spain and Mexico by Panini Comics since November 25, 2021, and January 26, 2022, respectively.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/223694.jpg", 243, 8.37m, new DateTime(2010, 7, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Twenty-Fifth Bam had been alone his whole life until he met Rachel. Now, however, Rachel is set on climbing the Tower, and she is willing to leave Bam behind to do so. After Rachel disappears in a veil of light, Bam follows her, vowing to ascend the Tower in hopes of meeting her again.\n\nBut the Tower is a dangerous place full of ancient secrets, fearsome monsters, and nefarious humans. Each floor is protected by an Administrator who puts the daring challengers through grueling tests that will push them to their limits.\n\nAs he confronts Headon, the Administrator of the first floor, Bam learns that he is an ''Irregular,'' someone who was not chosen by the Tower but was able to enter it on his own, an extremely rare event inside the Tower. Regardless of this revelation, however, his path forward is clear. Be it wealth, power, glory, or even reuniting with Rachel, all desires will be realized at the top of the Tower.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tower of God", "Tower of God", "신의 탑", 4, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122663/Tower_of_God", null },
                    { 122892, "", 8, new DateTime(1990, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/296270.jpg", 25374, null, new DateTime(1989, 5, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Universal Century 0079, Zeon Elementary School fifth grade student Mariko, meets the Red Comet, who is mounted on a white horse that gives magical powers. When the colony falls into crisis, Mariko becomes the beautiful Ensign Blaster Mari, and pilots the Zaku I to defend her home against the Federation's GMs.", "Mahou no Shoui Blaster Mari", null, "魔法の少尉ブラスターマリ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122892/Mahou_no_Shoui_Blaster_Mari", 1 },
                    { 122943, "Bishounen Series has been published in English as Pretty Boy Detective Club by Vertical since September 29, 2020.", null, new DateTime(2021, 5, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/243502.jpg", 4356, 7.34m, new DateTime(2015, 10, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Mayumi Doujima, a second-year student at the exclusive Yubiwa Academy middle school, has lost something—a star she glimpsed just once, ten long years ago. But help is on the way, in the form of the unofficial, secretive, and thoroughly mysterious Pretty Boy Detective Club! Rumored to solve problems within the school (most of which they themselves might as well created) for reasons aesthetic rather than financial, these five gorgeous boys sweep Mayumi into their world of excitement, danger, and overwhelming beauty.\n\n(Source: Vertical, edited)", "Bishounen Series", "Pretty Boy Detective Club", "美少年シリーズ", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/122943/Bishounen_Series", 12 },
                    { 123157, "", 9, new DateTime(2017, 3, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/287191.jpg", 44124, null, new DateTime(2016, 12, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Anthology of short stories created by various mangaka to celebrate the release of the live-action Hollywood Ghost in the Shell movie adaptation.", "Koukaku Kidoutai: Ghost in the Shell Comic Tribute", null, "攻殻機動隊 ゴースト・イン・ザ・シェル コミックトリビュート", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123157/Koukaku_Kidoutai__Ghost_in_the_Shell_Comic_Tribute", 1 },
                    { 123318, "", 23, new DateTime(2022, 2, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/256559.jpg", 25435, null, new DateTime(2019, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "This manga will center on Samurai Caliber, and a girl named Hime Kuzuki, who has been entrusted with Caliber's fifth sword.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "SSSS.Gridman: Hime to Samurai", null, "SSSS.GRIDMAN 姫とサムライ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123318/SSSSGridman__Hime_to_Samurai", 3 },
                    { 123319, "", 20, new DateTime(2020, 10, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/250595.jpg", 25436, null, new DateTime(2019, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga will focus on the four Neon Genesis Junior High Students and their everyday lives as they chase after cats, buy groceries, and eat nabe together.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "SSSS.Gridman: Shinseki Chuugakusei Nikki", null, "SSSS.GRIDMAN 新世紀中学生日記", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123319/SSSSGridman__Shinseki_Chuugakusei_Nikki", 2 },
                    { 123452, null, 44, new DateTime(2023, 8, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/234829.jpg", 9002, 6.99m, new DateTime(2019, 8, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Tate no Yuusha no Oshinagaki", "The Menu of the Shield Hero", "盾の勇者のおしながき", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123452/Tate_no_Yuusha_no_Oshinagaki", 7 },
                    { 123456, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/232832.jpg", 7221, 7.11m, new DateTime(2019, 11, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "It is common knowledge that it is best to become an adventurer when you are as young as possible because the magical power that is the basis of an adventurer's strength will hardly grow if you don't train it while you are young. But this man, Rick Gladiator, who became an adventurer when he was over thirty years old, had the combat power of an S-rank adventurer, the highest rank in the world. In fact, Rick has lived an unimaginable life with the members of the legendary Orihalcon Fist, a party of the continent's strongest adventurers. From dragons to vampires, Rick's fighting prowess, trained by his literally \"monster\" mentors, allows him to defeat elite adventurers one after another who try to underestimate him.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Shinmai Ossan Boukensha, Saikyou Party ni Shinu hodo Kitaerarete Muteki ni Naru.", null, "新米オッサン冒険者、最強パーティに死ぬほど鍛えられて無敵になる。", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123456/Shinmai_Ossan_Boukensha_Saikyou_Party_ni_Shinu_hodo_Kitaerarete_Muteki_ni_Naru", null },
                    { 123613, "", 52, new DateTime(2021, 12, 10, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/236197.jpg", 25466, null, new DateTime(2019, 11, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Yuuta Hibiki, a first year high-school student living in Tsutsujidai, suddenly lost his memories when he woke up one day. While confused due to not being able to remember who he is, Yuuta meets an existence called Hyper Agent Gridman. And it tells Yuuta to remember his mission!?\n\n(Source: Shueisha, translated)", "SSSS.Gridman", null, "SSSS.GRIDMAN", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123613/SSSSGridman", 6 },
                    { 123901, null, 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/242273.jpg", 15458, 6.55m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 18, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Saint Seiya: Destiny", null, "聖闘士星矢DESTINY", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123901/Saint_Seiya__Destiny", null },
                    { 123992, "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e: 2-nensei-hen has been published in English as Classroom of the Elite: Year 2 by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint since July 19, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/235363.jpg", 41, 8.8m, new DateTime(2020, 1, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "As Kiyotaka Ayanokouji and his classmates begin their second-year life, changes are seen everywhere throughout Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School. With the third-years having graduated and incoming first-years entering the school, alliances are well underway. Additionally, now that Miyabi Nagumo is the student council president, the promise of turning the school into a meritocracy may become a reality.\n\nMeanwhile, conflicts between classes continue to build as the class point totals draw close. With another special exam looming ahead, will Ayanokouji remain in the shadows, or will he finally enter the spotlight and help his class rise to the illustrious Class A?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e: 2-nensei-hen", "Classroom of the Elite: Year 2", "ようこそ実力至上主義の教室へ 2年生編", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/123992/Youkoso_Jitsuryoku_Shijou_Shugi_no_Kyoushitsu_e__2-nensei-hen", null },
                    { 124085, "Mashle was simulpub digitally in English as Mashle: Magic and Muscles through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since July 20, 2021. It has also been released in Polish by Studio JG since May 6, 2022.", 162, new DateTime(2023, 7, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/230705.jpg", 2189, 7.62m, new DateTime(2020, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "To everyone else in his magic-dominated world, the young and powerless Mash Burnedead is a threat to the gene pool and must be purged. Living secretly in the forest, he spends every day training his body, building muscles strong enough to compete with magic itself! However, upon having his identity exposed and his peaceful life threatened, Mash begins his journey to becoming a \"Divine Visionary,\" a role so powerful that society would have no choice but to accept his existence.\n\nAnd so, in order to maintain his peaceful life, the magicless Mash enrolls in the prestigious Easton Magic Academy, competing against the children of some of the most powerful and elite in the realm. Lacking the very skill needed to survive at Easton, magic, Mash appears to already be at a disadvantage to his fellow classmates. In order to achieve his goals, Mash will have to fight his way through every trial using his fists alone, overcoming magic with muscles, all for the illustrious title of Divine Visionary!\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Mashle", "Mashle: Magic and Muscles", "マッシュル-MASHLE-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124085/Mashle", 18 },
                    { 124182, "", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/229153.jpg", 11489, 6.83m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Speeding straight toward the Public Safety Bureau, a rogue vehicle collides into the building, its driver being a frightened woman with abnormally high Crime Coefficient asking for help. As she can utter only a few words, Inspectors fail to gain a clear insight into the reason behind her plea. That is, aside from her identity: Izumi Yasaka, a psychologist from the Isolation Facility for Latent Criminals in Aomori Prefecture—known as the \"Sanctuary.\"\n\nInspector Mika Shimotsuki, along with Enforcers Nobuchika Ginoza and Yayoi Kunizuka, is tasked with transferring Yasaka back to the rehabilitation center and performing a security check while on its grounds. But as the employees get in the way of the investigation and with Kunizuka temporarily detained, it does not take long for the detectives to realize that the Sanctuary is far from the paradise that it claims to be.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Psycho-Pass: Sinners of the System Case.1 - Tsumi to Bachi", null, "PSYCHO-PASS | SS (Sinners of the System) Case.1「罪と罰」", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124182/Psycho-Pass__Sinners_of_the_System_Case1_-_Tsumi_to_Bachi", 1 },
                    { 124183, "", 6, new DateTime(2020, 3, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/229154.jpg", 8851, 7m, new DateTime(2019, 9, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Traversing the war-scarred lands of the Southeast Asian Union outside of Japan, Shinya Kougami's next destination is the Tibet-Himalayan Alliance Kingdom. On his way, he makes acquaintance with Guillermo Garcia, commander of a paramilitary group with the goal of restoring peace, but refuses his offer to join them.\n\nWhen Kougami jumps in to aid a vehicle of refugees being attacked by guerrillas, his remarkable combat skills awe Tenzing Wangchuck—a young girl of Japanese and Tibetan descent who lost her parents to the violence of war. Motivated by Kougami's ability, Tenzing requests that he teaches her how to fight for the purpose of taking the life of the man who killed her parents.\n\nAlthough murder conflicts with Kougami's unwavering morals, he sympathizes with Tenzing and agrees to train her. But soon enough, Frederica Hanashiro from Japan's Ministry of Foreign Affairs appears, on her mission of bringing back to Japan and the Sibyl System the once abandoned Japanese emigrants—one of whom is Tenzing.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Psycho-Pass: Sinners of the System Case.3 - Onshuu no Kanata ni＿＿", null, "PSYCHO-PASS | SS (Sinners of the System) Case.3 恩讐の彼方に＿＿", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124183/Psycho-Pass__Sinners_of_the_System_Case3_-_Onshuu_no_Kanata_ni＿＿", 1 },
                    { 124305, "Akuyaku Reijou Level 99: Watashi wa Ura-Boss desu ga Maou dewa Arimasen has been published in English as Villainess Level 99: I May Be the Hidden Boss But I'm Not the Demon Lord by One Peace Books since August 15, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/238943.jpg", 3802, 7.4m, new DateTime(2020, 2, 4, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "A certain otome RPG takes place in the Valschein Kingdom, where dark hair is stigmatized to an abnormal degree. Yumiella Dolkness is the daughter of a count, hated from birth due to her pitch-black locks—and she is also the hidden boss! In a twist of fate, at five years of age, Yumiella recalls memories of her past life in Japan. Uninterested in the romance aspect of the original game, she begins to dedicate herself to training her rare dark-type magic.\n\nDespite this, Yumiella's goals are clear: avoid becoming the hidden boss and stay out of the limelight. Upon entering the magic academy, however, she shakes the foundation of the kingdom when her level 99 status comes to light. Whether a physical brawl or magic duel, her abilities are unmatched, and coupled with her black hair, she sticks out like a sore thumb. To make matters worse, the original heroine begins suspecting she is the demon lord! Can the deadpan noble girl achieve her wish of a peaceful life?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Akuyaku Reijou Level 99: Watashi wa Ura-Boss desu ga Maou dewa Arimasen", "Villainess Level 99: I May Be the Hidden Boss But I'm Not the Demon Lord", "悪役令嬢レベル99 ～私は裏ボスですが魔王ではありません～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124305/Akuyaku_Reijou_Level_99__Watashi_wa_Ura-Boss_desu_ga_Maou_dewa_Arimasen", null },
                    { 124340, null, null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/246287.jpg", 25589, null, new DateTime(2020, 1, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, null, "Saint Seiya Episode G: Requiem", null, "聖闘士星矢EPISODE.Gレクイエム", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124340/Saint_Seiya_Episode_G__Requiem", null },
                    { 124470, "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu: Dai-4 Shou - Seiiki to Gouyoku no Majo adapts volumes 10 through 15 of the light novel series. The manga has been published in English as Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-, Chapter 4: The Sanctuary and the Witch of Greed by Yen Press since January 26, 2021, and in Polish by Waneko since March 10, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/227408.jpg", 575, 8.1m, new DateTime(2019, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "On to the next stage: the witch's tomb known as the Sanctuary-Determined to release Rem from a mysterious slumber, Subaru and Emilia return to Roswaal's manor in search of clues on how to reach the Sanctuary, the secret location to which Ram and Roswaal escaped. But the way there is fraught with the unexpected-especially for Subaru, who finds himself in the company of a curious figure. A new chapter begins, and with it, a new adventure...\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu: Dai-4 Shou - Seiiki to Gouyoku no Majo", "Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-, Chapter 4: The Sanctuary and the Witch of Greed", "Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 第四章 聖域と強欲の魔女", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124470/Re_Zero_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu__Dai-4_Shou_-_Seiiki_to_Gouyoku_no_Majo", null },
                    { 124619, null, 2, new DateTime(2017, 5, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/227242.jpg", 14169, 6.64m, new DateTime(2017, 4, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "To LOVE-Ru Bangai-hen: Multiplication - Mae kara Ushiro kara", null, "To LOVEる -とらぶる- 番外編「Multiplication～前から後ろから～」", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124619/To_LOVE-Ru_Bangai-hen__Multiplication_-_Mae_kara_Ushiro_kara", null },
                    { 124620, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/227243.jpg", 13958, 6.66m, new DateTime(2017, 11, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After partaking in a challenge between the Deviluke sisters to see who can withstand cold temperatures the longest, Lala Satalin Deviluke falls sick due to her unwillingness to give up. Worried about her wellbeing, Rito Yuuki decides to go to her room to check up on her. However, when he accidentally steps on one of her peculiar inventions, he inadvertently transforms into a thermometer, causing the situation to turn quite steamy...\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "To LOVE-Ru: Tokubetsu Bangai-hen", null, "To LOVEる -とらぶる- 特別番外編", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124620/To_LOVE-Ru__Tokubetsu_Bangai-hen", null },
                    { 124629, "", 28, new DateTime(2021, 8, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/254768.jpg", 25638, null, new DateTime(2019, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Centered around two rookie inspectors of the Ministry of Welfare's Public Safety Bureau (MWPSB); Arata Shindou and Kei Mikhail Ignatov. These two inspectors are confronted with an ever changing society under the jurisdiction of the all knowing and impartial system of collective consciousness known as Sibyl and a contradiction that exists solely to evince the imperfections of the Sibyl system. Contending with an increasing anti immigrant sentiment, political intrigue, as well as peculiar individuals who exist solely to test the Sibyl system, these two inspectors are confronted with two choices, which are to either follow or overturn the system.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Psycho-Pass 3", null, "PSYCHO-PASS 3", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124629/Psycho-Pass_3", 4 },
                    { 124743, "Re:IF kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu was released as a purchase bonus for those who bought all volumes of the limited edition Blu-Ray/DVDs of the first season of Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu.", 9, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/283138.jpg", 4578, 7.32m, new DateTime(2017, 4, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "An alternate story where Rem and Subaru live happily together after escaping to the countryside of Kararagi.", "Re:IF kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu", null, "Re:IFから始める異世界生活", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124743/Re_IF_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu", 1 },
                    { 124776, "", 67, new DateTime(2016, 8, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/227503.jpg", 25674, null, new DateTime(2010, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In F.C. 60, the 13th Gundam Fight begins. Domon Kasshu pilots the Shining Gundam as the representative of Neo Japan, the Japanese space colony. Along with his crew member Rain Mikamura, he battles the other countries' representatives in order to earn the right to rule Earth and the colonies for four years for Neo Japan. However, Domon seems to be more concerned with finding his brother and the stolen Devil Gundam.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Choukyuu! Kidou Butouden G Gundam", "Mobile Fighter G Gundam", "超級!機動武闘伝Gガンダム", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/124776/Choukyuu_Kidou_Butouden_G_Gundam", 26 },
