                    { 125236, "", 18, new DateTime(2021, 2, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/235834.jpg", 15914, 6.51m, new DateTime(2019, 9, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "While Arata and the rest of girls are training to go to Dante's Gate, Anastasia goes to Biblia Academy to investigate a strange event that is related to \"The Demise.\"\n\n(Source: MU)", "Trinity Seven: Anastasia Seiden", "Trinity Seven: Anastasia Holy Story", "トリニティセブン アナスタシア聖伝", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/125236/Trinity_Seven__Anastasia_Seiden", 3 },
                    { 125735, null, 25, new DateTime(2020, 8, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/236976.jpg", 5415, 7.24m, new DateTime(2018, 10, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Mushoku Tensei: 4-koma ni Nattemo Honki Dasu", null, "無職転生～4コマになっても本気だす～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/125735/Mushoku_Tensei__4-koma_ni_Nattemo_Honki_Dasu", 3 },
                    { 125767, "Sword Art Online: Kiss and Fly has been published in English by Yen Press since June 18, 2024.", 16, new DateTime(2023, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/281699.jpg", 25841, null, new DateTime(2019, 9, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "This might be a game, but it's not something you play. Asuna and Kirito's romantic day turns into a quest to uncover the mystery of the flying house! Teaming up with some familiar faces may not be enough, though. They'll need heart, brains, and a whole lot of courage if they want to clear this one! And when Asuna begins to have out-of-body experiences, their investigation returns a shocking possibility—maybe it's not an issue with the system, but rather something tugging at her very soul...\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online: Kiss and Fly", "Sword Art Online: Kiss and Fly", "ソードアート・オンライン キス・アンド・フライ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/125767/Sword_Art_Online__Kiss_and_Fly", 3 },
                    { 125770, "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Houei no Barcarolle was published in English as Sword Art Online: Progressive - Barcarolle of Froth by Yen Press from November 3, 2020, to January 19, 2021.", 17, new DateTime(2019, 10, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/236995.jpg", 4170, 7.36m, new DateTime(2018, 4, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Kirito, having explored the latest beta test, has a pretty good idea of what to expect from the newest SAO launch. With Asuna along, the pair hope to experience the official playthrough together, but there's something about the release that's a little different from before... Certain unexpected tweaks from the previous version have Kirito and Asuna tackling a flood of puzzles anew!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Houei no Barcarolle", "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Barcarolle of Froth", "ソードアート・オンライン プログレッシブ 泡影のバルカローレ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/125770/Sword_Art_Online__Progressive_-_Houei_no_Barcarolle", 2 },
                    { 125771, "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Kuraki Yuuyami no Scherzo was published in English as Sword Art Online Progressive Scherzo of Deep Night by Yen Press from June 20, 2023 to January 23, 2024.", 20, new DateTime(2021, 11, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/242632.jpg", 4357, 7.34m, new DateTime(2020, 1, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Nearly two months have passed since Kirito and Asuna found themselves trapped in the world of Aincrad. Kirito's experience with the beta version of the game has put him far ahead of the curve, but it has also attracted the attention of some dangerous players...For Asuna, his competence has been a god send in this harsh world, yet she can't help but feel like her overreliance on Kirito's skills is becoming an obstacle to their growing relationship. Even so, they'll have to work together to make it through the ancient ruins of the fifth floor, where all sorts of undead monsters—and player-killers—lurk in the shadows!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Kuraki Yuuyami no Scherzo", "Sword Art Online Progressive Scherzo of Deep Night", "ソードアート・オンライン　プログレッシブ　冥き夕闇のスケルツォ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/125771/Sword_Art_Online__Progressive_-_Kuraki_Yuuyami_no_Scherzo", 3 },
                    { 126146, "\"Oshi no Ko\" ranked 11th and seventh in the 2021 and 2022 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division, respectively. The manga was nominated for the 14th and 15th Manga Taisho Awards and placed fifth and eighth in the final ranking, respectively. It was also nominated for the 46th and 48th Kodansha Manga Awards in the General category. The series has been published digitally in English through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published by Yen Press since January 17, 2023. It has also been released in French by Kurokawa since January 13, 2022; and in Polish by Studio JG since October 21, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/233991.jpg", 178, 8.46m, new DateTime(2020, 4, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Sixteen-year-old Ai Hoshino is a talented and beautiful idol who is adored by her fans. She is the personification of a pure, young maiden. But all that glitters is not gold.\n\nGorou Amemiya is a countryside gynecologist and a big fan of Ai. So when the pregnant idol shows up at his hospital, he is beyond bewildered. Gorou promises her a safe delivery. Little does he know, an encounter with a mysterious figure would result in his untimely death—or so he thought.\n\nOpening his eyes in the lap of his beloved idol, Gorou finds that he has been reborn as Aquamarine Hoshino—Ai's newborn son! With his world turned upside down, Gorou soon learns that the world of showbiz is paved with thorns, where talent does not always beget success. Will he manage to protect Ai's smile that he loves so much with the help of an eccentric and unexpected ally?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "\"Oshi no Ko\"", "[Oshi No Ko]", "【推しの子】", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126146/Oshi_no_Ko", null },
                    { 126241, null, 3, new DateTime(2019, 10, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/229574.jpg", 25900, null, new DateTime(2019, 8, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Fuuma no Kojirou: Jo no Maki", null, "風魔の小次郎 序の巻", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126241/Fuuma_no_Kojirou__Jo_no_Maki", null },
                    { 126287, "Sousou no Frieren ranked second and sixth in the 2021 and 2022 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division, respectively. In 2021, the series won the New Work Prize at the 25th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize awards. The manga was nominated twice for the 45th and 46th Kodansha Manga Awards in the Shounen category before winning the 48th Kodansha Manga Award in the same category in 2024. In the same year, the series won the 69th Shougakukan Manga Award. The series has been published in English as Frieren: Beyond Journey's End by VIZ Media under the Shonen Sunday imprint since November 9, 2021. The series has also been simulpub digitally through VIZ Manga. It has also been released in Polish as Frieren. U kresu drogi by Studio JG since May 12, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/232121.jpg", 34, 8.82m, new DateTime(2020, 4, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The Demon King has been defeated, and the victorious hero party returns home before disbanding. The four—mage Frieren, hero Himmel, priest Heiter, and warrior Eisen—reminisce about their decade-long journey as the moment to bid each other farewell arrives. But the passing of time is different for elves, thus Frieren witnesses her companions slowly pass away one by one.\n\nBefore his death, Heiter manages to foist a young human apprentice called Fern onto Frieren. Driven by the elf's passion for collecting a myriad of magic spells, the pair embarks on a seemingly aimless journey, revisiting the places that the heroes of yore had visited. Along their travels, Frieren slowly confronts her regrets of missed opportunities to form deeper bonds with her now-deceased comrades.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Sousou no Frieren", "Frieren: Beyond Journey's End", "葬送のフリーレン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126287/Sousou_no_Frieren", null },
                    { 126480, "", 17, new DateTime(2018, 2, 15, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/236045.jpg", 25963, null, new DateTime(2016, 12, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Blessed, a group of people who possess superhuman powers and intellect, and have manipulated human history since ancient times. Their goals are unknown and they cast a dark shadow over the world. Though few people believe in the Blessed's existence, one journalist named Lucy Davenport heads to Texas to contact a certain family, and she meets the cyborgs who escaped from the clutches of Black Ghost and have defended humanity from them and other threats. The cyborgs themselves have been freed from their duty of protecting humanity ever since the establishment of the UN Guardian troops, and they now live quiet lives of peace. However, Lucy's visit and the return of the Blessed draw Joe and the others once more unto the breach of a new battle.\n\n(Source: ANN, edited)", "Cyborg 009: Call of Justice", null, "CYBORG009 CALL OF JUSTICE", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126480/Cyborg_009__Call_of_Justice", 2 },
                    { 126487, "Akuyaku Reijou Level 99: Watashi wa Ura-Boss desu ga Maou dewa Arimasen began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on June 15, 2018. Kadokawa has released an expanded and illustrated version of the series since May 10, 2019 under its Kadokawa Books label. The series has been published digitally in English as Villainess Level 99: I May Be the Hidden Boss but I'm Not the Demon Lord by J-Novel Club since May 29, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/236050.jpg", 4583, 7.32m, new DateTime(2019, 5, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Yumiella Dolkness is your run-of-the-mill villainess in an otome RPG—except for the fact that she's also secretly the overpowered hidden boss. But Yumiella wasn't always Yumiella, you see. In her past life, she was nothing more than an introverted college student and devout gamer. So when she realizes that she's been reincarnated as a hidden boss, she's determined to steer clear of the protagonists and avoid her demise at their hands. All she wants is a nice, quiet life. Too bad when her gamer instincts kick in, Yumiella can't just ignore her awesome stats... A girl's gotta grind!\n\nSo, with plenty of time on her hands before starting life at the academy, she gets a little carried away and maxes out her level at 99. And when everyone else finds out, they get the wrong idea about her power—now they think she's the Demon Lord! Is this OP villainess strong enough to win back the peaceful life she always wanted?!\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Akuyaku Reijou Level 99: Watashi wa Ura-Boss desu ga Maou dewa Arimasen", "Villainess Level 99: I May Be the Hidden Boss but I'm Not the Demon Lord", "悪役令嬢レベル99 ～私は裏ボスですが魔王ではありません～", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126487/Akuyaku_Reijou_Level_99__Watashi_wa_Ura-Boss_desu_ga_Maou_dewa_Arimasen", null },
                    { 126522, "Rekishi ni Nokoru Akujo ni Naru zo: Akuyaku Reijou ni Naru hodo Ouji no Dekiai wa Kasoku suru you desu! has been published in English as I'll Become a Villainess Who Goes Down in History: It Seems Turning into a High-Born Baddie Makes the Prince All the More Lovestruck by Yen Press since October 15, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/238941.jpg", 5811, 7.21m, new DateTime(2020, 5, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Alicia is the eldest daughter of the noble Williams family—a bloodline that excels in dark magic. Her jet-black hair and golden eyes command a powerful presence, but her most unique features are, without a doubt, her sharp tongue and malevolent nature. By all means, she is a villainess, but also a fictional character from an otome game!\n\nAs an ardent admirer of Alicia, a young, unnamed woman wishes to be her. Fortunately, a sleepy truck driver grants her wish in a bizarre twist of events—killing and consequently reincarnating her as a seven-year-old Alicia inside the game. With sufficient knowledge of how the game plays out, \"Alicia\" is confident that she will go down as the greatest villainess in history as long as she endeavors to work hard. However, she soon begins to realize that escaping Alicia's fate is not so simple as it seemed.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Rekishi ni Nokoru Akujo ni Naru zo: Akuyaku Reijou ni Naru hodo Ouji no Dekiai wa Kasoku suru you desu!", "I'll Become a Villainess Who Goes Down in History: It Seems Turning into a High-Born Baddie Makes the Prince All the More Lovestruck", "歴史に残る悪女になるぞ 悪役令嬢になるほど王子の溺愛は加速するようです！", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126522/Rekishi_ni_Nokoru_Akujo_ni_Naru_zo__Akuyaku_Reijou_ni_Naru_hodo_Ouji_no_Dekiai_wa_Kasoku_suru_you_desu", null },
                    { 126738, "Hakata Tonkotsu Ramens won grand prize in the 20th Dengeki Novel Prize.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/252788.jpg", 26011, null, new DateTime(2014, 2, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Crime runs rampant in Fukuoka's seedy underworld. The Hakata ward is especially hard-hit, being a gathering place for top-class assassins, private eyes, information-mongers and professional avengers. Perhaps the most legendary among them is the Niwaka Samurai, notorious for being an \"assassin of assassins.\"\n\nIn the midst of all this, private detective Banba Zenji appears to be the eye of the storm, calmly and cheerfully investigating cases for his police officer friend and playing baseball in his spare time. But when he becomes the target of a powerful crime syndicate and has a run-in with a young cross-dresser named Lin Xianming, life in Hakata may never be the same again.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Hakata Tonkotsu Ramens", null, "博多豚骨ラーメンズ", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/126738/Hakata_Tonkotsu_Ramens", null },
                    { 127114, "One Piece Novel: A was published in English as One Piece: Ace's Story by VIZ Media from May 5, 2020 to September 1, 2020.", 11, new DateTime(2018, 6, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/232216.jpg", 989, 7.9m, new DateTime(2017, 7, 6, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Washed up on the shores of a deserted island at the edge of the East Blue Sea, two men from different backgrounds unite in their shared thirst for adventure. One of them, Portgaz D. Ace, will follow in his infamous father’s footsteps as the fearless captain of a pirate crew. The other, Masked Deuce, becomes the reluctant first member of Ace’s Spade Pirates. Survival is not enough for these seafaring buccaneers, as together they seek treasure, excitement, and a route to the New World.\n\n(Source: Viz Media)", "One Piece Novel: A", "One Piece: Ace's Story", "ONE PIECE novel A", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/127114/One_Piece_Novel__A", 2 },
                    { 127130, "Tensei shitara Ken deshita: Another Wish has been published in English as Reincarnated as a Sword: Another Wish by Seven Seas Entertainment since January 18, 2022.", 32, new DateTime(2023, 1, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/239533.jpg", 6390, 7.16m, new DateTime(2020, 5, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Reincarnated as a sentient weapon with memories of his past life, but not his name, a magical sword saved a young beastgirl from a life of slavery. Fran, the cat-eared girl, has become his wielder, and wants only to grow stronger, while the sword wants to know why he is here. Follow their new adventures in this spin-off manga series!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Tensei shitara Ken deshita: Another Wish", "Reincarnated as a Sword: Another Wish", "転生したら剣でした Another Wish", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/127130/Tensei_shitara_Ken_deshita__Another_Wish", 6 },
                    { 127222, "", 10, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/232811.jpg", 9679, 6.94m, new DateTime(2018, 12, 20, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A collection of stories by various mangaka, centered around the hit series Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari. This manga is filled with the charm of the heroine Raphtalia.", "Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari Anthology: Raphtalia to Issho", null, "盾の勇者の成り上がりアンソロジー ラフタリアといっしょ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/127222/Tate_no_Yuusha_no_Nariagari_Anthology__Raphtalia_to_Issho", 1 },
                    { 127781, "Tensei Kizoku, Kantei Skill de Nariagaru: Jakushou Ryouchi wo Uketsuida node, Yuushuu na Jinzai wo Fuyashiteitara, Saikyou Ryouchi ni Natteta has been published in English as As a Reincarnated Aristocrat, I'll Use My Appraisal Skill to Rise in the World by Kodansha USA since November 15, 2022. The series has also been simulpub through K Manga.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/236898.jpg", 14261, 6.64m, new DateTime(2020, 6, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "An ordinary salaryman dies one day and is reborn as Ars Louvent, the son of a noble. Although he is not talented in magic or swordplay, he does have one skill that no one else possesses: Appraisal. Using this ability, Ars can determine a person's current strength, how much potential they hold, and where their talents rest.\n\nThis skill is especially useful in the present situation of the country. The government is corrupt, revolts occur more often than not, and nobles far and wide are strengthening their fortifications in preparation for an all-out war. With this in mind, Ars realizes he too must prepare by gathering talented people.\n\nA persecuted foreigner unparalleled with the sword, a slave with an unknown talent for magic, and a timid boy with an unquenchable thirst for knowledge—such talents lend Ars their support as he aims to create the most powerful territory.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tensei Kizoku, Kantei Skill de Nariagaru: Jakushou Ryouchi wo Uketsuida node, Yuushuu na Jinzai wo Fuyashiteitara, Saikyou Ryouchi ni Natteta", "As a Reincarnated Aristocrat, I'll Use My Appraisal Skill to Rise in the World", "転生貴族、鑑定スキルで成り上がる～弱小領地を受け継いだので、優秀な人材を増やしていたら、最強領地になってた～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/127781/Tensei_Kizoku_Kantei_Skill_de_Nariagaru__Jakushou_Ryouchi_wo_Uketsuida_node_Yuushuu_na_Jinzai_wo_Fuyashiteitara_Saikyou_Ryouchi_ni_Natteta", null },
                    { 127907, "Kaijuu 8-gou was nominated for the 14th Manga Taisho Award and placed sixth in the final ranking in 2021. It ranked third in the 2022 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. The series has been published digitally in English as Monster #8 through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published in English as Kaiju No. 8 by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since December 7, 2021. It has also been released in Polish by Studio JG since October 29, 2021; and in Italian by Edizioni Star Comics since March 16, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/252929.jpg", 1485, 7.75m, new DateTime(2020, 7, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Grotesque, Godzilla-like monsters called \"kaijuu\" have been appearing around Japan for many years. To combat these beasts, an elite military unit known as the Defense Corps risks their lives daily to protect civilians. Once a creature is killed, \"sweepers\"—working under the Professional Kaijuu Cleaner Corporation—are left to dispose of its remains.\n\nKafka Hibino, a 32-year-old man, is unsatisfied with his job as a sweeper. From a young age, he has aspired to join the Defense Corps and kill kaijuus for a living. After a few failed attempts, however, he gave up on his dreams and resigned himself to the mediocrity that provided a decent paycheck. Nevertheless, when an ambitious, 18-year-old recruit named Reno Ichikawa joins his cleaning team, Kafka is once again reminded of his desire to join the military.\n\nFollowing a chain of unfortunate events and an interaction with the junior sweeper, Kafka encounters a parasite-type kaijuu that forces its way in through his mouth—turning him into a humanoid monster. With his newfound powers, Kafka aims to give his lifelong dream a final try.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kaijuu 8-gou", "Kaiju No. 8", "怪獣8号", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/127907/Kaijuu_8-gou", null },
                    { 127941, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/234918.jpg", 4678, 7.31m, new DateTime(2019, 8, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Hitoyoshi Yokoya is a high school student who currently lives alone. One day, an unfamiliar girl knocks on his door and offers to be his maid. She reveals that she is a former assassin, which makes Hitoyoshi nervous. But when her skills save him from being run over by a truck, Hitoyoshi ultimately decides to take her in.\n\nHowever, the mysterious girl actually has no household skills. In fact, her only expertise is assassination, as she has lived her entire life for the sake of killing. Nonetheless, her time with Hitoyoshi allows her to experience new emotions she had never felt before, inspiring her to become a regular girl.\n\nIn order to advance toward this upcoming chapter in her life, she asks Hitoyoshi to grant her a new name, to which he names her Yuki. Having someone she can finally consider family, Yuki acquires new fond memories that fill her heart with warmth as she tries to leave her dark and lonely past behind.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Kimi wa Meido-sama.", "You Are Ms. Servant.", "君は冥土様。", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/127941/Kimi_wa_Meido-sama", null },
                    { 128131, "Kimi ni Todoke Bangai-hen: Unmei no Hito was published in English as Kimi ni Todoke: From Me to You - Soulmate by VIZ Media under the Shojo Beat imprint from April 2, 2024, to October 1, 2024.", 13, new DateTime(2022, 5, 12, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/237197.jpg", 1343, 7.79m, new DateTime(2018, 4, 12, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "With her jet-black hair, sinister smile, and silent demeanor, Sawako \"Sadako\" Kuronuma always had trouble fitting in during high school. But with help from her friends, her boyfriend Kazehaya, and even her rival-turned-friend Kurumi, Sawako came out of her shell. Now in college, Sawako and Kurumi have become incredibly close, but Kurumi longs for a romance of her own.\n\nDespite considering herself unlovable, and despite feeling deeply satisfied with Sawako's companionship, Kurumi decides to put herself out there and try dating. When she's pestered by a persistent suitor after a party, a handsome stranger comes to her rescue. He looks suspiciously like Sawako...or not so suspicious, considering that he is actually Sawako's cousin! When Kurumi starts to feel drawn to him, could it be love?\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Kimi ni Todoke Bangai-hen: Unmei no Hito", "Kimi ni Todoke: From Me to You - Soulmate", "君に届け 番外編～運命の人～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128131/Kimi_ni_Todoke_Bangai-hen__Unmei_no_Hito", 3 },
                    { 128368, "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka II has been published in English as Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? II by Yen Press since November 16, 2021. It has also been published digitally in English by Square Enix through Manga UP!", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/235235.jpg", 6141, 7.19m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After Mikoto ventures into Orario's pleasure quarter on a lead to find her long-lost friend, Bell, Lily, and Welf decide to join the search! Unfortunately, Bell's hardly comfortable in such an unfamiliar environment, and after he gets separated from the group, he soon finds himself in a part of Orario he never knew existed. There, he spies a beautiful girl with fox ears and a tail, but little does he know, she's exactly who Mikoto's been looking for...\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka II", "Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? II", "ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうかⅡ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128368/Dungeon_ni_Deai_wo_Motomeru_no_wa_Machigatteiru_Darou_ka_II", null },
                    { 128594, "The one-shot, Roronoa Zoro, Umi ni Chiru, was simulpub in English as One Piece: Boichi Covers Zolo vs. Mihawk by VIZ Media. One Piece: Episode A was published in English as One Piece: Ace's Story by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint from March 12, 2024 to June 11, 2024.", 6, new DateTime(2021, 12, 1, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/266074.jpg", 594, 8.09m, new DateTime(2020, 9, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The infamous Portgas D. Ace's departure from Dawn Island marks the beginning of his pirate adventure, and he immediately finds himself deserted on an uninhabited, desolate island. There, he meets a mysterious man, who quickly becomes drawn to Ace's personality and befriends him. Aiming to get themselves off the island, the duo decides to work together to build a boat.\n\nHowever, due to a lack of food on the isle, the pair only have so much time to finish making their craft, causing tension to arise between the two. Nonetheless, the appearance of a special fruit may give them the hope needed to escape the island—because if they succeed, they vow to sail the Grand Line together.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]\n\nIncluded one-shots:\nVolume 1: Roronoa Zoro, Umi ni Chiru (Zolo Overboard)\nVolume 2: Nami vs. Kalifa", "One Piece: Episode A", "One Piece: Ace's Story", "ONE PIECE episode A", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128594/One_Piece__Episode_A", 2 },
                    { 128632, "Arifureta Gakuen de Sekai Saikyou is based off the side-story \"Arifureta Mahou Gakuen-hen\" (ありふれた魔法学園編), which was included in the light novel.", 11, new DateTime(2021, 7, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/242790.jpg", 11968, 6.79m, new DateTime(2020, 4, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Special student Hajime Nagumo enters the largest magic school of Tortus to meet new friends, enemies and fall in love with the most powerful vampire in this world, Yue.\n\n(Source: Overlap, translated)", "Arifureta Gakuen de Sekai Saikyou", null, "ありふれた学園で世界最強", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128632/Arifureta_Gakuen_de_Sekai_Saikyou", 2 },
                    { 128691, "Mokushiroku no Yonkishi has been published digitally as an English simulpub as The Seven Deadly Sins: Four Knights of the Apocalypse by Kodansha USA. It has also been published digitally and physically in book format since January 25, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/243307.jpg", 5440, 7.24m, new DateTime(2021, 1, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Percival has always lived with his grandfather on God's Finger, a remote haven that sits high above the clouds. And though he loves the simple life, he secretly longs for adventure. But Percival's life is changed forever when an intruder—who shares a shocking connection with him—tears away everything he's ever known.\n\nWith nothing left to do but chase down the one who took everything from him, Percival sets out on his own. During his journey, the sheltered boy discovers that there are a lot of things he doesn't know about normal life. Luckily, he meets friends along the way who can help him get by—but how will they react when they find out about Percival's destiny... and how it's connected to the end of the world?\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)", "Mokushiroku no Yonkishi", "The Seven Deadly Sins: Four Knights of the Apocalypse", "黙示録の四騎士", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128691/Mokushiroku_no_Yonkishi", null },
                    { 128694, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/233910.jpg", 2459, 7.57m, new DateTime(2020, 8, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Taiki Inomata is a student enthusiastic about sports and aspires to arrive first at his school's blue-box gymnasium every day. Unfortunately, his morning smile quickly turns into a frown as he loses again and again to the girl's basketball team leader: Chinatsu Kano. Despite this, Taiki secretly likes his senior, and just the sight of her rekindles his zealous spirit.\n\nWith a firm resolve, Taiki plans to declare his love to Chinatsu soon. However, a love confession is far from easy, with Chinatsu potentially having other admirers and Taiki being a complete stranger to her. Can Taiki's youthful love flourish inside the blue box?\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Ao no Hako", null, "アオのハコ", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128694/Ao_no_Hako", null },
                    { 128837, "", 12, new DateTime(2020, 11, 26, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/236638.jpg", 16636, 6.45m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Set in the same universe as High School DxD, but years before the events of that series, the story centers on Tobio Ikuse, a high school student still reeling from an incident that caused the disappearance of his childhood friends. One day, he is attacked by beings known as \"Utsusemi,\" but is rescued by Natsume, one of his missing friends. Together with Natsume and another girl named Vali, he races to find out the cause of his friends' disappearance.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Daten no Inugami: Slash Døg - High School DxD Universe", null, "堕天の狗神 -SLASHDØG- ハイスクールD×D Universe", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/128837/Daten_no_Inugami__Slash_Døg_-_High_School_DxD_Universe", 2 },
                    { 129262, "Hira Yakunin Yatte 1500-nen, Maou no Chikara de Daijin ni Sarechaimashita has been published in English as I Was a Bottom-Tier Bureaucrat for 1,500 Years, and the Demon King Made Me a Minister by Yen Press since April 27, 2021.", 16, new DateTime(2020, 8, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/235771.jpg", 5397, 7.25m, new DateTime(2019, 1, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "For 1,500 years, Beelzebub has happily taken it easy as a rank-and-file clerk. But her lazy lifestyle comes to an end when the new demon king suddenly promotes her to minister! Can she adopt the appearance and demeanor expected of the highest demon on the bureaucratic pyramid?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Hira Yakunin Yatte 1500-nen, Maou no Chikara de Daijin ni Sarechaimashita", "I Was a Bottom-Tier Bureaucrat for 1,500 Years, and the Demon King Made Me a Minister", "ヒラ役人やって1500年、魔王の力で大臣にされちゃいました", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/129262/Hira_Yakunin_Yatte_1500-nen_Maou_no_Chikara_de_Daijin_ni_Sarechaimashita", 3 },
                    { 129370, "Burn the Witch was simulpub in English through MANGA Plus. The volume was published by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on October 19, 2021.", 5, new DateTime(2020, 9, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/238094.jpg", 11520, 6.82m, new DateTime(2020, 8, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 3, "Ninny Spangcole is the leader of popular girl group, Cecile Die Twice, but her ambitions stretch far beyond a successful music career. In the hidden underground world of Reverse London, Ninny and her partner Noel \"Niiha\" Niihashi strive to achieve loftier goals as \"Witches,\" members of the organization Wing Bind which is dedicated to the handling of dragons. These powerful creatures once caused over half of all casualties in the city proper, prior to Reverse London splitting away from Front London. As dragons are invisible to most Front Londoners, their existence has become a mere myth, and Reverse Londoners have taken up the front lines. Thus, Wing Bind was created, prohibiting non-licensed individuals from coming into any contact with dragons.\n\nNinny and Noel have their work cut out for them when they are assigned as the caretakers of Balgo Ywain Parks and his dog Osushi-chan. With trouble persistently trailing close behind him, the two girls are left to deal with the aftermath. Even more problems arise when Macy Baljure, Ninny’s former bandmate, appears in Reverse London with a dragon by her side.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Burn the Witch", "Burn the Witch", "BURN THE WITCH", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/129370/Burn_the_Witch", 1 },
                    { 130174, "Hira Yakunin Yatte 1500-nen, Maou no Chikara de Daijin ni Sarechaimashita was published in English as I Was a Bottom-Tier Bureaucrat for 1,500 Years, and the Demon King Made Me a Minister by Yen Press under its Yen On imprint on March 30, 2021.", 12, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/237493.jpg", 26450, null, new DateTime(2019, 9, 12, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A devil's work is never done!\n\nBeelzebub is a demon of many roles—minister of agriculture, Azusa's \"big sister\" and the demon king's closest confidant. Before her illustrious rise to power, though, she was just a low-ranking pencil pusher in the government with no ambitions, no dreams, and no adventure in her life. Then, on a whim of the newly coronated demon king, she received the biggest and most terrifying promotion imaginable! How will Beelzebub handle the sudden responsibilities of the entire Ministry of Agriculture?!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Hira Yakunin Yatte 1500-nen, Maou no Chikara de Daijin ni Sarechaimashita", "I Was a Bottom-Tier Bureaucrat for 1,500 Years, and the Demon King Made Me a Minister", "ヒラ役人やって１５００年、魔王の力で大臣にされちゃいました", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/130174/Hira_Yakunin_Yatte_1500-nen_Maou_no_Chikara_de_Daijin_ni_Sarechaimashita", 1 },
                    { 130314, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/237178.jpg", 1444, 7.76m, new DateTime(2020, 10, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The curtain has lowered on Tatsuya Shiba's turbulent high school life, during which he has defeated countless formidable enemies. He has now set in motion the realization of his new ambitions: The General Incorporated Association \"Magian Company.\" The purpose of the organization to which Tatsuya was appointed the managing director of, is to implement protections to guarantee the human rights of magicians who possess a magical aptitude, yet are not able to reach a practical level. While being a college student, Tatsuya has steadily moved towards securing a new era where magicians can live as ordinary humans rather than as living weapons. For Tatsuya, whose influence has surpassed that of other Strategic-Class Magicians, the direction in which he has chosen to go has naturally attracted the attention of others from around the world. An assassin from the magician association \"FEHR\" in the USNA, is sent to investigate the direction Tatsuya has chosen to go... The curtain opens on the new legend of Tatsuya Shiba.\n\n(Source: Kadokawa, translated)", "Zoku Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Magian Company", "The Irregular at Magic Highschool: Magian Company", "続・魔法科高校の劣等生 メイジアン・カンパニー", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/130314/Zoku_Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Magian_Company", null },
                    { 130331, "Shangri-La Frontier: Kusoge Hunter, Kamige ni Idoman to su is an adaptation of the web novel of the same title released on Shousetsuka ni Narou. The series has been published digitally in English as Shangri-La Frontier by Kodansha USA since December 8, 2020, and in print since September 6, 2022, and it has also been simulpub. The series won the 47th Kodansha Manga Award in the shounen category in 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/235471.jpg", 749, 8m, new DateTime(2020, 7, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Second year high school student Rakurou Hizutome is interested in one thing only: finding \"shitty games\" and beating the crap out of them. His gaming skills are second to none, and no game is too bad for him to enjoy. So when he's introduced to the new VR game Shangri-La Frontier, he does what he does best—min-maxes and skips the prologue to jump straight into the action. But can even an expert gamer like Rakurou discover all the secrets that Shangri-La Frontier hides...?\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)", "Shangri-La Frontier: Kusoge Hunter, Kamige ni Idoman to su", "Shangri-La Frontier", "シャングリラ・フロンティア～クソゲーハンター、神ゲーに挑まんとす～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/130331/Shangri-La_Frontier__Kusoge_Hunter_Kamige_ni_Idoman_to_su", null },
                    { 130370, "Nanami Minami wa Kagayakitai: Jaku-Chara Tomozaki-kun Gaiden was published in English as Minami Nanami Wants to Shine by Yen Press from March 22, 2022 to February 20, 2024.", 12, new DateTime(2022, 11, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/238476.jpg", 3302, 7.45m, new DateTime(2020, 7, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Whether doing high jumps or blending with a crowd, Minami Nanami has always been flexible both physically and socially. But when her friend Aoi outshines her at her track-and-field specialty, Mimimi starts to wish for something more, a light to claim as her own. As she contemplates her talents, her mom asks if she'll model in a local ad for her makeup company. Faced with an unfamiliar challenge, can Mimimi find herself in this dazzling new world?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Nanami Minami wa Kagayakitai: Jaku-Chara Tomozaki-kun Gaiden", "Minami Nanami Wants to Shine", "七海みなみは輝きたい 弱キャラ友崎くん外伝", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/130370/Nanami_Minami_wa_Kagayakitai__Jaku-Chara_Tomozaki-kun_Gaiden", 3 },
                    { 130491, "", 12, new DateTime(2021, 4, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/235830.jpg", 26531, null, new DateTime(2020, 5, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga's story begins with Rikka waking up one day with her family's junk shop turned into a butler cafe. The Neon Genesis Junior High Students serve as the butlers.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "SSSS.Gridman: Shinseiki Chuugakusei no Shitsuji Café", "SSSS.Gridman: Neo Genesis Junior High School Students Butler Cafe", "SSSS.GRIDMAN 新世紀中学生の執事カフェ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/130491/SSSSGridman__Shinseiki_Chuugakusei_no_Shitsuji_Café", 2 },
                    { 131030, "Nageki no Bourei wa Intai shitai: Saijaku Hunter ni Yoru Saikyou Party Ikuseijutsu was published in English as Let This Grieving Soul Retire! Woe Is the Weakling Who Leads the Strongest Party by Sol Press on December 28, 2020. Sol Press published only one volume before it went defunct. The series has been published digitally in English by J-Novel Club since March 8, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/241416.jpg", 45319, null, new DateTime(2018, 8, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The golden age has dawned for treasure hunters, who raid treasure vaults all over the world in search of glory, despite the dangers. Immeasurable wealth, fame, and power await those who prevail.\n\n\"Let's be treasure hunters!\"\n\nThis promise between Krai Andrey and his friends came to a sad conclusion when young Krai realized he didn't have a treasure-hunting bone in his body. Yet for some reason, people's expectations of Krai continued to grow—as did the danger to his life. While his friends became greater, greedier beasts, Krai mastered the art of begging and pleading!\n\nWitness the weal and woe of a man who just wants to retire.\n\n(Source: Sol Press)", "Nageki no Bourei wa Intai shitai: Saijaku Hunter ni Yoru Saikyou Party Ikuseijutsu", "Let This Grieving Soul Retire! Woe Is the Weakling Who Leads the Strongest Party", "嘆きの亡霊は引退したい ～最弱ハンターによる最強パーティ育成術～", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131030/Nageki_no_Bourei_wa_Intai_shitai__Saijaku_Hunter_ni_Yoru_Saikyou_Party_Ikuseijutsu", null },
                    { 131041, "Saijaku Tamer wa Gomi Hiroi no Tabi wo Hajimemashita. @comic has been published in English as The Weakest Tamer Began a Journey to Pick Up Trash by Seven Seas Entertainment since June 14, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/236905.jpg", 2388, 7.58m, new DateTime(2020, 2, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "When Ivy was born into this world, she remembered her past life. Remembering her preincarnation, she strove to avoid strife. But fate curdled at the status check, when kids learn who they are. For she had only one skill - Taming - and not a single star.\n\nIvy was weak from the start - at most, she could tame a slime. And in her world, most people did not give the weak their time. Only one woman in her village would treat her as her own. But after she \"died,\" Ivy got the hint and ran from home.\n\nWhile on the run, she met a tiny slime and named it Sora. And such begins the heartwarming survival story of a small girl who can tame.\n\n(Source: TO Books, translated)", "Saijaku Tamer wa Gomi Hiroi no Tabi wo Hajimemashita. @comic", "The Weakest Tamer Began a Journey to Pick Up Trash", "最弱テイマーはゴミ拾いの旅を始めました。＠COMIC", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131041/Saijaku_Tamer_wa_Gomi_Hiroi_no_Tabi_wo_Hajimemashita_comic", null },
                    { 131084, "Assassin's Creed Valhalla x Vinland Saga was published digitally in English, French, German, Italian, Korean, Spanish, Mandarin, and Thai on the official Assassin's Creed Valhalla site on January 13, 2021.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/242607.jpg", 19380, 5.88m, new DateTime(2020, 10, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A 6-page collaboration comic between Assassin's Creed Valhalla and Vinland Saga.", "Assassin's Creed Valhalla x Vinland Saga", null, "『アサシンクリード ヴァルハラ』×『ヴィンランド・サガ』", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131084/Assassins_Creed_Valhalla_x_Vinland_Saga", null },
                    { 131121, "", 9, new DateTime(1987, 7, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/255419.jpg", 26619, null, new DateTime(1986, 11, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Jun Jun, independent private eye, solves hi-tech crimes and busts criminals using her feminine wit and charm, and also with the help of her homemade gadgets. An occasional enemy is Dr. Nekura, AKA the most evil genius in the world, who's desperate to prove he's better than everyone (especially Jun Jun).\n\n(Source: MangaDex)\n\nIncluded one-shot: Gyakuten Watson", "Pinky Punky", null, "ピンキー・パンキィ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131121/Pinky_Punky", 1 },
                    { 131215, "", 52, new DateTime(2023, 9, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/237151.jpg", 3665, 7.41m, new DateTime(2019, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Cid is a boy who reincarnated in another world, and decided to enjoy a scenario of being \"the eminence in shadow, someone who meddles with the story from the shadows, and exhibits his true power in secrecy.\" Thus unfolds the story of him and the secret organization he leads—Shadow Garden—as well their their pleasant friends! An easy-going 4-koma manga starts right here and now!\n\n(Source: Kadokawa, translated)", "Kage no Jitsuryokusha ni Naritakute!: Shadow Gaiden", "The Eminence in Shadow: Shadow Side Story.", "陰の実力者になりたくて! しゃどーがいでん", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131215/Kage_no_Jitsuryokusha_ni_Naritakute__Shadow_Gaiden", 6 },
                    { 131334, "Sakamoto Days has been simulpub digitally in English through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since April 5, 2022. It has also been released in Italian by Panini Comics since May 19, 2022; and in Polish by Studio JG since October 21, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/242919.jpg", 497, 8.15m, new DateTime(2020, 11, 20, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Tarou Sakamoto was considered the greatest hitman of all time. Feared by many, he stood at the top of the underground world until he met and fell in love with a woman. As a result, Sakamoto abandoned his life of crime and now works as a convenience store clerk.\n\nLeaving his shady past behind proves more difficult than Sakamoto initially imagined. Many of his former rivals and partners do not believe that he has truly left the business and show up in hopes of taking him out. Barred from killing, Sakamoto must find creative ways to subdue his enemies and prevent them from bringing harm to his family, his store, and the small town he resides in.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Sakamoto Days", "Sakamoto Days", "SAKAMOTO DAYS", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131334/Sakamoto_Days", null },
                    { 131396, "Sword Art Online: Alicization Lycoris is an adaptation of a video game with the same title, released on PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC.", 16, new DateTime(2021, 5, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/237559.jpg", 7917, 7.06m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 27, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "While on their way to Zakkaria from Rulid Village, Eugeo and Kirito encounter a noble girl named Medina battling monsters on the highway. Medina Orthinanos is a noble whose family was banished to the borderlands due to being considered defects by the empress of Norlangarth. Having lost her father in an accident, Medina seeks to become an Integrity Knight to clear her family's besmirched name. Little did she know that the two boys she encountered on the road to Zakkaria shared her goal of becoming Integrity Knights but would one day go up against the Axiom Church and kill the supreme ruler of the church...\n\n(Source: MangaDex)", "Sword Art Online: Alicization Lycoris", null, "ソードアート・オンライン アリシゼーション リコリス", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131396/Sword_Art_Online__Alicization_Lycoris", 3 },
                    { 131487, null, 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/237840.jpg", 10451, 6.89m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Sakamoto", null, "SAKAMOTO", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131487/Sakamoto", null },
                    { 131678, "Mazinger Z: Interval Peace is a prequel to the Mazinger Z Infinity movie. The series was published in Italian by Edizioni BD under the J-Pop imprint on October 25, 2018.", 6, new DateTime(2017, 10, 19, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/252891.jpg", 26689, null, new DateTime(2017, 5, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga takes place in a world where the use of Super Robots is questioned. Koji is a former pilot with his companions faced with both personal and outer conflicts. They were once heroes but peace was achieved, bringing their robot's use into question. Can this peace even last and can it even lead to true peace...?\n\n(Source: Mazinger Wiki)", "Mazinger Z: Interval Peace", null, "マジンガーZ インターバルピース", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131678/Mazinger_Z__Interval_Peace", 1 },
                    { 131706, "Kimetsu no Yaiba Gaiden was published in English as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Stories of Water and Flame by Viz Media on January 4, 2022.", 5, new DateTime(2020, 10, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/238006.jpg", 1813, 7.68m, new DateTime(2019, 3, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "1-2. Kimetsu no Yaiba: Tomioka Giyuu Gaiden\n3-4. Kimetsu no Yaiba: Rengoku Kyoujurou Gaiden\n5. Kimetsu no Aima!", "Kimetsu no Yaiba Gaiden", "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Stories of Water and Flame", "鬼滅の刃 外伝", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131706/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_Gaiden", 1 },
                    { 131924, "Tsue to Tsurugi no Wistoria has been published in English as Wistoria: Wand and Sword by Kodansha USA since November 29, 2022. The series has also been simulpub through K Manga.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/243105.jpg", 1345, 7.79m, new DateTime(2020, 12, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Will Serfort dreams of keeping his promise to a childhood friend by becoming a Magia Vander, one of the mighty magicians who sit atop the Wizard's Tower. However, he is unable to cast even the simplest of spells, leaving him to fight dungeon monsters to earn credits at Regarden Magical Academy. As if that weren't enough, he finds himself putting his sword skills to the test against a bullying professor!\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)", "Tsue to Tsurugi no Wistoria", "Wistoria: Wand and Sword", "杖と剣のウィストリア", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/131924/Tsue_to_Tsurugi_no_Wistoria", null },
                    { 132079, "", 12, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/238595.jpg", 11116, 6.85m, new DateTime(2019, 3, 21, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A collection of stories by various mangaka, centered around the hit series Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari. This manga is filled with the charm of the filolial Filo.", "Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari Anthology: Filo to Issho", null, "盾の勇者の成り上がりアンソロジー　フィーロといっしょ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132079/Tate_no_Yuusha_no_Nariagari_Anthology__Filo_to_Issho", 1 },
                    { 132100, "", 12, new DateTime(2012, 12, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/240058.jpg", 26732, null, new DateTime(2012, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Manga adaptation of the third Meitantei Conan movie.", "Meitantei Conan: Seikimatsu no Majutsushi", "Detective Conan the Movie: The Last Wizard of the Century", "名探偵コナン 世紀末の魔術師", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132100/Meitantei_Conan__Seikimatsu_no_Majutsushi", 3 },
                    { 132186, "", 11, new DateTime(2004, 5, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/238828.jpg", 26748, null, new DateTime(2004, 3, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "It will be the first year of high school for Tooru and as such, she decided to go live with her grandpa to be close to school. But it turns out that the old man is a robot engineer with a peculiar dream... for which he created the robot assistant Spin! What will happen to Tooru from now on!?\n\n(Source: Shueisha, translated)", "Mutekitekki Spin-chan", null, "無敵鉄姫スピンちゃん", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132186/Mutekitekki_Spin-chan", 1 },
                    { 132335, "Death Note Tanpenshuu was published in English as Death Note Short Stories by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on May 10, 2022. C Kira-hen, a.k.a. Death Note: Tokubetsu-hen, was drawn in commemoration of the screening of the live-action movie, L change the WorLd. The one-shot was published in English as a part of VIZ Media's Death Note All-in-One Edition, which was released on September 6, 2017.", 6, new DateTime(2020, 2, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/240669.jpg", 2972, 7.49m, new DateTime(2003, 8, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A collection of short stories about Death Note.\n\n1. C Kira-hen (C-Kira)\n2. a Kira-hen (a-Kira)\n3. Death Note ni Rakugaki 4-koma (Death Note Four-Panel Comics)\n4. L: Day One\n5. L: The Wammy's House\n6. Kagami Tarou-hen (Taro Kagami)", "Death Note Tanpenshuu", "Death Note Short Stories", "DEATH NOTE短編集", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132335/Death_Note_Tanpenshuu", 1 },
