                    { 132500, "Loop 7-kaime no Akuyaku Reijou wa, Moto Tekikoku de Jiyuu Kimama na Hanayome Seikatsu wo Mankitsu suru has been published in English as 7th Time Loop: The Villainess Enjoys a Carefree Life Married to Her Worst Enemy! by Seven Seas Entertainment since September 27, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/246550.jpg", 1904, 7.67m, new DateTime(2020, 12, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "By the seventh loop, Rishe Irmgard Weitzner knows all too well how her condemnation will go: with her engagement broken and an expulsion from her family. Each iteration, she has been thrown back to that exact moment, but she has lived her life differently each time. In the first loop, she became a merchant; in the second an herbalist; in another a handmaiden; and in the sixth a knight. Yet, no matter which occupation, she has always died at the age of 20.\n\nRishe's sixth life ended at the hand of Arnold Hein, the emperor of the neighboring country. However, at the start of her seventh loop, Arnold offers her a shocking proposal: become his fiancée and live in the lap of luxury by his side. In her previous lives, Rishe never had the chance to visit his country due to the war. Thus, she jumps at the opportunity to fulfill her long-held dream of seeing the world.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Loop 7-kaime no Akuyaku Reijou wa, Moto Tekikoku de Jiyuu Kimama na Hanayome Seikatsu wo Mankitsu suru", "7th Time Loop: The Villainess Enjoys a Carefree Life Married to Her Worst Enemy!", "ループ7回目の悪役令嬢は、元敵国で自由気ままな花嫁生活を満喫する", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132500/Loop_7-kaime_no_Akuyaku_Reijou_wa_Moto_Tekikoku_de_Jiyuu_Kimama_na_Hanayome_Seikatsu_wo_Mankitsu_suru", null },
                    { 132505, "Loop 7-kaime no Akuyaku Reijou wa, Moto Tekikoku de Jiyuu Kimama na Hanayome Seikatsu wo Mankitsu suru began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on February 7, 2020. Overlap has released a revised and illustrated version of the series since October 25, 2020 under its Overlap Novels f label. The series has been published in English as 7th Time Loop: The Villainess Enjoys a Carefree Life Married to Her Worst Enemy! by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint since July 19, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/241432.jpg", 782, 7.99m, new DateTime(2020, 10, 24, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Rishe, the daughter of a duke, is stuck in a time loop that begins at the moment her engagement is annulled and ends with her early demise at the age of 20. She has now begun her seventh loop. In her past do-overs, Rishe experienced various occupations, including being a merchant, a pharmacist, and a knight. But this time around, she simply wishes to live a long and leisurely life!\n\nThat was the plan, only for it to be derailed by an unprecedented marriage proposal from her killer in the previous loop, the neighboring country's Crown Prince—?!\n\n(Source: Overlap, translated)", "Loop 7-kaime no Akuyaku Reijou wa, Moto Tekikoku de Jiyuu Kimama na Hanayome Seikatsu wo Mankitsu suru", "7th Time Loop: The Villainess Enjoys a Carefree Life Married to Her Worst Enemy!", "ループ7回目の悪役令嬢は、元敵国で自由気ままな花嫁生活を満喫する", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132505/Loop_7-kaime_no_Akuyaku_Reijou_wa_Moto_Tekikoku_de_Jiyuu_Kimama_na_Hanayome_Seikatsu_wo_Mankitsu_suru", null },
                    { 132537, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/5/249925.jpg", 12611, 6.75m, new DateTime(2020, 11, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "A spin-off reimagining Haman Karn as a modern corporate section chief at an apparel company named Neo Zeon.", "Around 30 OL Haman-sama", null, "アラサーOLハマーン様", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132537/Around_30_OL_Haman-sama", null },
                    { 132845, "Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi won the 69th Shogakukan Manga Award in 2024. The series has been simulpub digitally in English as The Elusive Samurai through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since July 5, 2022. It has also been released in Italian by Panini Comics since October 27, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/247594.jpg", 14749, 6.6m, new DateTime(2021, 1, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Eight-year-old Tokiyuki Houjou, the next successor of the Kamakura shogunate, is a young boy lacking talent in everything besides hide-and-seek. One day, his carefree life is abruptly turned upside down when Takauji Ashikaga brutally seizes power from the Kamakuras, ending their reign. Rescued by a self-proclaimed prophetic priest, Tokiyuki manages to escape with his life. Now he must evade those trying to kill him while recruiting comrades who can help him restore the Kamakura Shogunate to its former glory.\n\nSet during the Nanboku-chou period of Japanese history, Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi is a tale of redemption, documenting the life of the forgotten hero that altered Japan's destiny by running away.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Nige Jouzu no Wakagimi", "The Elusive Samurai", "逃げ上手の若君", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132845/Nige_Jouzu_no_Wakagimi", null },
                    { 132966, "", 13, new DateTime(2020, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/240055.jpg", 26862, null, new DateTime(2019, 1, 31, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A new mission has been assigned to the Orochi subjugation unit, the Yamainu. Could this be—a gag-comedy!?", "Yamainu no Zangyou ni Warau", null, "犲の残業に笑う", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/132966/Yamainu_no_Zangyou_ni_Warau", 1 },
                    { 133004, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/246066.jpg", 26868, null, new DateTime(2019, 5, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The manga features a new heroine named Yuki Hashibami, a magician assassin who is not a magician herself. She challenges Tatsuya in the story.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Shiba Tatsuya Ansatsu Keikaku", "The Irregular at Magic High School: Plan to Assassinate Tatsuya Shiba", "魔法科高校の劣等生 司波達也暗殺計画", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/133004/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Shiba_Tatsuya_Ansatsu_Keikaku", null },
                    { 133005, "Shin Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Cygnus no Otome-tachi began as a web novel on the author's personal website on July 10, 2020. Kadokawa has released a revised and illustrated version of the series since January 9, 2021, under its Dengeki Bunko label.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/246037.jpg", 26869, null, new DateTime(2021, 1, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The series moves away from the Shibas and focuses on Alisa Iba, now Alisa Juumonji, the half-sister of Katsuto Juumonji, who came about due to their father having an affair before remarrying after the death of his first wife.\n\n(Source: Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei Wiki)", "Shin Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Cygnus no Otome-tachi", "Cygnus Maidens: The Irregular at Magic High School", "新・魔法科高校の劣等生 キグナスの乙女たち", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/133005/Shin_Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Cygnus_no_Otome-tachi", null },
                    { 133047, "Jujutsu Kaisen: Yuku Natsu to Kaeru Aki was published in English as Jujutsu Kaisen: Summer of Ashes, Autumn of Dust by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on December 27, 2022.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/244856.jpg", 2148, 7.62m, new DateTime(2019, 4, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Cursed spirits have struck the opening blow at Satozakura High School in an unfolding conflict against the Jujutsu Sorcerers. But while this epic and unyielding battle intensifies, the heroes of Jujutsu Kaisen have other mysteries to solve...such as why Yuji and Megumi see Gojo at a maid cafe, whether Nanami can uncover the secret behind a website that claims to sell dolls that resurrect the dead, and what happens when a blind old man is able to see the scheming Mahito.\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Jujutsu Kaisen: Yuku Natsu to Kaeru Aki", "Jujutsu Kaisen: Summer of Ashes, Autumn of Dust", "呪術廻戦 逝く夏と還る秋", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/133047/Jujutsu_Kaisen__Yuku_Natsu_to_Kaeru_Aki", 1 },
                    { 133048, "Jujutsu Kaisen: Yoake no Ibara Michi was published in English as Jujutsu Kaisen: Thorny Road at Dawn by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on April 25, 2023.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/244857.jpg", 2410, 7.58m, new DateTime(2020, 1, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A talent scout who approaches Kugisaki on a street corner turns out to be a Cursed Speech user with an ulterior motive. When Inumaki comes to her rescue, things don't quite turn out as he planned... Then Mechamaru goes on a solo mission, Gojo and friends take a night off, and more chilling and charming adventures ensue in these five short stories set in the world of Jujutsu Kaisen.\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Jujutsu Kaisen: Yoake no Ibara Michi", "Jujutsu Kaisen: Thorny Road at Dawn", "呪術廻戦 夜明けのいばら道", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/133048/Jujutsu_Kaisen__Yoake_no_Ibara_Michi", 1 },
                    { 133053, "Kimetsu no Yaiba: Kaze no Michishirube was published in English as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Signs from the Wind by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on June 27, 2023. It was also released in Polish by Waneko on December 4, 2023.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/248771.jpg", 3664, 7.41m, new DateTime(2020, 7, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Demon Slayer Masachika kills a demon to save Sanemi's life, and then he takes the younger boy under his wing. Years later, the pair investigates disappearing children and ends up facing off against one of the Twelve Kizuki! In other tales, Kanamori hopes to smooth out Hotaru's rough personality through marriage, Inosuke searches for Kiyo's stolen butterfly clip, Muichiro helps Kotetsu repair the Yoriichi Type Zero, and Rengoku leads a mission to hunt ghosts at Kimetsu Academy!\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Kimetsu no Yaiba: Kaze no Michishirube", "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Signs from the Wind", "鬼滅の刃　風の道しるべ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/133053/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba__Kaze_no_Michishirube", 1 },
                    { 133167, "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu: Hyouketsu no Kizuna was published in English as Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-, The Frozen Bond by Yen Press from May 31, 2022 to March 21, 2023.", 15, new DateTime(2021, 7, 10, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/240385.jpg", 2873, 7.51m, new DateTime(2020, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Deep within the isolated Great Elior Forest, a freezing land covered in snow and ice, lives a girl feared for her resemblance to the legendary Witch of Jealousy. She is the half-elf Emilia, her only company a cat-like spirit named Puck. Both are similarly spurred by duty and guilt, yet the two never grow closer. In this world, the days seem as if they're an unchanging eternity, but the trials awaiting them are merciless like hellfire...\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu: Hyouketsu no Kizuna", "Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-, The Frozen Bond", "Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 氷結の絆", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/133167/Re_Zero_kara_Hajimeru_Isekai_Seikatsu__Hyouketsu_no_Kizuna", 3 },
