                    { 134732, "", 2, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/309554.jpg", 27182, null, new DateTime(2018, 8, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A booklet of side stories distributed to those who watched Nanatsu no Taizai: Tenkuu no Torawarebito in theaters.", "Nanatsu no Taizai: Tenkuu no Torawarebito", null, "七つの大罪 天空の囚われ人", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/134732/Nanatsu_no_Taizai__Tenkuu_no_Torawarebito", 1 },
                    { 134946, "Tensei Kizoku, Kantei Skill de Nariagaru: Jakushou Ryouchi wo Uketsuida node, Yuushuu na Jinzai wo Fuyashiteitara, Saikyou Ryouchi ni Natteta has been published in English by Kodansha USA under the Vertical imprint since March 14, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/242653.jpg", 12273, 6.77m, new DateTime(2020, 7, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "An ordinary salaryman dies one day and is reborn as Ars Louvent, the son of a noble. Although he isn't talented in magic or swordplay, he does have one skill that no one else possesses: Appraisal. Using this ability, Ars can determine a person's current strength, how much potential they hold, and where their talents rest.\n\nThis skill is especially useful in the present situation of the country. The government is corrupt, revolts occur more often than not, and nobles far and wide are strengthening their fortifications in preparation for an all-out war. With this in mind, Ars realizes he too must prepare by gathering talented people.\n\nA persecuted foreigner unparalleled with the sword, a slave with an unknown talent for magic, and a timid boy with an unquenchable thirst for knowledge—such talents lend Ars their support as he aims to create the most powerful territory.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Tensei Kizoku, Kantei Skill de Nariagaru: Jakushou Ryouchi wo Uketsuida node, Yuushuu na Jinzai wo Fuyashiteitara, Saikyou Ryouchi ni Natteta", "As a Reincarnated Aristocrat, I'll Use My Appraisal Skill to Rise in the World", "転生貴族、鑑定スキルで成り上がる～弱小領地を受け継いだので、優秀な人材を増やしていたら、最強領地になってた～", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/134946/Tensei_Kizoku_Kantei_Skill_de_Nariagaru__Jakushou_Ryouchi_wo_Uketsuida_node_Yuushuu_na_Jinzai_wo_Fuyashiteitara_Saikyou_Ryouchi_ni_Natteta", null },
                    { 135181, "", 14, new DateTime(2018, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/246206.jpg", 27237, null, new DateTime(2017, 10, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The prequel manga is based on the \"Sengo no Sensou\" (The Postwar War) short story that appears in the 11th volume of Harutoshi Fukui's original Mobile Suit Gundam UC novels. The story centers on the Neo Zeon remnants' hijacking of the Sinanju Stein mobile suit.\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam Unicorn: Bande Dessinee - Episode:0", null, "機動戦士ガンダムUC バンデシネ Episode:0", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135181/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_Unicorn__Bande_Dessinee_-_Episode_0", 3 },
                    { 135242, "", 6, new DateTime(2019, 8, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/242940.jpg", 27247, null, new DateTime(2019, 4, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Frederica Hanashiro from the Ministry of Foreign Affairs visits the Public Safety Bureau with the intent to make an offer to Teppei Sugou, one of the current Division 01 Enforcers. Since Sugou was once an ace pilot in the National Defense Army, Frederica gives him the opportunity to clear his status as a latent criminal and rejoin the military.\n\nAs he considers the offer, Sugou recalls his days in the army. While carrying out a mission, Sugou's First Guardian drone was ordered to drop supplies and abandon a ground unit—including his commanding officer, Itsuki Ootomo. All of the members in the group were proclaimed missing, but it was evident that they marched to their deaths.\n\nHowever, three months later, during a massacre at the Ministry of Defense, the security cameras caught none other than Ootomo at the scene. Now considered a suspect in aiding a terrorist attack, Sugou works together with Inspector Risa Aoyanagi and Enforcer Tomomi Masaoka to get to the bottom of the case.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Psycho-Pass: Sinners of the System Case.2 - First Guardian", null, "PSYCHO-PASS サイコパス Sinners of the System 「Case.2 First Guardian」", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135242/Psycho-Pass__Sinners_of_the_System_Case2_-_First_Guardian", 1 },
                    { 135262, null, null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/243510.jpg", 27249, null, new DateTime(2014, 4, 27, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, null, "Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei: Yonkoma-hen", null, "魔法科高校の劣等生 よんこま編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135262/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Rettousei__Yonkoma-hen", null },
                    { 135455, "Shikanoko Nokonoko Koshitantan has been published in English as My Deer Friend Nokotan by Seven Seas Entertainment since March 15, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/243191.jpg", 3347, 7.44m, new DateTime(2019, 11, 14, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "No one knows Torako used to be a delinquent. All of her classmates only know her as the perfect student. But everything changes when Nokotan, a transfer student with antlers, enters her life. Antlers aren't the only thing strange about Nokotan. Her deer nose can sniff out Torako's secret past! Whether it's at school or the zoo, chaos follows this doe-eyed girl's every step. Torako has so many questions! Is Nokotan a deer, a girl, or something in-between?\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Shikanoko Nokonoko Koshitantan", "My Deer Friend Nokotan", "しかのこのこのここしたんたん", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135455/Shikanoko_Nokonoko_Koshitantan", null },
                    { 135496, "Dandadan ranked fourth in the 2022 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division. The manga was nominated for the 15th Manga Taisho Award in 2022 and ranked seventh in the final ranking. The series has been simulpub digitally in English through MANGA Plus. The volumes have been published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since October 11, 2022. It has also been released in Italian by J-POP since September 21, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/248746.jpg", 222, 8.39m, new DateTime(2021, 4, 5, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After being aggressively rejected, Momo Ayase finds herself sulking when she stumbles across a boy being bullied. Saved by her rash kindness, the occult-obsessed boy attempts to speak to her about supernatural interests he believes they share. Rejecting his claims, Ayase proclaimed that she instead is a believer in ghosts, starting an argument between the two over which is real.\n\nIn a bet to determine who is correct, the two decide to separately visit locations associated with both the occult and the supernatural—Ayase visiting the former and the boy visiting the latter. When the two reach their respective places, it turns out that neither was wrong and that both the occult and ghosts do exist.\n\nThis marks the beginning of Ayase and the boy's adventure, as they attempt to fix the surreal, supernatural, and occult elements around them to return to a normal life.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Dandadan", "Dandadan", "ダンダダン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135496/Dandadan", null },
                    { 135545, "Ao no Hako is published digitally as an English simulpub as Blue Box through MANGA Plus service. The volumes have been published by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint since November 1, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/248748.jpg", 477, 8.16m, new DateTime(2021, 4, 11, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Taiki Inomata, a third-year student in junior high, attends Eimei Academy, an integrated school with a major sports program. Having joined the high school badminton team, Taiki tries to attend open practice as early as possible. But no matter how early he goes, he always arrives second in the gymnasium. The person one step ahead of him is Chinatsu Kano, a first-year student in senior high and Taiki's crush.\n\nChinatsu is the rising star of the basketball team, and the gap between her and Taiki could not be greater. Although Taiki is a decent badminton player, his popularity is nowhere near Chinatsu's, making it even less likely for his feelings to be reciprocated. However, in a strange twist of fate, she ends up living in Taiki's house!\n\nWanting to become a worthy match for Chinatsu, Taiki pursues the same dream as his crush: to partake in the Nationals. Taiki starts training harder than ever before, all for the sake of building a strong relationship with his new housemate.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Ao no Hako", "Blue Box", "アオのハコ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135545/Ao_no_Hako", null },
                    { 135567, "", 32, new DateTime(2024, 2, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/249233.jpg", 6172, 7.18m, new DateTime(2021, 4, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Nagasaki prefecture, in Japan, is a magical kingdom. While the wizards that live there are unable to cross the ocean, and are trapped in Kyuushu, they still pose enough of a threat that Americans dropped the bomb on them during WWII. The residents are worried that this will happen again, especially if the regular humans decide magicians are a threat.\n\nDaughter of the most powerful wizard alive, Mizukura Risuka is ten years old, and living outside Nagasaki, searching for her father and killing evil wizards. Her blood contains spells that control time, and allow her to fast-forward her own life. Her ultimate technique kicks in only when she dies bloodily—her blood will reform into herself at 27, at the height of her powers, for one minute.\n\nHer guide through the world of normal humans is Kugi Kizutaka, also aged ten. Kizutaka is a genius, and a sociopath. He believes the only way for people to be happy is to be ruled by him and views everyone he meets as a potential pawn, or slave. Including Risuka.\n\n(Source: easternstandard.pbworks.com)", "Shin Honkaku Mahou Shoujo Risuka", null, "新本格魔法少女りすか", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135567/Shin_Honkaku_Mahou_Shoujo_Risuka", 7 },
