                    { 135743, null, null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/261711.jpg", 27322, null, new DateTime(2021, 2, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, null, "Mahouka Koukou no Yuutousei: 2nd Season", null, "魔法科高校の優等生 2nd Season", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135743/Mahouka_Koukou_no_Yuutousei__2nd_Season", null },
                    { 135893, "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Ougonritsu no Canon was published in English as Sword Art Online Progressive Canon of the Golden Rule by Yen Press from March 19, 2024 to July 30, 2024.", 10, new DateTime(2022, 4, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/253327.jpg", 7572, 7.08m, new DateTime(2021, 3, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Asuna and Kirito have made it to Aincrad's sixth floor, where in the town of Stachion they find something very odd—puzzles everywhere they look. New mysteries and complex riddles await, many of which can't be solved with a sword... Fighting against the odds, the two will have to put their heads together if they want to make it out alive. But as they focus their attention on confronting the challenges ahead, will they be ready for the sinister forces that lie in wait?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online: Progressive - Ougonritsu no Canon", "Sword Art Online Progressive Canon of the Golden Rule", "ソードアート・オンライン プログレッシブ 黄金律のカノン", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/135893/Sword_Art_Online__Progressive_-_Ougonritsu_no_Canon", 2 },
                    { 136106, "", null, new DateTime(2017, 1, 30, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/271166.jpg", 27372, null, new DateTime(2015, 3, 5, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Psycho-Pass Genesis tells the secret story of the creation of Sibyl System through an incident in which the young Tomomi Masaoka was involved.", "Psycho-Pass Genesis", null, "PSYCHO-PASS GENESIS", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/136106/Psycho-Pass_Genesis", 4 },
                    { 136660, "Spy x Family: Kazoku no Shouzou was published in English as Spy x Family: Family Portrait by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on December 26, 2023.", 5, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/248768.jpg", 963, 7.91m, new DateTime(2021, 7, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In this book of Spy x Family original prose stories, Anya attempts to make friends with her target Damian during an Eden Academy camping trip, Yuri spends his day off babysitting his niece, and Franky seeks Loid's help in winning the heart of a blind opera singer. Then, when the family sits for a portrait painting, Yor is terrified that her secret identity will be blown. And in the final story, the family is scrutinized by a pair of unseen observers... There's never been a family quite like this one!\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Spy x Family: Kazoku no Shouzou", "Spy x Family: Family Portrait", "SPY×FAMILY 家族の肖像", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/136660/Spy_x_Family__Kazoku_no_Shouzou", 1 },
                    { 136856, "Gimai Seikatsu has been published in English as Days with My Stepsister by Yen Press since October 22, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/259020.jpg", 4466, 7.33m, new DateTime(2021, 7, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After his father's remarriage, Yuuta Asamura ends up getting a new stepsister, coincidentally the number one beauty of the school year, Saki Ayase. Having learned important values when it comes to relationships between men and women through the previous ones of their parents, they promise each other not to be too close, not to be too opposing, and to merely keep a vague and comfortable distance.\n\nOn one hand, Saki, who has worked in solitude for the sake of her family, doesn't know how to properly rely on others, whereas Yuuta is unsure of how to really treat her. Standing on fairly equal ground, these two slowly learn the comfortable sensation of living together.\n\nTheir relationship slowly evolves from being strangers the more the days pass. This is a story that may lead to love someday.\n\n(Source: Kadokawa, translated)", "Gimai Seikatsu", "Days with My Stepsister", "義妹生活", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/136856/Gimai_Seikatsu", null },
                    { 137242, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/266837.jpg", 12177, 6.78m, new DateTime(2021, 2, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A short promotional one-shot for the light novel of the same title.", "Tokidoki Bosotto Russia-go de Dereru Tonari no Alya-san", null, "時々ボソッとロシア語でデレる隣のアーリャさん", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/137242/Tokidoki_Bosotto_Russia-go_de_Dereru_Tonari_no_Alya-san", null },
                    { 137358, null, 7, new DateTime(2013, 7, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/282229.jpg", 27517, null, new DateTime(2013, 2, 8, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, null, "Kidou Senshi Gundam Unicorn: Niji ni Norenakatta Otoko", "Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn: Bright Noah Story", "機動戦士ガンダムUC〈ユニコーン〉 虹にのれなかった男", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/137358/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_Unicorn__Niji_ni_Norenakatta_Otoko", 1 },
                    { 137939, "Chi.: Chikyuu no Undou ni Tsuite won the Grand Prize at the 26th Tezuka Osamu Cultural Prize awards in 2022. In the same year, it was nominated for the 15th Manga Taisho Award and the 46th Kodansha Manga Awards in the General category. It ranked second in the 2022 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers Division. In 2023, the manga won Best Comic at the 54th Seiun Awards. The series has been published in English as Orb: On the Movements of the Earth by Seven Seas Entertainment as 2-in-1 omnibus volumes since November 21, 2023. It was also released in Italian by Dynit as Il Movimento della Terra from January 20, 2023, to March 22, 2024.", 62, new DateTime(2022, 4, 17, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/246956.jpg", 1046, 7.87m, new DateTime(2020, 9, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In fifteenth-century Europe, heretics are being burned at the stake. Rafal, a brilliant young man, is expected to enter university at an early age and study the era's most important field, theology. But Rafal values Reason above all else, which leads him both to the shocking conclusion that the Earth orbits the Sun, and into the hands of the Inquisition!\n\nA decade later, two members of the Watch Guild, the dour young Oczy and the cynical Gras, find a hidden stone chest that details the secrets of the universe Rafal left behind. Dare they try to change their own stars by selling the heretical texts, or would that only lead to the stake and the fire?\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Chi.: Chikyuu no Undou ni Tsuite", "Orb: On the Movements of the Earth", "チ。―地球の運動について―", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/137939/Chi__Chikyuu_no_Undou_ni_Tsuite", 8 },
                    { 137967, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/268109.jpg", 9705, 6.94m, new DateTime(2021, 6, 11, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A prequel manga that takes place 120 minutes before Evangelion: 3.0 You Can (Not) Redo which was included in Eva-Extra-Extra, a booklet distributed at the theatrical release of Evangelion: 3.0+1.01 Thrice Upon a Time.", "Evangelion: 3.0 (-120min.)", null, "EVANGELION: 3.0 (-120min.)", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/137967/Evangelion__30_-120min", null },
                    { 137982, "Senpai wa Otokonoko is based on the web manga Otokonoko ga Kouhai ni Kokuhaku sareru Hanashi (おとこのこが後輩に告白される話), released on the author's Twitter and pixiv accounts from July 3, 2019, to July 24, 2019. The series was published digitally in English as Senpai Is an Otokonoko by Webtoon Entertainment from March 9, 2023, to February 8, 2024. Webtoon Entertainment also released the series in French from March 28, 2022, to February 5, 2024; and in German since May 28, 2022.", 100, new DateTime(2021, 12, 29, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/252739.jpg", 1254, 7.81m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 6, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Makoto Hanaoka, a womanly second-year student, easily attracts other people's attention. First-year student Saki Aoi is no exception, and she falls in love with Makoto at first sight. Having a vibrant and vigorous personality, she does not hesitate to confess her feelings to her senior. However, Makoto differs significantly from the person Saki perceives: Makoto is not a girl, but rather a cross-dressing boy!\n\nAfter revealing his well-known secret to Saki, Makoto expects her to be disgusted. Surprisingly, she is instead captivated by this revelation. Nonetheless, he still rejects her, but Saki's determination does not stop her from declaring that she will become his first love. With Saki and his childhood friend at his side, Makoto's world brightens, giving him strength amid his struggle between his interests and the expectations placed on him.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Senpai wa Otokonoko", "Senpai Is an Otokonoko: My Crossdressing Classmate", "先輩はおとこのこ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/137982/Senpai_wa_Otokonoko", null },
                    { 138078, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/254428.jpg", 11822, 6.8m, new DateTime(2020, 8, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A side story focusing on Lancelot, Ban and Elaine's son.", "Nanatsu no Taizai: Hajimari wo Sasou Ame no Mori", null, "七つの大罪 はじまりを誘う雨の森", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/138078/Nanatsu_no_Taizai__Hajimari_wo_Sasou_Ame_no_Mori", null },
                    { 138269, "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle - Episode Freya was published in English as Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Familia Chronicle: Episode Freya by Yen Press under its Yen On imprint on October 27, 2020.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/263264.jpg", 5876, 7.21m, new DateTime(2019, 12, 11, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The search for love is on!\n\nA fey mood strikes Freya, sparking a new quest to find her Odr, the one destined to stand forever by her side. Naturally, her followers are against it. They remember all too well the disaster that her last adventure turned out to be. Unfortunately for them, such a minor setback has never been enough to stop the goddess of beauty from following wherever her heart leads-which, this time, happens to be the sandy dunes of Kaios. Freya is eager to spread her wings to see what discoveries this new land has to offer, even as her familia frantically searches for her, no matter the cost...!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle - Episode Freya", "Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Familia Chronicle: Episode Freya", "ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうか ファミリアクロニクル episodeフレイヤ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/138269/Dungeon_ni_Deai_wo_Motomeru_no_wa_Machigatteiru_Darou_ka__Familia_Chronicle_-_Episode_Freya", 1 },
                    { 138481, "Make Heroine ga Oosugiru! won the Gagaga Award at the 15th Shogakukan Light Novel Award in 2021 under the title Ore wa Hyottoshite, Saishuuwa de Make Heroine no Yokoni Iru Pottode no Mob Chara nano Darou ka (俺はひょっとして、最終話で負けヒロインの横にいるポッと出のモブキャラなのだろうか). The series has been published in English as Too Many Losing Heroines! by Seven Seas Entertainment under the Airship imprint since August 13, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/248592.jpg", 466, 8.17m, new DateTime(2021, 7, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Plain, boring, and friendless Kazuhiko Nukumizu has witnessed something completely baffling: popular girl Anna Yanami was friend-zoned by her childhood friend and crush! In fact, all the popular girls around him are getting similarly rejected by the boys they like. Without realizing it, Kazuhiko becomes entangled in the relationship drama where all the leading heroines are losing out on love! Can he keep their spirits up and help them find happiness?\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Make Heroine ga Oosugiru!", "Too Many Losing Heroines!", "負けヒロインが多すぎる！", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/138481/Make_Heroine_ga_Oosugiru", null },
                    { 138915, "Maou 2099 won the Grand Prize at the 33rd Fantasia Award in 2020 under the title Ken to Maou no Cyberpunk (剣と魔王のサイバーパンク). The series has been published in English as Demon Lord 2099 by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since March 15, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/248745.jpg", 33999, null, new DateTime(2021, 1, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "​The cyberpunk metropolis Shinjuku—a massive city-state bedecked with neon signs, towering skyscrapers, and the latest cutting-edge technology. It is here, in year 2099 of the Fused Era, where the legendary Demon Lord Veltol has his second coming five centuries in the making. But this landscape is nothing like the one he conquered all those years ago, for the fusion of magic and engineering has elevated civilization to dazzling, unprecedented heights. Veltol may have been reduced to a historical footnote, but make no mistake...this brave new world will be his for the taking!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Maou 2099", "Demon Lord 2099", "魔王2099", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/138915/Maou_2099", null },
                    { 139018, "An English translation of Kidou Senshi Gundam SEED Eclipse has been streamed as a motion comic on the GUNDAM.INFO YouTube channel since July 26, 2021.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/256392.jpg", 27790, null, new DateTime(2021, 7, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "C.E.72 was a unique era which would later be called the \"two blank years.\" Some also call it \"the time of peace on thin ice,\" and others call it \"the break before the oncoming frenzy.\" This is the story of an interval. A story that takes place between two large wars in which members of a hollow unit known as ODR risked their lives.\n\n(Source: GUNDAM.INFO)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam SEED Eclipse", "Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Eclipse", "機動戦士ガンダムSEED ECLIPSE", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139018/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_SEED_Eclipse", null },
                    { 139066, "", 13, new DateTime(2020, 8, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/256632.jpg", 34031, null, new DateTime(2018, 8, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The era of e-sports has arrived, where anyone can compete and enjoy gaming tournaments! Kenzou, a gamer who loves the fighting game Dragon Ball FighterZ, enters the e-sport world and is prepared to challenge everyone with only his intuition and fists!\n\n(Source: Shueisha, translated)", "DeSpo FighterZ", null, "DeスポファイターZ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139066/DeSpo_FighterZ", 2 },
                    { 139152, "Bleach: Gokui Meimei-hen was published digitally in English as Bleach: Special One-shot through MANGA Plus.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/252464.jpg", 1106, 7.85m, new DateTime(2021, 8, 9, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Over a decade after the Thousand-Year Blood War, Ichigo Kurosaki lives a peaceful life with his wife Orihime Inoue and their son Kazui. Utilizing the fledgling Soul Reaper powers inherited from his father, Kazui assists those burdened by the deceased much like Ichigo did as a teenager.\n\nOne day, Ichigo receives an unexpected call from his married Soul Reaper allies Renji Abarai and Rukia Kuchiki. The couple invites him to take part in the \"Konso Reisai\"—a ceremony in which a Hollow, an evil spirit from the human world, is sacrificed to honor a Soul Reaper captain who died exactly 12 years prior.\n\nUnbeknownst to Ichigo and his friends, something sinister looms over the Konso Reisai. As Renji meets up with Ichigo to honor the dead, the two are interrupted by the return of an old enemy they never thought they'd meet again.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Bleach: Gokui Meimei-hen", "Bleach: Special One-shot", "BLEACH 獄頤鳴鳴〈ごくいめいめい〉篇", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139152/Bleach__Gokui_Meimei-hen", null },
                    { 139629, "JoJo no Kimyou na Bouken Part 9: The JoJoLands ranked 15th in the 2024 Kono Manga ga Sugoi! for the Male Readers division.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/286969.jpg", 268, 8.34m, new DateTime(2023, 2, 16, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "On the Hawaiian Islands, siblings Dragona and Jodio Joestar commit petty crimes to provide aid for their ailing mother Barbara Ann. Under the orders of Meryl May Qi, both a crime lord and their high school principal, the siblings work alongside fellow teenagers Usagi Alohaoe and Paco Laburantes. Together, the gang engages in outright robbery, fraudulent activity, and other schemes to rip off unsuspecting tourists and civilians.\n\nFifteen-year-old Jodio admires his older brother's strong sense of identity and his mother's incredible work ethic, but there is a darkness within him, one characterized by violent outbursts that he carries out with a cold stoicism. Diagnosed as a sociopath, Jodio is quick to brutalize those who threaten his loved ones. His one objective is to make money by any means necessary, both to support his family and to become filthy rich in his own right.\n\nOn one particular heist, the gang robs manga artist Rohan Kishibe of a seemingly ordinary lava rock. However, they soon find that the rock draws any object of high value that it touches to its wielder, no matter the distance or bizarre chain of circumstances it takes to get there. With this new power in hand, Jodio and his allies set out to become wealthier than they ever dreamed possible.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "JoJo no Kimyou na Bouken Part 9: The JoJoLands", "JoJo's Bizarre Adventure Part 9: The JoJoLands", "ジョジョの奇妙な冒険 Part9 The JOJOLands", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139629/JoJo_no_Kimyou_na_Bouken_Part_9__The_JoJoLands", null },
                    { 139665, "Magia Record: Mahou Shoujo Madoka☆Magica Gaiden - Another Story has been published in English as Magia Record: Puella Magi Madoka Magica Another Story by Yen Press since September 6, 2022.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/249364.jpg", 27878, null, new DateTime(2019, 3, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "With fewer witches cropping up in Mitakihara and the surrounding area, many magical girls are embracing their chance to enjoy a break from the hunt—but not Mami Tomoe! Mami wants to know why witch numbers are declining in every city save one. In Kamihama City, the witch population is greater and stronger than ever, not to mention there's a mysterious magical presence unlike anything Mami has encountered before...!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Magia Record: Mahou Shoujo Madoka☆Magica Gaiden - Another Story", "Magia Record: Puella Magi Madoka Magica Another Story", "マギアレコード 魔法少女まどか☆マギカ外伝 アナザーストーリー", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139665/Magia_Record__Mahou_Shoujo_Madoka☆Magica_Gaiden_-_Another_Story", null },
                    { 139761, "Ore wa Subete wo \"Parry\" suru: Gyaku Kanchigai no Sekai Saikyou wa Boukensha no Yume wo Miru has been published digitally in English as I Parry Everything: What Do You Mean I'm the Strongest? I'm Not Even an Adventurer Yet! by J-Novel Club since March 29, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/249442.jpg", 15971, 6.51m, new DateTime(2020, 9, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Ever since he was a young boy, Noor has wanted to be like the adventurers in his father's stories—dragon-slayers, curse-breakers, heroes who always save the day. But as everyone knows, to be an adventurer, you've gotta have the right skills! Unfortunately for Noor, his \"Parry\" is bottom-of-the-barrel useless, his prospects are nonexistent, and everybody he knows is telling him to throw in the towel. Faced with this harsh reality, he figures there's only one thing to do: make up for it with effort! An intense, solitary training regimen ought to do it. If one year won't cut it, he'll train for five! If not five, ten! Now facing the tail end of his twenties with no new skills to show for his labors, Noor sets out to become an adventurer anyway, determined to try one last time to make his dream come true. He might be clueless when it comes to adventuring, but he's no stranger to hard work! Now, if only he can figure out why everyone keeps looking at him like that...\n\n(Source: J-Novel Club)", "Ore wa Subete wo \"Parry\" suru: Gyaku Kanchigai no Sekai Saikyou wa Boukensha no Yume wo Miru", "I Parry Everything: What Do You Mean I'm the Strongest? I'm Not Even an Adventurer Yet!", "俺は全てを【パリイ】する～逆勘違いの世界最強は冒険者の夢をみる～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139761/Ore_wa_Subete_wo_Parry_suru__Gyaku_Kanchigai_no_Sekai_Saikyou_wa_Boukensha_no_Yume_wo_Miru", null },
                    { 139972, "One Piece: Vivi no Bouken is part of the One Piece Comic Cover Project. The one-shot was simulpub in English as One Piece: Vivi's Adventure through MANGA Plus service.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/249763.jpg", 4059, 7.37m, new DateTime(2021, 8, 29, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A remake of chapter 216 of One Piece, drawn by Naoshi Komi.", "One Piece: Vivi no Bouken", "One Piece: Vivi's Adventure", "ONE PIECE ビビの冒険", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/139972/One_Piece__Vivi_no_Bouken", null },
                    { 140150, "Chainsaw Man: Buddy Stories was published in English by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on July 25, 2023.", 4, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/252140.jpg", 1292, 7.8m, new DateTime(2021, 11, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Power lives out her favorite anime by becoming a genius detective—or so she wants her \"audience\" to believe! Denji is along for the ride as her assistant for an investigation into disappearances at a mountain hotel. Other stories center on Quanxi and Kishibe's relationship nine years after they met, Himeno and Aki's first assignment together, and Denji, Power, and Aki's dream trip to Enoshima.\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Chainsaw Man: Buddy Stories", "Chainsaw Man: Buddy Stories", "チェンソーマン　バディ・ストーリーズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/140150/Chainsaw_Man__Buddy_Stories", 1 },
