                    { 141953, "Sword Art Online Re:Aincrad has been published in English by Yen Press since May 21, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/259042.jpg", 34411, null, new DateTime(2021, 10, 26, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Die in the game, and you die in real life. This is Sword Art Online, the latest VRMMORPG, and upon the game's launch, ten thousand players realize they're trapped in this virtual world with no escape...unless they can make their way through Aincrad, a massive floating castle with dangers lurking on each of its one hundred floors. Enter Kirito, a swordsman and former beta tester for the game who has the knowledge and skills to rise to the top, and the rapier-wielding Asuna, whose fated meeting with Kirito will change their lives forever. Join these two warriors on their journey to freedom in this expanded retelling of the original Aincrad arc!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Sword Art Online Re:Aincrad", "Sword Art Online Re:Aincrad", "ソードアート・オンライン Re:Aincrad", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/141953/Sword_Art_Online_Re_Aincrad", null },
                    { 141959, "Fullmetal Alchemist 4-koma was published in English as Fullmetal Alchemist: The Complete Four-Panel Comics by VIZ Media on March 12, 2019.", 4, new DateTime(2014, 10, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/311662.jpg", 31130, null, new DateTime(2002, 1, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "This complete collection offers the beloved four-panel comic strips from the graphic novel series and bonus strips from the anime DVDs of Fullmetal Alchemist and Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood, as well as rare strips from Japan! \n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Fullmetal Alchemist 4-koma", "Fullmetal Alchemist: The Complete Four-Panel Comics", "鋼の錬金術師4コマ", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/141959/Fullmetal_Alchemist_4-koma", 1 },
                    { 142246, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/263020.jpg", 964, 7.91m, new DateTime(2021, 12, 24, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Students of the prestigious Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School are given remarkable freedom—if they can win, barter, or save enough points to work their way up the ranks! Kiyotaka Ayanokouji started at the bottom in the scorned Class D, where he met Suzune Horikita, who was determined to rise up the ladder to Class A. Who can beat the system in a school where cutthroat competition is the name of the game? The second year of this intense school drama begins now!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Youkoso Jitsuryoku Shijou Shugi no Kyoushitsu e: 2-nensei-hen", "Welcome to the Classroom of the Second-year", "ようこそ実力至上主義の教室へ ２年生編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142246/Youkoso_Jitsuryoku_Shijou_Shugi_no_Kyoushitsu_e__2-nensei-hen", null },
                    { 142475, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/270960.jpg", 28239, null, new DateTime(2017, 7, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Kishibe Rohan Tanpen Shousetsushuu is an anthology of short stories written by various authors and based on the Kishibe Rohan wa Ugokanai series.", "Kishibe Rohan Tanpen Shousetsushuu", null, "岸辺露伴 短編小説集", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142475/Kishibe_Rohan_Tanpen_Shousetsushuu", null },
                    { 142551, "", 16, new DateTime(2023, 5, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/5/261865.jpg", 2580, 7.55m, new DateTime(2021, 12, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Hol Horse accepts a request from an elderly woman to find her lost parrot, who was trained by the owner of Pet Shop, he finds himself trekking across half the globe to the Japanese city of Morioh.\n\nIn Morioh, Hol Horse quickly runs into Josuke Higashikata. Will the two become friends or foes? Then, what new enemy with grotesque stand powers lurks in Morioh? And will Hol Horse and Dio's other former followers ever truly be free from his influence?\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "JoJo no Kimyou na Bouken: Crazy Diamond no Akuryou-teki Shitsuren", "JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Shining Diamond's Demonic Heartbreak", "ジョジョの奇妙な冒険 クレイジー・D〈ダイヤモンド〉の悪霊的失恋", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142551/JoJo_no_Kimyou_na_Bouken__Crazy_Diamond_no_Akuryou-teki_Shitsuren", 3 },
                    { 142552, "", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/253442.jpg", 19043, 6.05m, new DateTime(2021, 12, 17, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "On an otherwise ordinary day in Green Dolphin Street Prison, Jolyne Kuujou—alongside Hermes Costello and Foo Fighters—witnesses a female prisoner kneeling before another, begging to draw something for her. The woman seems delirious; she claims that she cannot sleep without the drawing and that not having it causes her to pull her own hair out.\n\nThe artist, a woman named Fujiko, soon approaches Jolyne and offers to draw her in a shunga piece—a type of erotic artwork. Though disinterested in the offer, Jolyne is enamored by Fujiko's non-erotic sketch of her and decides to buy it.\n\nWhat Jolyne does not realize, however, is that Fujiko is a Stand user employed by Whitesnake to retrieve Joutarou Kuujou's \"disc\" from his daughter. When Jolyne begins experiencing a strange sensation, she is none the wiser as to what—or who—caused it.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Fujiko no Kimyou na Shoseijutsu: Whitesnake no Gosan", null, "フジコの奇妙な処世術 -ホワイトスネイクの誤算-", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142552/Fujiko_no_Kimyou_na_Shoseijutsu__Whitesnake_no_Gosan", null },
                    { 142617, "", 15, new DateTime(1985, 4, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/253563.jpg", 28257, null, new DateTime(1970, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "A collection of previously uncompiled chapters of Lupin III, Shin Lupin III, and the 5-part Sexy Lupin III series.", "Lupin III: Tankoubon Mishuuroku Sakuhinshuu", null, "ルパン三世 単行本未収録作品集", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142617/Lupin_III__Tankoubon_Mishuuroku_Sakuhinshuu", 1 },
                    { 142765, "Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu - Shitsui no Majutsushi-hen adapts the seventh volume of the original light novel.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/266702.jpg", 969, 7.9m, new DateTime(2021, 12, 19, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "After separating from Eris, Rudeus falls into the depths of depression. He travels to Rozenberg, the second city of the Principality of Basherant, to search for his missing mother, Zenith. Desperate, Rudeus tries to accept a high-ranking quest alone in order to make a name for himself. However, by chance, he ends up working with a party of B-rank adventurers called the Counter Arrow. One of the party members is a girl named Sara, who reminds him of Eris...!\n\n(Source: Frontier Works, translated)", "Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu - Shitsui no Majutsushi-hen", null, "無職転生 ～異世界行ったら本気だす～ 失意の魔術師編", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142765/Mushoku_Tensei__Isekai_Ittara_Honki_Dasu_-_Shitsui_no_Majutsushi-hen", null },
                    { 142771, "", 12, new DateTime(2020, 4, 1, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/253803.jpg", 28276, null, new DateTime(2018, 5, 31, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The manga's story centers on Chinpy, a boy who aspires to take up after Luffy, the protagonist of Eiichiro Oda's One Piece manga. Like Luffy, he is able to elongate \"a certain part\" of his body to fight.\n\n(Source: ANN)", "Chin Piece", null, "CHIN PIECE", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142771/Chin_Piece", 2 },
                    { 142772, "Fischer's x One Piece: Nanatsunagi no Daihihou is simultaneously published in Saikyou Jump and broadcast in video form on the official Saikyou Jump YouTube channel.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/253804.jpg", 28277, null, new DateTime(2018, 8, 2, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The members of the YouTuber group Fischer's are transported to the world of One Piece.", "Fischer's x One Piece: Nanatsunagi no Daihihou", null, "Fischer's×ONE PIECE 7つなぎの大秘宝", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142772/Fischers_x_One_Piece__Nanatsunagi_no_Daihihou", null },
                    { 142916, "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Memoria Freese - Seiya no Träumerei is an adaptation of a mobile game, titled DanMachi - Memoria Freese. It was released on June 19, 2017 for Android and iOS. The series has been published in English as Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Memoria Freese: Holy Night Traumerei by Yen Press since June 20, 2023.", 22, new DateTime(2023, 10, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/253985.jpg", 37500, null, new DateTime(2021, 10, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "The Holy Night Festival has arrived, and Bell the rest of Hestia Familia have worked hard to afford a lovely dress for their goddess to wear during the festivities, so there's only one thing left to do—celebrate! Their merriment is soon interrupted, however, by a mysterious girl from a foreign land, and it's up to Bell to help the girl evade her would-be captors! But his new friend isn't content to simply escape—she wants to enjoy the festival just like everyone else! Just who is this young lady, and why has she made the long journey to Orario...?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Memoria Freese - Seiya no Träumerei", "Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Memoria Freese: Holy Night Traumerei", "ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうか ～メモリア・フレーゼ～ 聖夜の夢想歌〈トロイメライ〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/142916/Dungeon_ni_Deai_wo_Motomeru_no_wa_Machigatteiru_Darou_ka__Memoria_Freese_-_Seiya_no_Träumerei", 4 },
                    { 143426, "", 4, new DateTime(2022, 6, 23, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/254718.jpg", 34657, null, new DateTime(2021, 11, 4, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 1, "The cyberpunk metropolis Shinjuku—a massive city-state bedecked with neon signs, towering skyscrapers, and the latest cutting-edge technology. It is here, in year 2099 of the Fused Era, where the legendary Demon Lord Veltol has his second coming five centuries in the making. But this landscape is nothing like the one he conquered all those years ago, for the fusion of magic and engineering has elevated civilization to dazzling, unprecedented heights. Veltol may have been reduced to a historical footnote, but make no mistake...this brave new world will be his for the taking!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Maou 2099", null, "魔王2099", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/143426/Maou_2099", null },
                    { 143881, "", 54, new DateTime(2024, 3, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/269102.jpg", 28500, null, new DateTime(2019, 6, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In Universal Century 0112, there was the Fastest Formula. They wielded the ultimate, general-purpose weapon: the F90. Seven years following the Mufti Uprising, in the surging wave of mobile suit miniaturization, there was a team operating behind the scenes. These are the records of its various operations.\n\n(Source: Zeonic Scanlations)", "Kidou Senshi Gundam F90 FF", "Mobile Suit Gundam F90: Fastest Formula", "機動戦士ガンダムF90FF 〈ファステストフォーミュラ〉", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/143881/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_F90_FF", 11 },
                    { 143972, "Rengoku Zero-wa, a.k.a. Kimetsu no Yaiba: Tokubetsu Yomikiri, was originally published in the Weekly Shounen Jump 2020 #44 issue on October 5, 2020. Later included in the Kimetsu no Yaiba Rengoku Zero-kan booklet given to people who viewed Kimetsu no Yaiba Movie: Mugen Ressha-hen in Japanese theaters, with only 4.5 Million Copies given out. The one-shot was published digitally in English as Kimetsu no Yaiba: Special One-shot through MANGA Plus. The second volume was published in English as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Corps Records by VIZ Media under the Shonen Jump imprint on September 26, 2023. Chuukou Ikkan!! Kimetsu Gakuen Monogatari was also published in that volume by VIZ Media as Junior High and High School!! Kimetsu Academy Story.", 6, new DateTime(2021, 2, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/285561.jpg", 6819, 7.13m, new DateTime(2018, 1, 25, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Volume 1\n1. Chuukou Ikkan!! Kimetsu Gakuen Monogatari (Junior High and High School!! Kimetsu Academy Story)\n\nVolume 2\n1. Jigoku no Oni Shuzai: Sanzu no Kawa wo Koete (Interview with the Demons in Hell: Crossing the River to the Underworld)\n2. Rengoku Zero-wa (Rengoku Chapter 0)\n3. Tanjirou no Kinkyou Houkokusho (An Update from Tanjiro)\n4. Micchaku! \"Kimetsu Gakuen\" ni Kayou Tanjirou no 1-nichi (New-Year Bonus Manga)\n5. Kimetsu no Dodai (Kimetsu: Behind the Scenes)", "Kimetsu no Yaiba Koushiki Fanbook: Kisatsutai Kenbunroku", "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Corps Records", "鬼滅の刃公式ファンブック 鬼殺隊見聞録", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/143972/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_Koushiki_Fanbook__Kisatsutai_Kenbunroku", null },
