                    { 144387, "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo!: Fantastic Days is an adaptation of Sumzap's mobile game released on February 27, 2020. The light novel was published in English as Konosuba: God's Blessing on This Wonderful World! Fantastic Days by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint on July 18, 2023.", 9, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/262139.jpg", 9921, 6.93m, new DateTime(2022, 2, 28, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Follow Kazuma and his party as they help a team of aspiring dancers, fight a former general of the Demon King, and more in a series of adventures based on the Fantastic Days game, along with new, unique content!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Kono Subarashii Sekai ni Shukufuku wo!: Fantastic Days", "Konosuba: God's Blessing on This Wonderful World! Fantastic Days", "この素晴らしい世界に祝福を! ファンタスティックデイズ", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/144387/Kono_Subarashii_Sekai_ni_Shukufuku_wo__Fantastic_Days", 1 },
                    { 144695, "Blue Lock: Episode Nagi has been published digitally as an English simulpub through K Manga. The volumes have also been published by Kodansha USA since October 15, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/269866.jpg", 900, 7.93m, new DateTime(2022, 6, 8, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "A spin-off series of Blue Lock focusing on Seishirou Nagi and Reo Mikage.", "Blue Lock: Episode Nagi", "Blue Lock: Episode Nagi", "ブルーロック-EPISODE 凪-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/144695/Blue_Lock__Episode_Nagi", null },
                    { 144724, "Shinmai Ossan Boukensha, Saikyou Party ni Shinu hodo Kitaerarete Muteki ni Naru. began as web novel. The first offical volume was published on December 22, 2018 by Hobby Japan under the HJ Novels label.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/279405.jpg", 34880, null, new DateTime(2018, 12, 21, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "It is common knowledge that it is best to become an adventurer when you are as young as possible because the magical power that is the basis of an adventurer's strength will hardly grow if you don't train it while you are young. But this man, Rick Gladiator, who became an adventurer when he was over thirty years old, had the combat power of an S-rank adventurer, the highest rank in the world. In fact, Rick has lived an unimaginable life with the members of the legendary Orihalcon Fist, a party of the continent's strongest adventurers. From dragons to vampires, Rick's fighting prowess, trained by his literally \"monster\" mentors, allows him to defeat elite adventurers one after another who try to underestimate him.\n\n(Source: MU)", "Shinmai Ossan Boukensha, Saikyou Party ni Shinu hodo Kitaerarete Muteki ni Naru.", null, "新米オッサン冒険者、最強パーティに死ぬほど鍛えられて無敵になる。", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/144724/Shinmai_Ossan_Boukensha_Saikyou_Party_ni_Shinu_hodo_Kitaerarete_Muteki_ni_Naru", null },
                    { 144847, "Trinity Seven: Revision has been published in English by Yen Press since April 16, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/263319.jpg", 34890, null, new DateTime(2019, 9, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "When Rinka Shinonome, a new transfer student, arrives in high schooler Mitsunari Miyazawa's class, he immediately falls for her and asks her out...only to be impaled by a grotesque monster! The next day, he awakens to find it was all a dream...or was it? As it turns out, he's been reborn with the power of the Magus of Envy, and he'll be fighting alongside Rinka from now on! Will he be able to master his new abilities and protect his little sister from the fiends that once claimed his life?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Trinity Seven: Revision", "Trinity Seven Revision", "トリニティセブン‐リヴィジョン‐", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/144847/Trinity_Seven__Revision", null },
                    { 145006, "Mushoku Tensei: Eris wa Honki de Kiba wo Togu was published digitally in English as Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation - Eris Sharpens Her Fangs by Square Enix through Manga UP!", 6, new DateTime(2022, 8, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/272565.jpg", 2906, 7.5m, new DateTime(2022, 3, 14, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After facing a devastating defeat at the hands of Dragon God Orsted at the Red Wyrm's Lower Jaw mountain range, Eris parts ways with Rudeus and makes her way to the Sword Sanctum in order to rectify her own inexperience as a swordsman. As the \"Mad Dog\" continues to hone her sword skills under the tutelage of the Sword God, her fangs continue to grow stronger and sharper!\n\n(Source: Square Enix)", "Mushoku Tensei: Eris wa Honki de Kiba wo Togu", "Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation - Eris Sharpens Her Fangs", "無職転生～エリスは本気で牙を砥ぐ～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/145006/Mushoku_Tensei__Eris_wa_Honki_de_Kiba_wo_Togu", 1 },
