                    { 146643, "Jujutsu Kaisen Bangai-hen was published in the 2022 #2 issue of Weekly Shounen Jump and was later included in the Jujutsu Kaisen 0.5 booklet, which was distributed at the Jujutsu Kaisen 0 Movie premiere on December 24, 2021. It was published digitally as an English simulpub as Jujutsu Kaisen Bonus Manga through MANGA Plus service.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/259446.jpg", 13059, 6.72m, new DateTime(2021, 12, 12, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "After depleting their savings, the Tokyo Jujutsu High first-years—Yuuta Okkotsu, Maki Zenin, Toge Inumaki, and Panda—search for part-time jobs. When they all start working at a cosmetics store, they are visited by Utahime Iori, who appears to have some adult skin issues that the young students cannot understand.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Jujutsu Kaisen Bangai-hen", "Jujutsu Kaisen Bonus Manga", "呪術廻戦 番外編", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/146643/Jujutsu_Kaisen_Bangai-hen", null },
                    { 146732, "Make Heroine ga Oosugiru! @comic has been published in English as Too Many Losing Heroines! by Seven Seas Entertainment since August 20, 2024.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/270079.jpg", 6164, 7.18m, new DateTime(2022, 4, 28, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "The popular girls in Kazuhiko Nukumizu's class seem to have it all—good looks, lots of friends, and the hearts of all their crushes! Except...not?! Upon witnessing the shocking turn of events where the popular Anna Yanami gets friend-zoned by the boy who has crushed on her since childhood, Kazuhiko starts noticing all the fan favorites are getting similarly turned down by the boys they like. Surrounded by heartbroken heroines, can he keep their spirits up and make sure they don't give up? Or is this a rom-com world where the girls never get their dream guy?\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Make Heroine ga Oosugiru! @comic", "Too Many Losing Heroines!", "負けヒロインが多すぎる!@comic", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/146732/Make_Heroine_ga_Oosugiru_comic", null },
                    { 146846, "", 20, new DateTime(2023, 10, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/288429.jpg", 38196, null, new DateTime(2022, 3, 3, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Warriors and fighters, from all over the space-time, gather to participate in the Space-Time Ultra Tournament. Goku and his allies will face very powerful opponents.\n\n(Source: Dragon Ball Wiki)", "Super Dragon Ball Heroes: Ultra God Mission!!!!", null, "スーパードラゴンボールヒーローズ ウルトラゴッドミッション!!!!", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/146846/Super_Dragon_Ball_Heroes__Ultra_God_Mission", 4 },
