                    { 158167, "Partially based on the Kidou Senshi Gundam F91: Crossbone Vanguard novel, the manga acts as a prequel to the events of Kidou Senshi Gundam F91, depicting the Crossbone Vanguard and the residents of Frontier IV prior to the Cosmo Babylonia War.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/286315.jpg", 31492, null, new DateTime(2020, 1, 23, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "In the futuristic setting of U.C. 0123, the Earth Federation Forces have developed the F91 Gundam, a cutting-edge mobile suit equipped with a Bio-Computer. Dr. Monica Arno and her team work tirelessly to overcome the F91's instability issues. Meanwhile, a mysterious organization called the Crossbone Vanguard emerges, led by Iron Mask and Supreme Commander Meitzer, with ambitious plans to change the world.", "Kidou Senshi Gundam F91 Prequel", "Mobile Suit Gundam Formula 91 Prequel", "機動戦士ガンダム F91 プリクエル", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/158167/Kidou_Senshi_Gundam_F91_Prequel", null },
                    { 158345, "Astrea Record: Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka - Eiyuutan is an adaptation of the story event Idai Boukentan: Astrea Record, written by Fujino Oomori, from the Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Memoria Freese mobile game. The series has been published in English as Astrea Record: Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Tales of Heroes by Yen Press under the Yen On imprint since February 20, 2024.", 40, new DateTime(2022, 12, 13, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/281026.jpg", 37762, null, new DateTime(2022, 10, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Seven years before a certain boy sets foot in the Labyrinth City, chaos and uncertainty plague the hearts of each god, goddess, and adventurer across every familia. Though Lyu Leon spends her waking hours carrying out the will of the goddess Astrea, she is constantly searching for a brand of justice she can believe in. She may be able to rely on the rest of Astrea Familia to serve as her light in the darkness, but evil yet stirs deep within the shadows. A great conflict draws near, and should it arrive, all of Orario will be shaken to its foundations...!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)", "Astrea Record: Dungeon ni Deai wo Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka - Eiyuutan", "Astrea Record: Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? Tales of Heroes", "アストレア・レコード ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうか 英雄譚", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/158345/Astrea_Record__Dungeon_ni_Deai_wo_Motomeru_no_wa_Machigatteiru_Darou_ka_-_Eiyuutan", 3 },
                    { 158357, "Sword Art Online: Unital Ring adapts the 5th story arc from the original light novel.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/291297.jpg", 37766, null, new DateTime(2023, 4, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Takes place after the events of Sword Art Online: Project Alicization. Kirito, Asuna, and the others have their accounts forcibly migrated to Unital Ring, a new VRMMORPG which incorporates locations from all the other environments they previously visited, and investigate the cause while meeting some familiar faces.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia, edited)", "Sword Art Online: Unital Ring", null, "ソードアート・オンライン ユナイタル・リング", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/158357/Sword_Art_Online__Unital_Ring", null },
                    { 158887, "", 31, new DateTime(2021, 12, 2, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/285532.jpg", 40824, null, new DateTime(2019, 8, 15, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "There is English bread, German bread, and French bread, but no typical Japanese bread... a \"Ja-pan\" in short does not exist... Here is a unique opportunity to make a mark in the history of the bakery! This is the life goal of young baker Hiromi Daisaku who aspires to create the next Japanese bread! But alas, creating this \"Ja-pan\" is not as simple as Daisaku thought, and returning to reality is somewhat bitter for him. Finally, Daisaku's laborious little routine changes when a mysterious woman approaches the front door of his bakery.", "Yakitate!! Japan: Super Real", null, "焼きたて!!ジャぱん～超現実〈スーパーリアル〉～", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/158887/Yakitate_Japan__Super_Real", 5 },
                    { 159387, "Mushoku Tensei: Dasoku-hen began as a web novel on Shousetsuka ni Narou on May 19, 2015. It has been published in print by Kadokawa since June 23, 2023.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/283797.jpg", 568, 8.11m, new DateTime(2023, 6, 22, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Rudeus Greyrat has finally emerged victorious from the showdown at Biheiril Kingdom. With his hard-fought battle over, he can finally rest easy and put his adventuring days behind him. Yeah right! The epic fight may be done, but the story of the Jobless Reincarnation cast is far from over. There's still Norn's wedding, Lucie's first day at school, hunting down marriage partners for Dohga and Isolde, and then...is that Ghislaine?! Get ready for a bounty of antics and action from the Mushoku Tensei universe as the story continues!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)", "Mushoku Tensei: Dasoku-hen", "Mushoku Tensei: Redundant Reincarnation", "無職転生 ～蛇足編～", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/159387/Mushoku_Tensei__Dasoku-hen", null },
                    { 159536, "", 6, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/289413.jpg", 31795, null, new DateTime(2001, 8, 30, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Six years after the conclusion of the One Year War (UC0086~0087). A girl who lost not only her parents, but her own memory by a colony dropping thanks to the Zeon, is recruited into a Newtype research institute (the Murasame Labs). After aimlessly wandering, she becomes test subject No. 004 (aka \"Four\"). Here she is trained to become a strengthened human with two other subjects (No. 005 Jill Ratokie and No. 006 Amari Garfield). The intense training killed many people, and yet through it all Four and Jill comfort each other. On the other side of the spectrum, at the Augusta Laboratory, Dr. Murasame learns of their plans to create another artificial newtype: Rosamia Badam. Murasame studies Rosamia's memory. It appears that the fear of a colony dropping amplified the newtype potential. In order to do this, Amari and Jill would be used.\n\n(Source: zeonic-republic.net)", "Kidou Senshi Z Gundam Four Story: Soshite, Senshi ni...", null, "機動戦士Zガンダムフォウ・ストーリー: そして、戦士に...", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/159536/Kidou_Senshi_Z_Gundam_Four_Story__Soshite_Senshi_ni", 1 },
                    { 159674, "", 24, new DateTime(2018, 6, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/283408.jpg", 31829, null, new DateTime(2011, 4, 3, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In the Kaettekita 3-nen Z-gumi Ginpachi-sensei series:\n\n1. Kaettekita 3-nen Z-gumi Ginpachi-sensei Returns: Reiketsu Kouha Takasugi-kun\n2. Kaettekita 3-nen Z-gumi Ginpachi-sensei Phoenix: Funky Monkey Teachers\n3. Kaettekita 3-nen Z-gumi Ginpachi-sensei Forever: Saraba, Itoshiki 3 Z-tachi yo\n4. Kaettekita 3-nen Z-gumi Ginpachi-sensei Motto Returns: Reiketsu Kouha Takasugi-kun", "Gintama: Kaettekita 3-nen Z-gumi Ginpachi-sensei", null, "銀魂 帰ってきた3年Z組銀八先生", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/159674/Gintama__Kaettekita_3-nen_Z-gumi_Ginpachi-sensei", 4 },
                    { 159777, "", 8, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/294667.jpg", 31858, null, new DateTime(2023, 6, 18, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Hol Horse accepts a request from an elderly woman to find her lost parrot, who was trained by the owner of Pet Shop, he finds himself trekking across half the globe to the Japanese city of Morioh.\n\nIn Morioh, Hol Horse quickly runs into Josuke Higashikata. Will the two become friends or foes? Then, what new enemy with grotesque stand powers lurks in Morioh? And will Hol Horse and Dio's other former followers ever truly be free from his influence?\n\n(Source: VIZ Media)", "Crazy Diamond no Akuryou-teki Shitsuren: JoJo no Kimyou na Bouken yori", "JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Crazy Heartbreakers", "クレイジーD〈ダイヤモンド〉の悪霊的失恋-ジョジョの奇妙な冒険より-", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/159777/Crazy_Diamond_no_Akuryou-teki_Shitsuren__JoJo_no_Kimyou_na_Bouken_yori", 1 },
                    { 159958, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/283876.jpg", 38136, null, new DateTime(2023, 5, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "Koyomi Araragi and Hitagi Senjougahara are finally married. Shinobu Oshino and Suruga Kanbaru accompany the couple on their eccentric honeymoon, and the itinerary includes an investigation into a strange phenomenon. Koyomi has a plan related to Hitagi and Shinobu? These are the modern-day oddities! Oddities! Oddities! \n\n(Source: Kodansha, translated)", "Monogatari Series: Family Season", null, "〈物語〉シリーズ ファミリーシーズン", 2, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/159958/Monogatari_Series__Family_Season", null },
                    { 160710, "Following the NARUTOP99 Worldwide Character Popularity Vote commemorating the 20th anniversary of the Naruto anime, Naruto Gaiden: Uzu no Naka no Tsumujikaze was released to compliment the winning character Minato Namikaze. In celebration of the new manga, a special column series about Minato was made available on the official website between July 19, 2023, and July 23, 2023. The one-shot was published digitally as an English simulpub as Naruto: The Whorl within the Spiral through MANGA Plus.", 1, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/3/285320.jpg", 1019, 7.89m, new DateTime(2023, 7, 16, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "Long before Naruto Uzumaki mastered the formidable Rasengan, Minato Namikaze trains to develop the ninjutsu under the tutelage of his mentor Jiraiya. Minato strives to create his own powerful technique to protect Kushina Uzumaki, the strong-willed woman he loves.\n\nHonoring Uzumaki clan tradition, Kushina's body hosts the nine-tailed fox spirit, Kurama. The demon seeks to break free from his confines and wreak havoc on the world. As Kushina struggles against Kurama's power and her own inner turmoil, Minato hurries to complete the Rasengan and save her from herself.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]", "Naruto Gaiden: Uzu no Naka no Tsumujikaze", "Naruto: The Whorl within the Spiral", "NARUTO-ナルト-外伝 〜渦の中のつむじ風〜", 3, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/160710/Naruto_Gaiden__Uzu_no_Naka_no_Tsumujikaze", null },
                    { 160723, "", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/293572.jpg", 38307, null, new DateTime(2016, 3, 9, 16, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "In July 2116, the Southeast Asia Union (SEAUn) and the Japanese government begin to export the Sibyl System to the coastal town of Shambala Float during a civil war as an experiment in spreading the system throughout the world. Under Sibyl's rule, Shambala Float achieves temporary peace and safety, but when SEAUn sends terrorists to Japan, now able to slip through the Sibyl System and attack Japan from within, the shadow of a certain man falls on the incident and Inspector Akane Tsunemori must lead her team to Shambala Float to investigate.\n\n(Source: Psycho-Pass Wiki)", "Gekijouban Psycho-Pass", null, "劇場版 PSYCHO-PASS", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/160723/Gekijouban_Psycho-Pass", 1 },
                    { 160786, "Boruto: Two Blue Vortex has been published digitally as an English simulpub through MANGA Plus.", null, null, "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/2/296325.jpg", 904, 7.93m, new DateTime(2023, 8, 20, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 4, "With everyone's memories having been altered, Boruto finds himself being hunted by his own village. After escaping with Sasuke, what future awaits Boruto...?\n\n(Source: MANGA Plus)", "Boruto: Two Blue Vortex", "Boruto: Two Blue Vortex", "BORUTO-ボルト- -TWO BLUE VORTEX-", 1, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/160786/Boruto__Two_Blue_Vortex", null },
                    { 160805, "", 121, new DateTime(2023, 7, 13, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), "https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/manga/1/285425.jpg", 38334, null, new DateTime(2020, 6, 25, 17, 0, 0, 0, DateTimeKind.Local), 2, "As long as anyone can remember, there have been rumors of man-eating demons living in the woods. Even in the more enlightened Taishou era, the townspeople never go near there at night. Tanjirou Kamado, a kind boy who has been supporting his family as a coal seller since his father died, quickly learns that the local superstition is more than just rumors when he returns home one day to find his family slaughtered by demons. Only he and his sister Nezuko manage to survive, but she is transformed into a demon. Determined and resolute, he is recruited into the Demon Slayer Corps and his quest to help turn his sister human again and avenge his family's deaths begins.\n\n(Source: Shueisha, translated)", "Kimetsu no Yaiba Novelize", null, "鬼滅の刃 ノベライズ", 5, "https://myanimelist.net/manga/160805/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_Novelize", 10 },
